460205,107,2058,4,4,1,34,1,Aññāsikoṇḍaññattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
460206,107,2059,2,8,1,73,5,Padumuttarasambuddhan tiādikaṃ āyasmato aññāsikoṇḍaññattherassa apadānaṃ. 
460207,107,2059,9,54,1,453,44,Ayaṃ kira purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle haṃsavatīnagare gahapatimahāsālakule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patvā ekadivasaṃ satthu santike dhammaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ attano sāsane paṭhamaṃ paṭividdhadhammarattaññūnaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā sayampi taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthento satasahassabhikkhuparivārassa bhagavato sattāhaṃ mahādānaṃ pavattetvā paṇidhānaṃ akāsi. 
460208,107,2059,55,61,1,58,6,Satthāpissa anantarāyataṃ disvā bhāviniṃ sampattiṃ byākāsi. 
460209,107,2059,62,79,1,158,16,"So yāvajīvaṃ puññāni karonto satthari parinibbute cetiye patiṭṭhāpiyamāne antocetiye ratanagharaṃ kārāpesi, cetiyaṃ parivāretvā sahassaratanagghikāni ca kāresi. "
460210,107,2060,2,30,1,289,28,So evaṃ puññāni katvā tato cavitvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto vipassissa bhagavato kāle mahākālo nāma kuṭumbiko hutvā aṭṭhakarīsamatte khette sāligabbhaṃ phāletvā gahitasālitaṇḍulehi asambhinnakhīrapāyāsaṃ sampādetvā tattha madhusappisakkarādayo pakkhipitvā buddhappamukhassa saṅghassa adāsi. 
460211,107,2060,31,37,1,52,5,Sāligabbhaṃ phāletvā gahitagahitaṭṭhānaṃ puna pūrati. 
460212,107,2060,38,42,1,34,4,Puthukakāle puthukaggaṃ nāma adāsi. 
460213,107,2060,43,70,1,188,21,"Lāyane lāyanaggaṃ, veṇikaraṇe veṇaggaṃ, kalāpādikaraṇe kalāpaggaṃ, khalaggaṃ, bhaṇḍaggaṃ, minaggaṃ koṭṭhagganti evaṃ ekasasse nava vāre aggadānaṃ adāsi, tampi sassaṃ atirekataraṃ sampannaṃ ahosi. "
460214,107,2061,2,25,1,224,23,Evaṃ yāvajīvaṃ puññāni katvā tato cuto devaloke nibbattitvā devesu ca manussesu ca saṃsaranto amhākaṃ bhagavato uppattito puretarameva kapilavatthunagarassa avidūre doṇavatthunāmake brāhmaṇagāme brāhmaṇamahāsālakule nibbatti. 
460215,107,2061,26,33,1,43,6,Tassa {koṇḍañño}ti gottato āgataṃ nāmaṃ ahosi. 
460216,107,2061,34,43,1,66,9,So vayappatto tayo vede uggahetvā lakkhaṇamantesu ca pāraṃ agamāsi. 
460217,107,2061,44,54,1,106,10,Tena samayena amhākaṃ bodhisatto tusitapurato cavitvā kapilavatthupure suddhodanamahārājassa gehe nibbatti. 
460218,107,2061,55,66,1,122,11,Tassa nāmaggahaṇadivase aṭṭhuttarasatesu brāhmaṇesu upanītesu ye aṭṭha brāhmaṇā lakkhaṇapariggahaṇatthaṃ mahātalaṃ upanītā. 
460219,107,2061,67,89,1,163,18,So tesu sabbanavako hutvā mahāpurisassa lakkhaṇanipphattiṃ disvā‘‘ ekaṃsena ayaṃ buddho bhavissatī’’ ti niṭṭhaṃ gantvā mahāsattassa abhinikkhamanaṃ udikkhanto vicarati. 
460220,107,2062,2,23,1,210,20,Bodhisattopi kho mahatā parivārena vaḍḍhamāno anukkamena vuddhippatto ñāṇaparipākaṃ gantvā ekūnatiṃsatime vasse mahābhinikkhamanaṃ nikkhamanto anomānadītīre pabbajitvā anukkamena uruvelaṃ gantvā padhānaṃ padahi. 
460221,107,2062,24,50,1,287,25,Tadā koṇḍañño māṇavo mahāsattassa pabbajitabhāvaṃ sutvā lakkhaṇapariggāhakabrāhmaṇānaṃ puttehi vappamāṇavādīhi saddhiṃ attapañcamo pabbajitvā anukkamena bodhisattassa santikaṃ upasaṅkamitvā chabbassāni taṃ upaṭṭhahanto tassa oḷārikāhāraparibhogena nibbinno apakkamitvā isipatanaṃ agamāsi. 
460222,107,2062,51,92,1,327,27,Atha kho bodhisatto oḷārikāhāraparibhogena laddhakāyabalo vesākhapuṇṇamāyaṃ bodhirukkhamūle aparājitapallaṅke nisinno tiṇṇaṃ mārānaṃ matthakaṃ madditvā abhisambuddho hutvā sattasattāhaṃ bodhimaṇḍeyeva vītināmetvā pañcavaggiyānaṃ ñāṇaparipākaṃ ñatvā āsāḷhīpuṇṇamāyaṃ isipatanaṃ gantvā tesaṃ dhammacakkapavattanasuttantaṃ( mahāva.13 ādayo; saṃ. ni.5.1081) kathesi. 
460223,107,2062,93,101,1,90,7,Desanāpariyosāne koṇḍaññatthero aṭṭhārasahi brahmakoṭīhi saddhiṃ sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāsi. 
460224,107,2062,102,122,1,77,6,Atha pañcamiyaṃ pakkhassa anattalakkhaṇasuttantadesanāya( mahāva.20 ādayo; saṃ. ni.3.59) arahattaṃ sacchākāsi. 
460225,107,2063,2,31,1,214,22,596. Evaṃ so arahattaṃ patvā‘‘ kiṃ kammaṃ katvā ahaṃ lokuttarasukhaṃ adhigatomhī’’ ti upadhārento attano pubbakammaṃ paccakkhato ñatvā somanassavasena pubbacaritāpadānaṃ udānavasena dassento padumuttarasambuddhan tiādimāha. 
