460231,107,2064,2,26,1,201,20,597. Yāvatā bodhiyā {mūle}ti yattakā bodhirukkhasamīpe yakkhā samāgatā rāsibhūtā sambuddhaṃ buddhabhūtaṃ taṃ buddhaṃ pañjalīkatā dasaṅgulisamodhānaṃ añjalipuṭaṃ sirasi ṭhapetvā vandanti namassantīti sambandho. 
