460235,107,2067,2,27,1,198,21,600. Devānaṃ {giramaññāyā}ti vācāya thutivacanena saha udīritaṃ devānaṃ saddaṃ jānitvā haṭṭho haṭṭhena cittena somanassasahagatena cittena ādibhikkhaṃ paṭhamaṃ āhāraṃ buddhabhūtassa ahaṃ adāsinti sambandho. 
460236,107,2068,2,21,1,176,14,602. Sattāhaṃ {abhinikkhammā}ti mahābhinikkhamanaṃ nikkhamitvā sattāhaṃ padhānaṃ katvā sabbaññutaññāṇapadaṭṭhānaṃ arahattamaggañāṇasaṅkhātaṃ bodhiṃ ajjhagamaṃ adhigañchiṃ ahanti attho. 
460237,107,2068,22,40,1,140,18,Idaṃ me paṭhamaṃ bhattan ti idaṃ bhattaṃ sarīrayāpanaṃ brahmacārissa uttamacārissa me mayhaṃ iminā devaputtena paṭhamaṃ dinnaṃ ahosīti attho. 
460238,107,2069,2,27,1,164,20,"603. Tusitā hi {idhāgantvā}ti tusitabhavanato idha manussaloke āgantvā yo devaputto me mama bhikkhaṃ upānayi adāsi, taṃ devaputtaṃ kittayissāmi kathessāmi pākaṭaṃ karissāmi. "
