460250,107,2073,2,39,1,327,31,610. Abhigantvāna {sabbaññū}ti sabbaṃ atītānāgatapaccuppannaṃ vā saṅkhāravikāralakkhaṇanibbānapaññattisaṅkhātaṃ ñeyyaṃ vā jānanto devehi saha vattamāne satta loke buddho migāraññaṃ migadāya vihāraṃ abhigantvā upasaṅkamitvā me mayā sacchikatena iminā sotāpattimaggañāṇena amatabheriṃ amatamahānibbānabheriṃ ahari pahari dassesīti attho. 
460251,107,2074,2,27,1,183,20,"611. So {dānī}ti so ahaṃ paṭhamaṃ sotāpanno idāni arahattamaggañāṇena amataṃ santaṃ vūpasantasabhāvaṃ padaṃ pajjitabbaṃ pāpuṇitabbaṃ, anuttaraṃ uttaravirahitaṃ nibbānaṃ patto adhigatoti attho. "
