460536,107,2166,2,4,1,25,2,3 . Nandattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
460537,107,2167,2,10,1,65,5,Padumuttarassa {bhagavato}tiādikaṃ āyasmato nandattherassa apadānaṃ. 
460538,107,2167,11,68,1,476,51,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle haṃsavatīnagare ekasmiṃ kule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto bhagavato santike dhammaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ indriyesu guttadvārānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā sayaṃ taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthento bhagavato bhikkhusaṅghassa ca pūjāsakkārabahulaṃ mahādānaṃ pavattetvā‘‘ ahaṃ, bhante, anāgate tumhādisassa buddhassa evarūpo sāvako bhaveyyan’’ ti paṇidhānaṃ akāsi. "
460539,107,2168,2,30,1,231,28,So tato paṭṭhāya devamanussesu saṃsaranto atthadassissa bhagavato kāle dhammatāya nāma nadiyā mahanto kacchapo hutvā nibbatto ekadivasaṃ satthāraṃ nadiṃ tarituṃ tīre ṭhitaṃ disvā sayaṃ bhagavantaṃ tāretukāmo satthu pādamūle nipajji. 
460540,107,2168,31,37,1,46,6,Satthā tassa ajjhāsayaṃ ñatvā piṭṭhiṃ abhiruhi. 
460541,107,2168,38,46,1,66,8,So haṭṭhatuṭṭho vegena sotaṃ chindanto sīghataraṃ paratīraṃ pāpesi. 
460542,107,2168,47,55,1,68,8,Bhagavā tassa anumodanaṃ vadanto bhāviniṃ sampattiṃ kathetvā pakkāmi. 
460543,107,2169,2,30,1,235,22,"So tena puññakammena sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kapilavatthusmiṃ suddhodanamahārājassa aggamahesiyā mahāpajāpatigotamiyā kucchimhi nibbatto, tassa nāmaggahaṇadivase ñātisaṅghaṃ nandayanto jātoti‘‘ nando’’ tveva nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
460544,107,2169,31,105,1,488,42,Tassa vayappattakāle bhagavā pavattitavaradhammacakko lokānuggahaṃ karonto anukkamena kapilavatthuṃ gantvā ñātisamāgame pokkharavassaṃ aṭṭhuppattiṃ katvā vessantarajātakaṃ( jā.2.22.1655 ādayo) kathetvā dutiyadivase piṇḍāya paviṭṭho‘‘ uttiṭṭhe nappamajjeyyā’’ ti( dha. pa.168) gāthāya pitaraṃ sotāpattiphale patiṭṭhāpetvā nivesanaṃ gantvā‘‘ dhammañcare sucaritan’’ ti( dha. pa.169) gāthāya mahāpajāpatiṃ sotāpattiphale rājānaṃ sakadāgāmiphale patiṭṭhāpetvā tatiyadivase nandakumārassa abhisekagehapavesanaāvāhamaṅgalesu vattamānesu piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
460545,107,2169,106,136,1,251,28,"Satthā nandakumārassa hatthe pattaṃ datvā maṅgalaṃ vatvā tassa hatthato pattaṃ aggahetvāva vihāraṃ gato , taṃ pattahatthaṃ vihāraṃ āgataṃ anicchamānaṃyeva pabbājetvā tathāpabbājitattāyeva anabhiratiyā pīḷitaṃ ñatvā upāyena tassa taṃ anabhiratiṃ vinodesi. "
460546,107,2169,137,145,1,74,8,So yoniso paṭisaṅkhāya vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
460547,107,2169,146,152,1,51,6,Thero puna divase bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evamāha–
460548,107,2169,153,178,1,132,15,"‘‘ yaṃ me, bhante, bhagavā pāṭibhogo pañcannaṃ accharāsatānaṃ paṭilābhāya kakuṭapādānaṃ, muñcāmahaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ etasmā paṭissavā’’ ti. "
460549,107,2169,179,200,1,97,14,"Bhagavāpi‘‘ yadeva te, nanda, anupādāya āsavehi cittaṃ vimuttaṃ, tadāhaṃ mutto etasmā paṭissavā’’ ti āha. "
460550,107,2169,201,242,1,212,24,"Athassa bhagavā savisesaṃ indriyesu guttadvārataṃ ñatvā taṃ guṇaṃ vibhāvento‘‘ etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ indriyesu guttadvārānaṃ yadidaṃ nando’’ ti( a. ni.1.219,230) indriyesu guttadvārabhāvena naṃ etadagge ṭhapesi. "
460551,107,2169,243,267,1,177,19,"Thero hi‘‘ indriyāsaṃvaraṃ nissāya imaṃ vippakāraṃ patto, tamahaṃ suṭṭhu niggaṇhissāmī’’ ti ussāhajāto balavahirottappo tattha ca katādhikārattā indriyasaṃvare ukkaṃsapāramiṃ agamāsi. "
460552,107,2170,2,18,1,135,12,27. Evaṃ so etadaggaṭṭhānaṃ patvā attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassappatto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttarassa {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
460553,107,2170,19,35,1,145,16,Vatthaṃ khomaṃ mayā dinnan ti khomaraṭṭhe jātaṃ vatthaṃ bhagavati cittappasādena gāravabahumānena mayā paramasukhumaṃ khomavatthaṃ dinnanti attho. 
460554,107,2170,36,45,1,66,7,{Sayambhussā}ti sayameva bhūtassa jātassa ariyāya jātiyā nibbattassa. 
460555,107,2170,46,62,1,165,14,"{Mahesino}ti mahante sīlasamādhipaññāvimuttivimuttiñāṇadassanakkhandhe esi gavesīti mahesi, tassa mahesino sayambhussa cīvaratthāya khomavatthaṃ mayā dinnanti sambandho. "
460556,107,2171,2,25,1,136,18,"28. Taṃ me buddho {viyākāsī}ti ettha tan ti sāmyatthe upayogavacanaṃ, tassa vatthadāyakassa me dānaphalaṃ visesena akāsi kathesi buddhoti attho. "
460557,107,2171,26,29,1,37,2,{Jalajuttamanāmako}ti padumuttaranāmako.
460558,107,2171,30,44,1,89,9,"‘‘ Jalaruttamanāyako’’ tipi pāṭho, tassa jalamānānaṃ devabrahmānaṃ uttamanāyako padhānoti attho. "
460559,107,2171,45,56,1,98,10,Iminā {vatthadānenā}ti iminā vatthadānassa nissandena tvaṃ anāgate hemavaṇṇo suvaṇṇavaṇṇo bhavissasi. 
460560,107,2172,2,14,1,73,7,29. Dve sampattiṃ {anubhotvā}ti dibbamanussasaṅkhātā dve sampattiyo anubhavitvā. 
460561,107,2172,15,37,1,131,16,"Kusalamūlehi {codito}ti kusalāvayavehi kusalakoṭṭhāsehi codito pesito,‘‘ tvaṃ iminā puññena satthu kulaṃ pasavāhī’’ ti pesito viyāti attho."
460562,107,2172,38,50,1,67,8,‘‘ Gotamassa bhagavato kaniṭṭho tvaṃ bhavissasī’’ ti byākāsīti sambandho. 
460563,107,2173,2,12,1,83,6,30. Rāgaratto {sukhasīlo}ti kilesakāmehi ratto allīno kāyasukhacittasukhānubhavanasabhāvo. 
460564,107,2173,13,22,1,78,8,Kāmesu {gedhamāyuto}ti vatthukāmesu gedhasaṅkhātāya taṇhāya āyuto yojitoti attho. 
460565,107,2173,23,48,1,169,22,"Buddhena codito santo, tadā tvan ti yasmā kāmesu gedhito, tadā tasmā tvaṃ attano bhātukena gotamabuddhena codito pabbajjāya uyyojito tassa santike pabbajissasīti sambandho. "
460566,107,2174,2,35,1,280,28,"31. Pabbajitvāna tvaṃ {tatthā}ti tasmiṃ gotamassa bhagavato sāsane tvaṃ pabbajitvā kusalamūlena mūlabhūtena puññasambhārena codito bhāvanāyaṃ niyojito sabbāsave sakalāsave pariññāya jānitvā pajahitvā anāmayo niddukkho nibbāyissasi adassanaṃ pāpessasi, apaṇṇattikabhāvaṃ gamissasīti attho. "
460567,107,2175,2,18,1,124,12,32. {Satakappasahassamhī}ti ito kappato pubbe satakappādhike sahassame kappamhi ceḷanāmakā cattāro cakkavattirājāno ahesunti attho. 
460568,107,2175,19,38,1,153,18,Saṭṭhi {kappasahassānī}ti kappasahassāni saṭṭhi ca atikkamitvā heṭṭhā ekasmiṃ kappe cattāro janā upaceḷā nāma cakkavattirājāno catūsu jātīsu ahesunti attho. 
460569,107,2176,2,27,1,238,20,33. {Pañcakappasahassamhī}ti pañcakappādhike sahassame kappamhi ceḷā nāma cattāro janā cakkavattirājāno sattahi ratanehi sampannā samaṅgībhūtā jambudīpaaparagoyānauttarakurupubbavidehadīpasaṅkhāte catudīpamhi issarā padhānā visuṃ ahesunti attho. 
460570,107,2176,28,30,1,21,2,Sesaṃ vuttanayamevāti. 
460571,107,2177,2,4,1,33,2,Nandattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
460572,107,2178,2,4,1,32,2,4 . Cūḷapanthakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
460573,107,2179,2,10,1,69,6,Padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādikaṃ āyasmato cūḷapanthakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
460574,107,2179,11,37,1,209,19,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle yadettha aṭṭhuppattivasena vattabbaṃ, taṃ aṭṭhakanipāte mahāpanthakavatthusmiṃ( theragā.510 ādayo) vuttameva. "
460575,107,2179,38,48,1,93,9,Ayaṃ pana viseso– mahāpanthakatthero arahattaṃ patvā phalasamāpattisukhena vītināmento cintesi–
460576,107,2179,49,62,1,66,9,‘‘ kathaṃ nu kho sakkā cūḷapanthakampi imasmiṃ sukhe patiṭṭhāpetun’’ ti. 
460577,107,2179,63,69,1,48,6,So attano ayyakaṃ dhanaseṭṭhiṃ upasaṅkamitvā āha–
460578,107,2179,70,85,1,60,7,"‘‘ sace, mahāseṭṭhi , anujānātha, ahaṃ cūḷapanthakaṃ pabbājeyyan’’ ti."
460579,107,2179,86,94,1,20,3,"‘‘ Pabbājetha, bhante’’ ti. "
460580,107,2179,95,98,1,19,3,Thero taṃ pabbājesi. 
460581,107,2179,99,105,1,41,6,So dasasu sīlesu patiṭṭhito bhātu santike–
460582,107,2180,2,12,1,63,8,"‘ ‘ Padumaṃ yathā kokanadaṃ sugandhaṃ, pāto siyā phullamavītagandhaṃ; "
460583,107,2181,2,28,1,58,5,"Aṅgīrasaṃ passa virocamānaṃ, tapantamādiccamivantalikkhe’’ ti.( saṃ. ni.1.123; a. ni.5.195)– "
460584,107,2182,2,13,1,79,10,"Gāthaṃ uggaṇhanto catūhi māsehi uggahetuṃ nāsakkhi, gahitampi hadaye na tiṭṭhati. "
460585,107,2182,14,53,1,235,30,"Atha naṃ mahāpanthako,‘‘ cūḷapanthaka, tvaṃ imasmiṃ sāsane abhabbo, catūhi māsehi ekaṃ gāthampi gahetuṃ na sakkosi, pabbajitakiccaṃ pana tvaṃ kathaṃ matthakaṃ pāpessasi, nikkhama ito’’ ti so therena paṇāmiko dvārakoṭṭhakasamīpe rodamāno aṭṭhāsi. "
460586,107,2183,2,8,1,46,6,Tena ca samayena satthā jīvakambavane viharati. 
460587,107,2183,9,13,1,26,4,Atha jīvako purisaṃ pesesi–
460588,107,2183,14,26,1,59,7,"‘‘ gaccha, pañcahi bhikkhusatehi saddhiṃ satthāraṃ nimantehī’’ ti. "
460589,107,2183,27,34,1,55,7,Tena ca samayena āyasmā mahāpanthako bhattuddesako hoti. 
460590,107,2183,35,56,1,106,13,So‘‘ pañcannaṃ bhikkhusatānaṃ bhikkhaṃ paṭicchathā’’ ti vutto‘‘ cūḷapanthakaṃ ṭhapetvā sesānaṃ paṭicchāmī’’ ti āha. 
460591,107,2183,57,63,1,60,6,Taṃ sutvā cūḷapanthako bhiyyosomattāya domanassappatto ahosi. 
460592,107,2183,64,94,1,146,19,"Satthā tassa cittakkhedaṃ ñatvā‘‘ cūḷapanthako mayā katena upāyena bujjhissatī’’ ti tassa avidūraṭṭhāne attānaṃ dassetvā‘‘ kiṃ, panthaka, rodasī’’ ti pucchi."
460593,107,2183,95,107,1,32,6,"‘‘ Bhātā maṃ, bhante, paṇāmetī’’ ti āha."
460594,107,2183,108,140,1,159,21,"‘‘ Panthaka, mā cintayi, mama sāsane tuyhaṃ pabbajjā, ehi imaṃ gahetvā‘ rajoharaṇaṃ, rajoharaṇan’ ti manasi karohī’’ ti iddhiyā suddhaṃ coḷakkhaṇḍaṃ abhisaṅkharitvā adāsi. "
460595,107,2183,141,156,1,87,10,"So satthārā dinnaṃ coḷakkhaṇḍaṃ‘‘ rajoharaṇaṃ, rajoharaṇan’’ ti hatthena parimajjanto nisīdi. "
460596,107,2183,157,167,1,102,9,"Tassa taṃ parimajjantassa kiliṭṭhadhātukaṃ jātaṃ, puna parimajjantassa ukkhaliparipuñchanasadisaṃ jātaṃ. "
460597,107,2183,168,172,1,31,4,So ñāṇaparipākattā evaṃ cintesi–
460598,107,2183,173,210,1,276,30,"‘‘ idaṃ coḷakkhaṇḍaṃ pakatiyā parisuddhaṃ, imaṃ upādiṇṇakasarīraṃ nissāya kiliṭṭhaṃ aññathā jātaṃ, tasmā aniccaṃ yathāpetaṃ, evaṃ cittampī’’ ti khayavayaṃ paṭṭhapetvā tasmiṃyeva nimitte jhānāni nibbattetvā jhānapādakaṃ katvā vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
460599,107,2183,211,216,1,55,5,Arahattapattassevassa tepiṭakaṃ pañcābhiññā ca āgamiṃsu. 
460600,107,2184,2,12,1,89,10,Satthā ekūnehi pañcabhikkhusatehi saddhiṃ gantvā jīvakassa nivesane paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
460601,107,2184,13,21,1,62,8,Cūḷapanthako pana attano bhikkhāya appaṭicchitattā eva na gato. 
460602,107,2184,22,27,1,25,4,Jīvako yāguṃ dātuṃ ārabhi. 
460603,107,2184,28,32,1,29,4,Satthā hatthena pattaṃ pidahi.
460604,107,2184,33,56,1,68,12,"‘‘ Kasmā, bhante, na gaṇhathā’’ ti vutte‘‘ vihāre eko bhikkhu atthi, jīvakā’’ ti. "
460605,107,2184,57,60,1,17,3,So purisaṃ pesesi–
460606,107,2184,61,75,1,49,8,"‘‘ gaccha, bhaṇe, vihāre nisinnaṃ ayyaṃ gahetvā ehī’’ ti. "
460607,107,2184,76,86,1,95,10,Cūḷapanthakattheropi rūpena kiriyāya ca ekampi ekena asadisaṃ bhikkhusahassaṃ nimminitvā nisīdi. 
460608,107,2184,87,96,1,69,9,So puriso vihāre bhikkhūnaṃ bahubhāvaṃ disvā gantvā jīvakassa kathesi–
460609,107,2184,97,112,1,83,10,"‘‘ imasmā bhikkhusaṅghā vihāre bhikkhusaṅgho bahutaro, pakkositabbaṃ ayyaṃ na jānāmī’’ ti. "
460610,107,2184,113,116,1,23,3,Jīvako satthāraṃ pucchi–
460611,107,2184,117,130,1,40,7,"‘‘ ko nāmo, bhante, vihāre nisinno bhikkhū’’ ti?"
460612,107,2184,131,140,1,27,4,"‘‘ Cūḷapanthako nāma, jīvakā’’ ti."
460613,107,2184,141,159,1,63,10,"‘‘ Gaccha, bhaṇe,‘ cūḷapanthako nāma kataro’ ti pucchitvā taṃ ānehī’’ ti. "
460614,107,2184,160,174,1,59,9,"So vihāraṃ gantvā‘‘ cūḷapanthako nāma kataro, bhante’’ ti pucchi."
460615,107,2184,175,188,1,77,8,"‘‘ Ahaṃ cūḷapanthako, ahaṃ cūḷapanthako’’ ti ekappahārena bhikkhusahassampi kathesi. "
460616,107,2184,189,230,1,205,28,"So punāgantvā taṃ pavattiṃ jīvakassa ārocesi jīvako paṭividdhasaccattā‘‘ iddhimā maññe, ayyo’’ ti nayato ñatvā‘‘ gaccha, bhaṇe, paṭhamaṃ kathentaṃ ayyameva‘ tumhe satthā pakkosatī’ ti vatvā cīvarakaṇṇe gaṇhāhī’’ ti āha. "
460617,107,2184,231,236,1,29,5,So vihāraṃ gantvā tathā akāsi. 
460618,107,2184,237,240,1,38,3,Tāvadeva nimmitabhikkhū antaradhāyiṃsu. 
460619,107,2184,241,245,1,25,4,So theraṃ gahetvā agamāsi. 
460620,107,2185,2,9,1,57,6,Satthā tasmiṃ khaṇe yāguñca khajjakādibhedañca paṭiggaṇhi. 
460621,107,2185,10,22,1,77,8,Katabhattakicco bhagavā āyasmantaṃ cūḷapanthakaṃ āṇāpesi‘‘ anumodanaṃ karohī’’ ti. 
460622,107,2185,23,39,1,148,15,So pabhinnapaṭisambhido sineruṃ gahetvā mahāsamuddaṃ manthento viya tepiṭakaṃ buddhavacanaṃ saṅkhobhento satthu ajjhāsayaṃ gaṇhanto anumodanaṃ akāsi. 
460623,107,2185,40,108,1,452,56,"Dasabale bhattakiccaṃ katvā vihāraṃ gate dhammasabhāyaṃ kathā udapādi‘ aho buddhānaṃ ānubhāvo, yatra hi nāma cattāro māse ekagāthaṃ gahetuṃ asakkontampi lahukena khaṇeneva evaṃ mahiddhikaṃ akaṃsū’ ti, tathā hi jīvakassa nivesane nisinno bhagavā‘ evaṃ cūḷapanthakassa cittaṃ samāhitaṃ, vīthipaṭipannā vipassanā’ ti ñatvā yathānisinnoyeva attānaṃ dassetvā,‘ panthaka, nevāyaṃ pilotikā kiliṭṭhā rajānukiṇṇā, ito pana aññopi ariyassa vinaye saṃkileso rajo’ ti dassento–"
460624,107,2186,2,15,1,63,11,"‘ ‘ Rāgo rajo na ca pana reṇu vuccati, rāgassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ rajoti; "
460625,107,2187,2,11,1,67,8,"Etaṃ rajaṃ vippajahitvā bhikkhavo, viharanti te vigatarajassa sāsane."
460626,107,2188,2,11,1,33,6,‘ ‘ Doso rajo… pe… vigatarajassa sāsane.
460627,107,2189,2,26,1,36,7,‘ ‘ Moho rajo… pe… vigatarajassa sāsane’’ ti.( mahāni.209; cūḷani. udayamāṇavapucchāniddesa74)– 
460628,107,2190,2,6,1,24,4,Imā tisso gāthāyo abhāsi. 
460629,107,2190,7,12,1,66,5,Gāthāpariyosāne cūḷapanthako sahapaṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ pāpuṇīti. 
460630,107,2190,13,74,1,292,36,"Satthā tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kathāsallāpaṃ sutvā āgantvā buddhāsane nisīditvā‘‘ kiṃ vadetha, bhikkhave’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ imaṃ nāma, bhante’’ ti vutte‘‘ bhikkhave, cūḷapanthakena idāni mayhaṃ ovāde ṭhatvā lokuttharadāyajjaṃ laddhaṃ, pubbe pana lokiyadāyajjaṃ laddhan’’ ti vatvā tehi yācito cūḷaseṭṭhijātakaṃ( jā.1.1.4) kathesi. "
460631,107,2190,75,88,1,145,13,Aparabhāge naṃ satthā ariyagaṇaparivuto dhammāsane nisinno manomayaṃ kāyaṃ abhinimminantānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ cetovivaṭṭakusalānañca aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapesi. 
460632,107,2191,2,18,1,134,12,35. Evaṃ so pattaetadaggaṭṭhāno attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā pītisomanassavasena pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādimāha. 
460633,107,2191,19,22,1,37,3,Tattha purimapadadvayaṃ vuttatthameva. 
460634,107,2191,23,40,1,120,15,Gaṇamhā vūpakaṭṭho {so}ti so padumuttaro nāma satthā gaṇamhā mahatā bhikkhusamūhato vūpakaṭṭho visuṃ bhūto vivekaṃ upagato. 
460635,107,2191,41,55,1,106,12,"Tadā mama tāpasakāle himavante himālayapabbatasamīpe vasi vāsaṃ kappesi, catūhi iriyāpathehi vihāsīti attho. "
460636,107,2192,2,34,1,207,24,"36. Ahampi… pe… {tadā}ti yadā so bhagavā himavantaṃ upagantvā vasi, tadā ahampi himavantasamīpe kataassame ā samantato kāyacittapīḷāsaṅkhātā parissayā samanti etthāti {assamo}ti laddhanāme araññāvāse vasāmīti sambandho. "
460637,107,2192,35,51,1,143,15,"Acirāgataṃ mahāvīran ti aciraṃ āgataṃ mahāvīriyavantaṃ lokanāyakaṃ padhānaṃ taṃ bhagavantaṃ upesinti sambandho, āgatakkhaṇeyeva upāgaminti attho. "
460638,107,2193,2,25,1,189,19,37. Pupphacchattaṃ {gahetvānā}ti evaṃ upagacchanto ca padumuppalapupphādīhi chāditaṃ pupphamayaṃ chattaṃ gahetvā narāsabhaṃ narānaṃ seṭṭhaṃ bhagavantaṃ chādento upagacchiṃ samīpaṃ gatosmīti attho. 
460639,107,2193,26,37,1,117,11,Samādhiṃ samāpajjantan ti rūpāvacarasamādhijjhānaṃ samāpajjantaṃ appetvā nisinnassa antarāyaṃ ahaṃ akāsinti sambandho. 
460640,107,2194,2,20,1,114,13,38. Ubho hatthehi {paggayhā}ti taṃ susajjitaṃ pupphacchattaṃ dvīhi hatthehi ukkhipitvā ahaṃ bhagavato adāsinti sambandho. 
460641,107,2194,21,34,1,99,11,"{Paṭiggahesī}ti taṃ mayā dinnaṃ pupphacchattaṃ padumuttaro bhagavā sampaṭicchi, sādaraṃ sādiyīti attho. "
460642,107,2195,2,23,1,176,17,41. Satapattachattaṃ {paggayhā}ti ekekasmiṃ padumapupphe satasatapattānaṃ vasena satapattehi padumapupphehi chāditaṃ pupphacchattaṃ pakārena ādarena gahetvā tāpaso mama adāsīti attho. 
460643,107,2195,24,34,1,78,9,Tamahaṃ {kittayissāmī}ti taṃ tāpasaṃ ahaṃ kittayissāmi pākaṭaṃ karissāmīti attho. 
460644,107,2195,35,42,1,56,7,Mama bhāsato bhāsamānassa vacanaṃ suṇotha manasi karotha. 
460645,107,2196,2,16,1,124,10,42. {Pañcavīsatikappānī}ti iminā pupphacchattadānena pañcavīsativāre tāvatiṃsabhavane sakko hutvā devarajjaṃ karissatīti sambandho. 
460646,107,2196,17,24,1,80,6,{Catuttiṃsatikkhattuñcā}ti catuttiṃsativāre manussaloke cakkavattī rājā bhavissati. 
460647,107,2197,2,17,1,77,11,43. Yaṃ yaṃ yonin ti manussayoniādīsu yaṃ yaṃ jātiṃ saṃsarati gacchati upapajjati. 
460648,107,2197,18,32,1,123,14,Tattha tattha yoniyaṃ abbhokāse suññaṭṭhāne patiṭṭhantaṃ nisinnaṃ ṭhitaṃ vā padumaṃ dhārayissati upari chādayissatīti attho. 
460649,107,2198,2,17,1,118,11,45. Pakāsite {pāvacane}ti tena bhagavato sakalapiṭakattaye pakāsite dīpite manussattaṃ manussajātiṃ labhissati upapajjissati. 
460650,107,2198,18,37,1,134,15,"Manomayamhi {kāyamhī}ti manena jhānacittena nibbattoti manomayo, yathā cittaṃ pavattati, tathā kāyaṃ pavatteti cittagatikaṃ karotīti attho. "
460651,107,2198,38,50,1,87,12,Tamhi manomaye kāyamhi so tāpaso cūḷapanthako nāma hutvā uttamo aggo bhavissatīti attho. 
460652,107,2198,51,57,1,49,6,Sesaṃ heṭṭhā vuttattā uttānattā ca suviññeyyameva. 
460653,107,2199,2,17,1,98,12,52. Sariṃ kokanadaṃ ahan ti ahaṃ bhagavato nimmitacoḷakaṃ parimajjanto kokanadaṃ padumaṃ sarinti attho. 
460654,107,2199,18,36,1,120,16,"Tattha cittaṃ vimucci {me}ti tasmiṃ kokanade padume mayhaṃ cittaṃ adhimucci allīno, tato ahaṃ arahattaṃ pāpuṇinti sambandho. "
460655,107,2200,2,16,1,97,11,53. Ahaṃ manomayesu cittagatikesu kāyesu sabbattha sabbesu pāramiṃ pariyosānaṃ gato pattoti sambandho. 
460656,107,2200,17,19,1,21,2,Sesaṃ vuttanayamevāti. 
460657,107,2201,2,4,1,40,2,Cūḷapanthakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
460658,107,2202,2,4,1,33,2,5 . Pilindavacchattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
460659,107,2203,2,9,1,69,5,Nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato pilindavacchattherassa apadānaṃ. 
460660,107,2203,10,54,1,418,44,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle haṃsavatīnagare mahābhogakule nibbatto heṭṭhā vuttanayena satthu santike dhammaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ devatānaṃ piyamanāpabhāvena aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthetvā yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā tato cuto devamanussesu saṃsaranto sumedhassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto. 
460661,107,2203,55,79,1,225,23,Parinibbute bhagavati tassa thūpaṃ pūjetvā saṅghassa mahādānaṃ pavattetvā tato cavitvā devamanussesu ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā anuppanne buddhe cakkavattī rājā hutvā mahājanaṃ pañcasīlesu patiṭṭhāpetvā saggaparāyanaṃ akāsi. 
460662,107,2203,80,92,1,95,11,"So anuppanneyeva amhākaṃ bhagavati sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbatti, pilindo tissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
460663,107,2203,93,96,1,15,2,{Vaccho}ti gottaṃ. 
460664,107,2203,97,102,1,41,4,So aparabhāge {pilindavaccho}ti paññāyittha. 
460665,107,2203,103,121,1,184,18,Saṃsāre pana saṃvegabahulatāya paribbājakapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā cūḷagandhāraṃ nāma vijjaṃ sādhetvā tāya vijjāya ākāsacārī paracittavidū ca hutvā rājagahe lābhaggayasaggapatto paṭivasati. 
460666,107,2204,2,10,1,69,8,Atha amhākaṃ bhagavā abhisambuddho hutvā anukkamena rājagahaṃ upagato. 
460667,107,2204,11,24,1,83,12,"Tato paṭṭhāya buddhānubhāvena tassa sā vijjā na sampajjati, attano kiccaṃ na sādheti. "
460668,107,2204,25,27,1,10,2,So cintesi–
460669,107,2204,28,74,1,322,36,"‘‘ sutaṃ kho panetaṃ ācariyapācariyānaṃ bhāsamānānaṃ‘ yattha mahāgandhāravijjā dharati , tattha cūḷagandhāravijjā na sampajjatī’ ti samaṇassa pana gotamassa āgatakālato paṭṭhāya nāyaṃ mama vijjā sampajjati, nissaṃsayaṃ samaṇo gotamo mahāgandhāravijjaṃ jānāti, yaṃnūnāhaṃ taṃ payirupāsitvā tassa santike taṃ vijjaṃ pariyāpuṇeyyan’’ ti. "
460670,107,2204,75,79,1,38,4,So bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā etadavoca–
460671,107,2204,80,98,1,77,11,"‘‘ ahaṃ, mahāsamaṇa, tava santike ekaṃ vijjaṃ pariyāpuṇitukāmo, okāsaṃ me karohī’’ ti."
460672,107,2204,99,110,1,37,7,‘‘ Tena hi mama santike pabbajāhī’’ ti āha. 
460673,107,2204,111,122,1,51,7,So‘‘ vijjāya parikammaṃ pabbajjā’’ ti maññamāno pabbaji. 
460674,107,2204,123,130,1,63,7,Tassa bhagavā dhammaṃ kathetvā caritānukūlaṃ kammaṭṭhānaṃ adāsi. 
460675,107,2204,131,138,1,77,7,So upanissayasampannatāya nacirasseva vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
460676,107,2205,2,24,1,148,18,"55. Yā pana purimajātiyaṃ tassovāde ṭhatvā sagge nibbattā devatā, tā kataññutaṃ nissāya tasmiṃ sañjātabahumānā sāyaṃ pātaṃ theraṃ payirupāsitvā gacchanti. "
460677,107,2205,25,61,1,166,18,"Tasmā naṃ bhagavā devatānaṃ ativiya piyamanāpabhāvena aggabhāve ṭhapesi‘‘ etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ devatānaṃ piyamanāpānaṃ yadidaṃ pilindavaccho’’ ti( a. ni.1.209,215). "
460678,107,2205,62,74,1,133,11,Evaṃ so pattaaggaṭṭhāno attano pubbakammaṃ anussaritvā pītisomanassavasena pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādimāha. 
460679,107,2206,2,8,1,52,5,Tattha kāmarūpārūpalokassa nātho padhānoti lokanātho. 
460680,107,2206,9,37,1,210,24,"Medhā vuccanti sabbaññutaññāṇaanāvaraṇañāṇādayo, sundarā, pasaṭṭhā vā medhā yassa so sumedho, aggo ca so puggalo cāti aggapuggalo, tasmiṃ sumedhe lokanāyake aggapuggale khandhaparinibbānena nibbute satīti sambandho. "
460681,107,2206,38,53,1,138,14,Pasannacitto {sumano}ti saddhāya pasāditacitto somanassena sundaramano ahaṃ tassa sumedhassa bhagavato thūpapūjaṃ cetiyapūjaṃ akāsinti attho. 
460682,107,2207,2,42,1,294,35,"56. Ye ca khīṇāsavā {tatthā}ti tasmiṃ samāgame ye ca khīṇāsavā pahīnakilesā chaḷabhiññā chahi abhiññāhi samannāgatā mahiddhikā mahantehi iddhīhi samannāgatā santi, te sabbe khīṇāsave ahaṃ tattha samānetvā suṭṭhu ādarena ānetvā saṅghabhattaṃ sakalasaṅghassa dātabbabhattaṃ akāsiṃ tesaṃ bhojesinti attho. "
460683,107,2208,2,21,1,126,15,57. Upaṭṭhāko tadā {ahū}ti tadā mama saṅghabhattadānakāle sumedhassa bhagavato nāmena sumedho nāma upaṭṭhākasāvako ahu ahosīti attho. 
460684,107,2208,22,31,1,77,9,So sāvako mayhaṃ pūjāsakkāraṃ anumodittha anumodito ānisaṃsaṃ kathesīti attho. 
460685,107,2209,2,24,1,159,16,"58. Tena {cittappasādenā}ti tena thūpapūjākaraṇavasena uppannena cittappasādena devaloke dibbavimānaṃ upapajjiṃ upagato asmīti attho, tattha nibbattomhīti vuttaṃ hoti. "
460686,107,2209,25,38,1,113,12,{Chaḷāsītisahassānī}ti tasmiṃ vimāne cha asītisahassāni devaccharāyo me mayhaṃ cittaṃ ramiṃsu ramāpesunti sambandho. 
460687,107,2210,2,23,1,157,17,59. Mameva {anuvattantī}ti tā accharāyo sabbakāmehi dibbehi rūpādivatthukāmehi upaṭṭhahantiyo mamaṃ eva anuvattanti mama vacanaṃ anukaronti sadā niccakālanti attho. 
460688,107,2210,24,26,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
460689,107,2211,2,4,1,41,2,Pilindavacchattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
460690,107,2212,2,4,1,26,2,6 . Rāhulattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
460691,107,2213,2,10,1,66,5,Padumuttarassa {bhagavato}tiādikaṃ āyasmato rāhulattherassa apadānaṃ. 
460692,107,2213,11,48,1,360,37,Ayampi āyasmā purimajinavaresu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā satthu dhammadesanaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ sikkhākāmānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā sayampi taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthento senāsanavisodhanavijjotanādikaṃ uḷāraṃ puññaṃ katvā paṇidhānaṃ akāsi. 
460693,107,2213,49,71,1,211,21,So tato cavitvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde amhākaṃ bodhisattaṃ paṭicca yasodharāya deviyā kucchimhi nibbattitvā {rāhulo}ti laddhanāmo mahatā khattiyaparivārena vaḍḍhi. 
460694,107,2213,72,81,1,42,4,Tassa pabbajjāvidhānaṃ khandhake( mahāva.105) āgatameva. 
460695,107,2213,82,94,1,116,12,So pabbajitvā satthu santike anekehi suttapadehi suladdhovādo paripakkañāṇo vipassanaṃ ussukkāpetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
460696,107,2213,95,103,1,66,8,Arahā pana hutvā attano paṭipattiṃ paccavekkhitvā aññaṃ byākaronto–
460697,107,2214,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Ubhayeneva sampanno, rāhulabhaddoti maṃ vidū; "
460698,107,2215,2,9,1,48,6,"Yañcamhi putto buddhassa, yañca dhammesu cakkhumā."
460699,107,2216,2,12,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Yañca me āsavā khīṇā, yañca natthi punabbhavo; "
460700,107,2217,2,7,1,39,4,"Arahā dakkhiṇeyyomhi, tevijjo amataddaso."
460701,107,2218,2,8,1,42,4,"‘ ‘ Kāmandhā jālapacchannā, taṇhāchadanachāditā; "
460702,107,2219,2,8,1,44,5,"Pamattabandhunā bandhā, macchāva kuminā mukhe."
460703,107,2220,2,11,1,47,7,"‘ ‘ Taṃ kāmaṃ ahamujjhitvā, chetvā mārassa bandhanaṃ; "
460704,107,2221,2,16,1,45,5,"Samūlaṃ taṇhamabbuyha, sītibhūtosmi nibbuto’’ ti.( theragā.295-298); "
460705,107,2222,2,5,1,20,3,Catasso gāthā abhāsi. 
460706,107,2222,6,16,1,99,8,Tattha ubhayeneva {sampanno}ti jātisampadā paṭipattisampadāti ubhayasampattiyāpi sampanno samannāgato. 
460707,107,2222,17,31,1,71,8,Rāhulabhaddoti maṃ {vidū}ti‘‘ rāhulabhaddo’’ ti maṃ sabrahmacārino sañjānanti. 
460708,107,2222,32,61,1,130,17,"Tassa hi jātasāsanaṃ sutvā bodhisattena,‘‘ rāhu, jāto, bandhanaṃ jātan’’ ti vuttavacanaṃ upādāya suddhodanamahārājā‘‘ rāhulo’’ ti nāmaṃ gaṇhi. "
460709,107,2222,62,68,1,49,6,Tattha ādito pitarā vuttapariyāyameva gahetvā āha–
460710,107,2222,69,77,1,26,4,‘‘ rāhulabhaddoti maṃ vidū’’ ti. 
460711,107,2222,78,81,1,26,2,{Bhaddo}ti pasaṃsāvacanameva. 
460712,107,2222,82,112,1,136,15,"Aparabhāge satthā taṃ sikkhākāmabhāvena aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapesi‘‘ etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ sikkhākāmānaṃ yadidaṃ rāhulo’’ ti( a. ni.1.209). "
460713,107,2223,2,17,1,131,11,68. Evaṃ so pattaetadaggaṭṭhāno attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttarassa {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
460714,107,2223,18,25,1,57,6,Sattabhūmimhi {pāsāde}ti pasādaṃ somanassaṃ janetīti pāsādo. 
460715,107,2223,26,38,1,88,11,"Uparūpari ṭhitā satta bhūmiyo yasmiṃ pāsāde soyaṃ sattabhūmi, tasmiṃ sattabhūmimhi pāsāde. "
460716,107,2223,39,55,1,128,15,"Ādāsaṃ santhariṃ ahan ti ādāsatalaṃ nipphādetvā lokajeṭṭhassa bhagavato tādino ahaṃ santharaṃ adāsiṃ, santharitvā pūjesinti attho. "
460717,107,2224,2,10,1,57,4,69. {Khīṇāsavasahassehī}ti arahantasahassehi parikiṇṇo parivuto. 
460718,107,2224,11,23,1,95,12,Dvipadindo dvipadānaṃ indo sāmi narāsabho mahāmuni gandhakuṭiṃ tehi saha upāgami pāvisīti attho. 
460719,107,2225,2,26,1,194,21,70. Virocento gandhakuṭin ti taṃ gandhakuṭiṃ sobhayamāno devānaṃ devo devadevo narānaṃ āsabho narāsabho jeṭṭho satthā bhikkhusaṅghamajjhe nisīditvā imā byākaraṇagāthāyo abhāsatha kathesīti sambandho. 
460720,107,2226,2,17,1,90,11,71. Yenāyaṃ jotitā {seyyā}ti yena upāsakena ayaṃ pāsādasaṅkhātā seyyā jotitā pabhāsitā pajjalitā. 
460721,107,2226,18,26,1,65,8,Ādāsova kaṃsalohamayaṃ ādāsatalaṃ iva suṭṭhu samaṃ katvā santhatā. 
460722,107,2226,27,33,1,51,6,Taṃ upāsakaṃ kittayissāmi pākaṭaṃ karissāmīti attho. 
460723,107,2226,34,36,1,20,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyameva. 
460724,107,2227,2,28,1,173,21,"81. Aṭṭhānametaṃ yaṃ {tādī}ti yaṃ yena kāraṇena tādī iṭṭhāniṭṭhesu akampiyasabhāvattā tādī agāre gharāvāse ratiṃ allīnabhāvaṃ ajjhagā pāpuṇi, etaṃ kāraṇaṃ aṭṭhānaṃ akāraṇanti attho. "
460725,107,2228,2,17,1,108,10,82. Nikkhamitvā {agārasmā}ti gharāvāsato nikkhamitvā taṃ tiṇadalamiva pariccajitvā subbato susikkhito pabbajissati. 
460726,107,2228,18,46,1,159,19,"Rāhulo nāma {nāmenā}ti suddhodanamahārājena pesitaṃ kumārassa jātasāsanaṃ sutvā pitarā siddhatthena,‘‘ rāhu jāto, bandhanaṃ jātan’’ ti vuttanāmattā rāhulo nāmāti attho."
460727,107,2228,47,78,1,196,21,"‘‘ Yathā candasūriyānaṃ vimānapabhāya kiliṭṭhakaraṇena rāhu asurindo upeti gacchati, evamevāyaṃ mama abhinikkhamanapabbajjādīnaṃ antarāyaṃ karontoriva jāto’’ ti adhippāyena,‘‘ rāhu jātoti āhā’’ ti daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
460728,107,2228,79,92,1,112,12,Arahā so {bhavissatī}ti so tādiso upanissayasampanno vipassanāyaṃ yuttappayutto arahā khīṇāsavo bhavissatīti attho. 
460729,107,2229,2,38,1,254,31,"83. Kikīva aṇḍaṃ {rakkheyyā}ti aṇḍaṃ bījaṃ rakkhamānā kikī sakuṇī iva appamatto sīlaṃ rakkheyya, cāmarī viya vāladhin ti vālaṃ rakkhamānā kaṇḍakesu vāle laggante bhindanabhayena anākaḍḍhitvā maramānā cāmarī viya jīvitampi pariccajitvā sīlaṃ abhinditvā rakkheyya. "
460730,107,2229,39,59,1,177,18,"Nipako {sīlasampanno}ti nepakkaṃ vuccati paññā, tena nepakkena samannāgato nipako khaṇḍachiddādibhāvaṃ apāpetvā rakkhaṇato sīlasampanno bhavissatīti evaṃ so bhagavā byākaraṇamakāsi. "
460731,107,2229,60,71,1,105,10,So evaṃ pattaarahattaphalo ekadivasaṃ vivekaṭṭhāne nisinno somanassavasena evaṃ rakkhiṃ {mahāmunī}tiādimāha. 
460732,107,2229,72,74,1,20,2,Taṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
460733,107,2230,2,4,1,34,2,Rāhulattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
460734,107,2231,2,4,1,40,2,7 . Upasenavaṅgantaputtattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
460735,107,2232,2,8,1,82,6,Padumuttaraṃ bhagavantan tiādikaṃ āyasmato upasenavaṅgantaputtattherassa apadānaṃ. 
460736,107,2232,9,61,1,477,50,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle haṃsavatīnagare kulagehe nibbattitvā vayappatto satthu santikaṃ gantvā dhammaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ samantapāsādikānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā satthu adhikārakammaṃ katvā taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthetvā yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde nālakagāme rūpasārī brāhmaṇiyā kucchimhi nibbatti, upaseno tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
460737,107,2232,62,92,1,219,26,So vayappatto tayo vede uggaṇhitvā satthu santike dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā upasampadāya ekavassiko‘‘ ariyagabbhaṃ vaḍḍhemī’’ ti ekaṃ kulaputtaṃ attano santike upasampādetvā tena saddhiṃ satthu santikaṃ gato. 
460738,107,2232,93,145,1,285,34,"Satthārā cassa tassa avassikassa bhikkhuno saddhivihārikabhāvaṃ sutvā‘‘ atilahuṃ kho tvaṃ, moghapurisa, bāhullāya āvatto’’ ti( mahāva.75) garahito‘‘ idānāhaṃ yadi parisaṃ nissāya satthārā garahito, parisaṃyeva pana nissāya satthu pasādaṃ karissāmī’’ ti vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
460739,107,2232,146,165,1,146,17,"Arahā pana hutvā sayampi sabbe dhutaṅgadhamme samādāya vattati, aññepi tadatthāya samādapesi, tena naṃ bhagavā samantapāsādikānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapesi. "
460740,107,2232,166,205,1,268,33,"So aparena samayena kosambiyaṃ kalahe uppanne bhikkhusaṅghe ca dvidhābhūte ekena bhikkhunā taṃ kalahaṃ parivajjitukāmena‘‘ etarahi kho kalaho uppanno, bhikkhusaṅgho ca dvidhābhūto, kathaṃ nu kho mayā paṭipajjitabban’’ ti puṭṭho vivekavāsato paṭṭhāya tassa paṭipattiṃ kathesi. "
460741,107,2232,206,217,1,95,11,Evaṃ thero tassa bhikkhuno ovādadānāpadesena attano tathā paṭipannabhāvaṃ dīpento aññaṃ byākāsi. 
460742,107,2233,2,17,1,135,12,86. So evaṃ pattaetadaggaṭṭhāno attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassavasena pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttaraṃ bhagavantan tiādimāha. 
460743,107,2233,18,37,1,185,19,Pabbhāramhi nisīdantan ti purato bhāraṃ namitaṃ onamitanti pabbhāraṃ vivekakāmaṃ vanamajjhe sayaṃjātapabbatapabbhāre nisinnaṃ naruttamaṃ bhagavantaṃ ahaṃ upagacchiṃ samīpaṃ gatoti attho. 
460744,107,2234,2,15,1,83,9,87. Kaṇikārapuppha {disvā}ti tathā upagacchanto tasmiṃ padese supupphitaṃ kaṇikāraṃ disvā. 
460745,107,2234,16,29,1,104,12,Vaṇṭe chetvānahaṃ {tadā}ti tasmiṃ tathāgatassa diṭṭhakāle taṃ pupphaṃ vaṇṭe vaṇṭasmiṃ chetvāna chinditvāna. 
460746,107,2234,30,37,1,54,6,Alaṅkaritvā {chattamhī}ti tena pupphena chattaṃ chādetvā. 
460747,107,2234,38,47,1,78,9,Buddhassa abhiropayin ti pabbhāre nisinnassa buddhassa muddhani akāsinti attho. 
460748,107,2235,2,17,1,99,11,88. Piṇḍapātañca pādāsin ti tasmiṃyeva nisinnassa bhagavato piṇḍapātaṃ pakārena adāsiṃ bhojesinti attho. 
460749,107,2235,18,24,1,71,6,Paramannaṃ subhojanan ti sundarabhojanasaṅkhātaṃ paramannaṃ uttamāhāraṃ. 
460750,107,2235,25,40,1,123,14,Buddhena navame {tatthā}ti tasmiṃ vivekaṭṭhāne buddhena saha navame aṭṭha samaṇe samitapāpe khīṇāsavabhikkhū bhojesinti attho. 
460751,107,2236,2,14,1,123,11,Yaṃ vadanti {sumedho}ti yaṃ gotamasammāsambuddhaṃ bhūripaññaṃ pathavisamānaṃ paññaṃ sumedhaṃ sundaraṃ sabbaññutādipaññavantaṃ. 
460752,107,2236,15,30,1,123,15,Sumedho iti sundarapañño iti vadanti paṇḍitā ito kappato satasahasse kappe eso gotamo sammāsambuddho bhavissatīti sambandho. 
460753,107,2236,31,33,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
460754,107,2237,2,4,1,48,2,Upasenavaṅgantaputtattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
460755,107,2238,2,4,1,30,2,8 . Raṭṭhapālattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
460756,107,2239,2,10,1,70,5,Padumuttarassa {bhagavato}tiādikaṃ āyasmato raṭṭhapālattherassa apadānaṃ. 
460757,107,2239,11,63,1,485,47,"Ayampāyasmā purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato uppattito puretarameva haṃsavatīnagare gahapatimahāsālakule nibbattitvā vayappatto pitu accayena gharāvāse patiṭṭhito ratanakoṭṭhāgārakammikena dassitaṃ aparimāṇaṃ vaṃsānugataṃ dhanaṃ disvā‘‘ imaṃ ettakaṃ dhanarāsiṃ mayhaṃ pituayyakapayyakādayo attanā saddhiṃ gahetvā gantuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu, mayā pana gahetvā gantuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā kapaṇaddhikādīnaṃ mahādānaṃ adāsi. "
460758,107,2239,64,95,1,278,31,So abhiññālābhiṃ ekaṃ tāpasaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tena devalokādhipacce niyojito yāvajīvaṃ puññāni katvā tato cuto devaloke nibbattitvā dibbasampattiṃ anubhavanto tattha yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cuto manussaloke bhinnaṃ raṭṭhaṃ sandhāretuṃ samatthassa kulassa ekaputtako hutvā nibbatti. 
460759,107,2239,96,107,1,139,11,Tena samayena padumuttaro bhagavā loke uppajjitvā pavattitavaradhammacakko veneyyasatte nibbānamahānagarasaṅkhātaṃ khemantabhūmiṃ sampāpesi. 
460760,107,2239,108,126,1,156,18,Atha so kulaputto anukkamena viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ upāsakehi saddhiṃ vihāraṃ gantvā satthāraṃ dhammaṃ desentaṃ disvā pasannacitto parisapariyante nisīdi. 
460761,107,2240,2,13,1,81,10,Tena kho pana samayena satthā ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ saddhāpabbajitānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapesi. 
460762,107,2240,14,26,1,111,12,So taṃ disvā pasannamānaso satasahassabhikkhuparivutassa bhagavato sattāhaṃ mahādānaṃ datvā taṃ ṭhānaṃ patthesi. 
460763,107,2240,27,46,1,141,15,Satthā anantarāyena samijjhanabhāvaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ anāgate gotamassa nāma sammāsambuddhassa sāsane saddhāpabbajitānaṃ aggo bhavissatī’’ ti byākāsi. 
460764,107,2240,47,53,1,58,6,So satthāraṃ bhikkhusaṅghañca vanditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi. 
460765,107,2240,54,78,1,210,24,So yāvatāyukaṃ puññāni katvā tato cavitvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto ito dvenavute kappe phussassa bhagavato kāle satthu vemātikesu tīsu rājaputtesu satthāraṃ upaṭṭhahantesu tesaṃ puññakiriyāsu sahāyakiccaṃ akāsi. 
460766,107,2240,79,107,1,258,26,"Evaṃ tattha tattha bhave bahuṃ kusalaṃ upacinitvā sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kururaṭṭhe thullakoṭṭhikanigame raṭṭhapālaseṭṭhino gehe nibbatti, tassa bhinnaṃ raṭṭhaṃ sandhāretuṃ samatthakule nibbattattā {raṭṭhapālo}ti vaṃsānugatameva nāmaṃ ahosi. "
460767,107,2240,108,125,1,165,16,So mahatā parivārena vaḍḍhanto anukkamena yobbanappatto mātāpitūhi patirūpena dārena saṃyojito mahante ca yase patiṭṭhāpito dibbasampattisadisasampattiṃ paccanubhoti. 
460768,107,2241,2,10,1,73,7,Atha bhagavā kururaṭṭhe janapadacārikaṃ caranto thullakoṭṭhikaṃ anupāpuṇi. 
460769,107,2241,11,46,1,346,35,Taṃ sutvā raṭṭhapālo kulaputto satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā satthu santike dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitukāmo sattāhaṃ bhattacchedaṃ katvā kicchena kasirena mātāpitaro anujānāpetvā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā pabbajjaṃ yācitvā satthu āṇattiyā aññatarassa santike pabbajitvā yonisomanasikārena kammaṃ karonto vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
460770,107,2241,47,117,1,514,54,"Arahattaṃ pana patvā satthāraṃ anujānāpetvā mātāpitaro passituṃ thullakoṭṭhikaṃ gantvā tattha sapadānaṃ piṇḍāya caranto pitu nivesane ābhidosikaṃ kummāsaṃ labhitvā taṃ amataṃ viya paribhuñjanto pitarā nimantito svātanāya adhivāsetvā dutiyadivase pitu nivesane piṇḍapātaṃ paribhuñjitvā alaṅkatapaṭiyatte itthāgārajane upagantvā‘‘ kīdisā nāma tā, ayyaputta, accharāyo, yāsaṃ tvaṃ hetu brahmacariyaṃ carasī’’ tiādīni( ma. ni.2.301) vatvā palobhanakammaṃ kātuṃ āraddhe tassādhippāyaṃ viparivattetvā aniccatādipaṭisaṃyuttaṃ dhammaṃ kathento–"
460771,107,2242,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Passa cittakataṃ bimbaṃ, arukāyaṃ samussitaṃ; "
460772,107,2243,2,9,1,46,6,"Āturaṃ bahusaṅkappaṃ, yassa natthi dhuvaṃ ṭhiti."
