460792,107,2258,2,10,1,62,7,"Luddhā dhanaṃ sannicayaṃ karonti, bhiyyova kāme abhipatthayanti."
460793,107,2259,2,10,1,56,6,"‘ ‘ Rājā pasayhappathaviṃ vijetvā, sasāgarantaṃ mahimāvasanto; "
