460796,107,2262,2,12,1,58,9,"Ūnāva hutvāna jahanti dehaṃ, kāmehi lokamhi na hatthi titti."
460797,107,2263,2,19,1,57,12,"‘ ‘ Kandanti naṃ ñātī pakiriya kese,‘ aho vatā no amarā’ ti cāhu; "
460798,107,2264,2,11,1,59,8,"Vatthena naṃ pārutaṃ nīharitvā, citaṃ samodhāya tato ḍahanti."
