460800,107,2266,2,13,1,57,10,"Na mīyamānassa bhavanti tāṇā, ñātī ca mittā atha vā sahāyā."
460801,107,2267,2,15,1,61,10,"‘ ‘ Dāyādakā tassa dhanaṃ haranti, satto pana gacchati yena kammaṃ; "
460802,107,2268,2,13,1,65,10,"Na mīyamānaṃ dhanamanveti kiñci, puttā ca dārā ca dhanañca raṭṭhaṃ."
460803,107,2269,2,14,1,59,10,"‘ ‘ Na dīghamāyuṃ labhate dhanena, na cāpi vittena jaraṃ vihanti; "
460804,107,2270,2,9,1,57,6,"Appaṃ hidaṃ jīvitamāhu dhīrā, asassataṃ vippariṇāmadhammaṃ."
460805,107,2271,2,17,1,66,12,"‘ ‘ Aḍḍhā daliddā ca phusanti phassaṃ, bālo ca dhīro ca tatheva phuṭṭho; "
460806,107,2272,2,13,1,62,10,"Bālo hi bālyā vadhitova seti, dhīro ca no vedhati phassaphuṭṭho."
460807,107,2273,2,12,1,58,8,"‘ ‘ Tasmā hi paññāva dhanena seyyā, yāya vosānamidhādhigacchati; "
460808,107,2274,2,10,1,54,7,"Abyositattā hi bhavābhavesu, pāpāni kammāni karoti mohā."
460809,107,2275,2,10,1,55,6,"‘ ‘ Upeti gabbhañca parañca lokaṃ, saṃsāramāpajjaparamparāya; "
