460812,107,2278,2,11,1,57,8,"Evaṃ pajā pecca paramhi loke, sakammunā haññati pāpadhammo."
460813,107,2279,2,13,1,59,9,"‘ ‘ Kāmā hi citrā madhurā manoramā, virūparūpena mathenti cittaṃ; "
460814,107,2280,2,10,1,54,7,"Ādīnavaṃ kāmaguṇesu disvā, tasmā ahaṃ pabbajitomhi rāja."
