460827,107,2293,2,5,1,15,3,Imā gāthā avoca. 
460828,107,2293,6,15,1,67,9,Evaṃ thero rañño korabyassa dhammaṃ desetvā satthu santikameva gato. 
460829,107,2293,16,25,1,89,9,Satthā ca aparabhāge ariyagaṇamajjhe nisinno theraṃ saddhāpabbajitānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapesi. 
460830,107,2294,2,4,1,0,0,97-8. 
460831,107,2294,5,18,1,130,11,Evaṃ so thero pattaetadaggaṭṭhāno pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttarassa {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
460832,107,2294,19,36,1,134,16,Varanāgo mayā {dinno}ti tassa bhagavato rūpakāye pasīditvā varo uttamo seṭṭho īsādanto rathīsāsadisadanto urūḷhavā bhāravaho rājāraho vā. 
460833,107,2294,37,43,1,79,5,{Setacchattopasobhito}ti hatthikkhandhe ussāpitasetacchattena upasevito sobhamāno. 
460834,107,2294,44,48,1,28,4,Punapi kiṃ visiṭṭho varanāgo? 
460835,107,2294,49,51,1,29,2,Sakappano hatthālaṅkārasahito. 
460836,107,2294,52,60,1,91,8,Saṅghārāmaṃ buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa vasanatthāya ārāmaṃ vihāraṃ akārayiṃ kāresiṃ. 
460837,107,2295,2,17,1,117,11,99. {Catupaññāsasahassānī}ti tasmiṃ kārāpite vihārabbhantare catupaññāsasahassāni pāsādāni ca ahaṃ akārayiṃ kāresinti attho. 
460838,107,2295,18,29,1,116,10,Mahoghadānaṃ {karitvānā}ti sabbaparikkhārasahitaṃ mahoghasadisaṃ mahādānaṃ sajjetvā mahesino munino niyyādesinti attho. 
460839,107,2296,2,24,1,203,18,100. Anumodi {mahāvīro}ti caturāsaṅkhyeyyasatasahassesu kappesu abbocchinnaussāhasaṅkhātena vīriyena mahāvīro sayambhū sayameva bhūto jāto laddhasabbaññutaññāṇo aggo seṭṭho puggalo anumodi vihārānumodanaṃ akāsi. 
460840,107,2296,25,44,1,184,17,Sabbe jane {hāsayanto}ti sakalānantāparimāṇe devamanusse hāsayanto santuṭṭhe kurumāno amatanibbānapaṭisaṃyuttaṃ catusaccadhammadesanaṃ desesi pakāsesi vivari vibhaji uttānī akāsīti attho. 
