460845,107,2297,49,68,1,137,17,"Sabbasattānaṃ nāyako uttamoti nāyako, sambhāravante satte nibbānaṃ neti pāpetīti vā nāyako, jalanuttamo ca so nāyako cāti jalanuttamanāyako. "
