460849,107,2299,2,4,1,26,2,9 . Sopākattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
460850,107,2300,2,8,1,65,5,Pabbhāraṃ {sodhayantassā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato sopākattherassa apadānaṃ. 
460851,107,2300,9,27,1,166,17,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle aññatarassa kuṭumbikassa putto hutvā nibbatti. 
460852,107,2300,28,39,1,98,10,"Ekadivasaṃ satthāraṃ disvā bījapūraphalāni satthu upanesi, paribhuñji bhagavā tassānukampaṃ upādāya. "
460853,107,2300,40,54,1,135,14,So bhikkhu satthari saṅghe ca abhippasanno salākabhattaṃ paṭṭhapetvā saṅghuddesavasena tiṇṇaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ yāvatāyukaṃ khīrabhattaṃ adāsi. 
460854,107,2300,55,69,1,136,14,So tehi puññehi aparāparaṃ devamanussesu sampattiyo anubhavanto ekadā manussayoniyaṃ nibbatto ekassa paccekabuddhassa khīrabhattaṃ adāsi. 
460855,107,2301,2,18,1,166,16,Evaṃ tattha tattha puññāni katvā sugatīsuyeva paribbhamanto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde purimakammanissandena sāvatthiyaṃ aññatarāya duggatitthiyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
460856,107,2301,19,35,1,132,16,Sā taṃ dasamāse kucchinā pariharitvā paripakke gabbhe vijāyanakāle vijāyituṃ asakkontī mucchaṃ āpajjitvā bahuvelaṃ matā viya nipajji. 
460857,107,2301,36,55,1,116,14,Ñātakā‘‘ matā’’ ti saññāya susānaṃ netvā citakaṃ āropetvā devatānubhāvena vātavuṭṭhiyā uṭṭhitāya aggiṃ adatvā pakkamiṃsu. 
460858,107,2301,56,63,1,77,7,Dārako pacchimabhavikattā devatānubhāveneva arogo hutvā mātukucchito nikkhami. 
460859,107,2301,64,67,1,20,3,Mātā pana kālamakāsi. 
460860,107,2301,68,80,1,111,12,Devatā manussarūpenupagamma taṃ gahetvā susānagopakassa gehe ṭhapetvā katipāhaṃ kālaṃ patirūpena āhārena posesi. 
460861,107,2301,81,88,1,52,7,Tato paraṃ susānagopako attano puttaṃ katvā vaḍḍhesi. 
460862,107,2301,89,101,1,79,11,So tathā vaḍḍhento tassa puttena suppiyena nāma dārakena saddhiṃ kīḷanto vicari. 
460863,107,2301,102,109,1,56,6,Tassa susāne jātasaṃvaḍḍhabhāvato {sopāko}ti samaññā ahosi. 
460864,107,2302,2,16,1,151,14,Athekadivasaṃ sattavassikaṃ taṃ bhagavā paccūsavelāyaṃ ñāṇajālaṃ pattharitvā veneyyabandhave olokento ñāṇajālassa antogataṃ disvā susānaṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
460865,107,2302,17,25,1,84,8,Dārako pubbahetunā codiyamāno pasannamānaso satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā aṭṭhāsi. 
460866,107,2302,26,30,1,28,4,Satthā tassa dhammaṃ kathesi. 
460867,107,2302,31,48,1,91,13,So dhammaṃ sutvā pabbajjaṃ yācitvā pitarā‘‘ anuññātosī’’ ti vutto pitaraṃ satthu santikaṃ ānesi. 
460868,107,2302,49,70,1,118,15,"Tassa pitā satthāraṃ vanditvā‘‘ imaṃ dārakaṃ pabbājetha, bhante’’ ti anujāni, taṃ pabbājetvā bhagavā mettābhāvanāya niyojesi. "
460869,107,2302,71,84,1,125,13,So mettākammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā susāne viharanto nacirasseva mettājhānaṃ pādakaṃ katvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ sacchākāsi. 
460870,107,2302,85,105,1,106,11,Arahā hutvāpi aññesaṃ sosānikabhikkhūnaṃ mettābhāvanāvidhiṃ dassento‘‘ yathāpi ekaputtasmin’’ ti( theragā.33) gāthaṃ abhāsi. 
460871,107,2302,106,215,1,544,69,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yathā ekaputtake piye manāpe mātā pitā ca kusalī ekantahitesī bhaveyya, evaṃ puratthimādibhedāsu sabbāsu disāsu kāmabhavādibhedesu vā sabbesu bhavesu daharādibhedāsu sabbāsu avatthāsupi ṭhitesu sabbesu sattesu ekantahitesitāya kusalī bhaveyya‘‘ mitto, udāsino, paccatthiko’’ ti sīmaṃ akatvā sīmāya sambhedavasena sabbattha ekarasaṃ mettaṃ bhāveyyāti imaṃ pana gāthaṃ vatvā‘‘ sace tumhe āyasmanto evaṃ mettaṃ bhāveyyātha, ye te bhagavatā‘ sukhaṃ supatī’ tiādinā( a. ni.11.15; pari.331; mi. pa.4.4.6) ekādasa mettānisaṃsā ca vuttā, ekaṃsena tesaṃ bhāgino bhavathā’’ ti ovādaṃ adāsi. "
460872,107,2303,2,18,1,136,11,112. Evaṃ so pattaphalādhigamo attano katapuññaṃ paccavekkhitvā sañjātasomanasso pubbacaritāpadānaṃ dassento pabbhāraṃ {sodhayantassā}tiādimāha. 
460873,107,2303,19,49,1,252,27,"Tattha pabbhāran ti silāpabbatassa vivekaṭṭhānaṃ, taṃ pabbajitānurūpattā iṭṭhakapākāraṃ katvā dvārakavāṭaṃ yojetvā bhikkhūnaṃ vasanatthāya adāsi, pakārena bharo patthetabboti pabbhāro, taṃ sodhayantassa mama santikaṃ siddhattho nāma bhagavā āgacchi pāpuṇi. "
460874,107,2304,2,30,1,248,24,113. Buddhaṃ upagataṃ {disvā}ti evaṃ mama santikaṃ āgataṃ disvā tādino iṭṭhāniṭṭhesu akampiyasabhāvattā tādiguṇayuttassa lokajeṭṭhassa buddhassa santharaṃ tiṇapaṇṇādisantharaṃ kaṭṭhattharaṃ paññāpetvā niṭṭhāpetvā pupphāsanaṃ pupphamayaṃ āsanaṃ ahaṃ adāsiṃ. 
460875,107,2305,2,16,1,89,9,114. Pupphāsane {nisīditvā}ti tasmiṃ paññatte pupphāsane nisīditvā lokanāyako siddhattho bhagavā. 
460876,107,2305,17,30,1,110,12,Mamañca {gatimaññāyā}ti mayhaṃ gatiṃ āyatiṃ uppattiṭṭhānaṃ aññāya jānitvā aniccataṃ aniccabhāvaṃ udāhari kathesi. 
460877,107,2306,2,21,1,134,15,115. Aniccā vata {saṅkhārā}ti vata ekantena saṅkhārā paccayehi samecca samāgantvā karīyamānā sabbe sappaccayadhammā hutvā abhāvaṭṭhena aniccā. 
460878,107,2306,22,33,1,116,10,{Uppādavayadhammino}ti uppajjitvā vinassanasabhāvā uppajjitvā pātubhavitvā ete saṅkhārā nirujjhanti vinassantīti attho. 
460879,107,2306,34,49,1,116,13,"Tesaṃ vūpasamo {sukho}ti tesaṃ saṅkhārānaṃ visesena upasamo sukho, tesaṃ vūpasamakaraṃ nibbānameva ekantasukhanti attho. "
460880,107,2307,2,32,1,221,25,116. Idaṃ vatvāna {sabbaññū}ti sabbadhammajānanako bhagavā lokānaṃ jeṭṭho vuḍḍho narānaṃ āsabho padhāno vīro idaṃ aniccapaṭisaṃyuttaṃ dhammadesanaṃ vatvāna kathetvā ambare ākāse haṃsarājā iva nabhaṃ ākāsaṃ abbhuggamīti sambandho. 
460881,107,2308,2,14,1,70,9,117. Sakaṃ diṭṭhiṃ attano laddhiṃ khantiṃ ruciṃ ajjhāsayaṃ jahitvāna pahāya. 
460882,107,2308,15,25,1,92,10,Bhāvayāniccasaññahan ti anicce aniccanti pavattasaññaṃ ahaṃ bhāvayiṃ vaḍḍhesiṃ manasi akāsiṃ. 
460883,107,2308,26,40,1,80,14,Tattha kālaṃ kato ahan ti tattha tissaṃ jātiyaṃ tato jātito ahaṃ kālaṃ kato mato. 
460884,107,2309,2,14,1,88,7,118. Dve sampattī {anubhotvā}ti manussasampattidibbasampattisaṅkhātā dve sampattiyo anubhavitvā. 
460885,107,2309,15,25,1,80,8,"Sukkamūlena {codito}ti purāṇakusalamūlena, mūlabhūtena kusalena vā codito sañcodito. "
460886,107,2309,26,34,1,60,7,Pacchime bhave {sampatte}ti pariyosāne bhave sampatte pāpuṇite. 
