461059,107,2351,2,8,1,71,5,Nagare {bandhumatiyā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato tisaraṇagamaniyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461060,107,2351,9,26,1,181,17,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle bandhumatīnagare kulagehe nibbattitvā andhamātāpitaro upaṭṭhāsi. 
461061,107,2351,27,30,1,21,3,So ekadivasaṃ cintesi–
461062,107,2351,31,62,1,195,23,"‘‘ ahaṃ mātāpitaro upaṭṭhahanto pabbajituṃ na labhāmi, yaṃnūnāhaṃ tīṇi saraṇāni gaṇhissāmi , evaṃ duggatito mocessāmī’’ ti nisabhaṃ nāma vipassissa bhagavato aggasāvakaṃ upasaṅkamitvā tīṇi saraṇāni gaṇhi. "
461063,107,2351,63,91,1,272,27,"So tāni vassasatasahassāni rakkhitvā teneva kammena tāvatiṃsabhavane nibbatto, tato paraṃ devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthinagare mahāsālakule nibbatto viññutaṃ patto sattavassikova dārakehi parivuto ekaṃ saṅghārāmaṃ agamāsi. "
