461108,107,2368,80,102,1,234,20,"Siddho paripuṇṇo sabbaññutaññāṇādiguṇasaṅkhāto attho payojanaṃ yassa bhagavato soyaṃ siddhattho, tassa siddhatthassa bhagavato bhagyādiguṇavantassa lokajeṭṭhassa sakalalokuttamassa tādino iṭṭhāniṭṭhesu tādisassa acalasabhāvassāti attho. "
