461164,107,2388,9,37,1,274,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vayappatto sāsane abhippasanno ratanattayamāmako vipassissa bhagavato santike dhammaṃ sutvā pasannamānaso khomadussena pūjaṃ akāsi. 
461165,107,2388,38,48,1,68,10,So tadeva mūlaṃ katvā yāvajīvaṃ puññāni katvā tato devaloke nibbatto. 
