461258,107,2407,247,263,1,151,14,Yasmā ayaṃ thero rājānaṃ upatthambhaṃ labhitvā sappāyāhārapaṭilābhena samāhitacitto vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto upanissayasampannatāya chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
461259,107,2407,264,288,1,133,19,"Evaṃbhūtassāpi imassa therassa guṇe ajānantā ye puthujjanā bhikkhū‘‘ ayaṃ paṭhamaṃ salākaṃ gaṇhati, kiṃ nu kho etan’’ ti vimatiṃ uppādenti. "
461260,107,2407,289,309,1,142,16,Tesaṃ taṃ vimatividhamanatthaṃ thero ākāsaṃ abbhuggantvā iddhipāṭihāriyaṃ dassetvā aññāpadesena aññaṃ byākaronto‘‘ pañca chinde’’ ti gāthaṃ abhāsi. 
461261,107,2408,2,20,1,172,15,1. Evaṃ so pūritapuññasambhārānurūpena arahā hutvā pattaetadaggaṭṭhāno attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassavasena pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento sattāhaṃ paṭisallīnan tiādimāha. 
461262,107,2408,21,28,1,88,7,Tattha satthāhaṃ sattadivasaṃ nirodhasamāpattivihārena paṭisallīnaṃ vivekabhūtanti attho. 
