461265,107,2410,2,4,1,26,2,2 . Sāgatattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461266,107,2411,2,9,1,61,6,Sobhito nāma {nāmenā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato sāgatattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461267,107,2411,10,43,1,344,32,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbatto sabbasippesu nipphattiṃ patto nāmena sobhito nāma hutvā tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ padako veyyākaraṇo lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo. 
461268,107,2411,44,61,1,185,17,So ekadivasaṃ padumuttaraṃ bhagavantaṃ dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇasiriyā sobhamānaṃ uyyānadvārena gacchantaṃ disvā atīva pasannamānaso anekehi upāyehi anekehi guṇavaṇṇehi thomanaṃ akāsi. 
461269,107,2411,62,81,1,113,15,Bhagavā tassa thomanaṃ sutvā‘‘ anāgate gotamassa bhagavato sāsane sāgato nāma sāvako bhavissatī’’ ti byākaraṇaṃ adāsi. 
461270,107,2411,82,93,1,79,11,So tato paṭṭhāya puññāni karonto yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cuto devaloke nibbatto. 
461271,107,2411,94,102,1,104,8,Kappasatasahassadevamanussesu ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto. 
461272,107,2411,103,114,1,75,9,Tassa mātāpitaro somanassaṃ vaḍḍhento sujāto āgatoti {sāgato}ti nāmaṃ kariṃsu. 
461273,107,2411,115,123,1,67,8,So sāsane pasīditvā pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ patto. 
461274,107,2412,2,20,1,147,13,17. Evaṃ so puññasambhārānurūpena pattaarahattaphalo attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento sobhito nāma {nāmenā}tiādimāha. 
461275,107,2412,21,31,1,93,10,Tattha tadā puññasambhārassa paripūraṇasamaye nāmena sobhito nāma brāhmaṇo ahosinti sambandho. 
461276,107,2413,2,15,1,75,8,"21. Vipathā {uddharitvānā}ti viruddhapathā kumaggā, uppathā vā uddharitvā apanetvā. "
461277,107,2413,16,34,1,140,15,"Pathaṃ {ācikkhase}ti, bhante, sabbaññu tuvaṃ pathaṃ sappurisamaggaṃ nibbānādhigamanupāyaṃ ācikkhase kathesi desesi vibhaji uttāniṃ akāsīti attho. "
