461280,107,2415,2,4,1,31,2,3 . Mahākaccānattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461281,107,2416,2,7,1,62,4,{Padumuttaranāthassā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato kaccānattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461282,107,2416,8,65,1,548,56,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle gahapatimahāsālakulagehe nibbattetvā vuddhippatto ekadivasaṃ satthu santike dhammaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ saṃkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajantānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā sayampi taṃ ṭhānantaraṃ patthento dānādīni puññāni katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto sumedhassa bhagavato kāle vijjādharo hutvā ākāsena gacchanto satthāraṃ ekasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe nisinnaṃ disvā pasannamānaso kaṇikārapupphehi pūjaṃ akāsi. 
461283,107,2417,2,33,1,298,27,So tena puññakammena aparāparaṃ sugatīsuyeva parivattetvā kassapadasabalassa kāle bārāṇasiyaṃ kulaghare nibbattitvā parinibbute bhagavati suvaṇṇacetiyakaraṇaṭṭhānaṃ dasasahassagghanikāya suvaṇṇiṭṭhakāya pūjaṃ katvā‘‘ bhagavā mayhaṃ nibbattanibbattaṭṭhāne sarīraṃ suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ hotū’’ ti pattharaṃ akāsi. 
461284,107,2417,34,71,1,275,31,"Tato yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā ekaṃ buddhantaraṃ devamanussesu saṃsaritvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ujjeniyaṃ rañño caṇḍapajjotassa purohitassa gehe nibbatti, tassa nāmaggahaṇadivase mātāpitaro‘‘ amhākaṃ putto suvaṇṇavaṇṇo attano nāmaṃ gahetvā āgato’’ ti kañcanamāṇavo tveva nāmaṃ kariṃsu. "
461285,107,2417,72,81,1,73,9,So vuddhimanvāya tayo vede uggaṇhitvā pitu accayena purohitaṭṭhānaṃ labhi. 
461286,107,2417,82,87,1,36,4,So gottavasena {kaccāno}ti paññāyittha. 
461287,107,2418,2,21,1,92,12,"Rājā caṇḍapajjoto buddhuppādaṃ sutvā,‘‘ ācariya, tvaṃ tattha gantvā satthāraṃ idhānehī’’ ti pesesi. "
461288,107,2418,22,27,1,37,5,So attaṭṭhamo satthu santikaṃ upagato. 
461289,107,2418,28,32,1,27,4,Tassa satthā dhammaṃ desesi. 
461290,107,2418,33,41,1,81,8,Desanāpariyosāne so sattahi janehi saddhiṃ sahapaṭisambhidāhi arahatte patiṭṭhāsi. 
461291,107,2418,42,54,1,46,7,"Atha satthā‘‘ etha, bhikkhavo’’ ti hatthaṃ pasāresi. "
461292,107,2418,55,62,1,94,7,Te tāvadeva dvaṅgulamattakesamassukā iddhimayapattacīvaradharā vassasaṭṭhikattherā viya ahesuṃ. 
461293,107,2418,63,85,1,117,16,"Evaṃ thero sadatthaṃ nipphādetvā,‘‘ bhante, rājā pajjoto tumhākaṃ pāde vandituṃ dhammañca sotuṃ icchatī’’ ti satthu ārocesi. "
461294,107,2418,86,102,1,73,11,"Satthā‘‘ tvaṃyeva bhikkhu tattha gaccha, tayi gatepi rājā pasīdissatī’’ ti āha. "
461295,107,2418,103,116,1,108,13,Thero attaṭṭhamo tattha gantvā rājānaṃ pasādetvā avantīsu sāsanaṃ patiṭṭhāpetvā puna satthu santikameva gato. 
461296,107,2419,2,46,1,246,23,"31. Evaṃ so pattaarahattaphalo‘‘ etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṃ saṃkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajantānaṃ yadidaṃ mahākaccāno’’ ti( a. ni.1.188,197) etadaggaṭṭhānaṃ patvā attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento {padumuttaranāthassā}tiādimāha. "
461297,107,2419,47,90,1,339,34,"Tattha padumaṃ nāma cetiyan ti padumehi chāditattā vā padumākārehi katattā vā bhagavato vasanagandhakuṭivihārova pūjanīyabhāvena cetiyaṃ, yathā‘‘ gotamakacetiyaṃ, āḷavakacetiyan’’ ti vutte tesaṃ yakkhānaṃ nivasanaṭṭhānaṃ pūjanīyaṭṭhānattā cetiyanti vuccati, evamidaṃ bhagavato vasanaṭṭhānaṃ cetiyanti vuccati, na dhātunidhāyakacetiyanti veditabbaṃ. "
461298,107,2419,91,99,1,72,8,Na hi aparinibbutassa bhagavato sarīradhātūnaṃ abhāvā dhātucetiyaṃ akari. 
461299,107,2419,100,111,1,111,10,Silāsanaṃ {kārayitvā}ti tassā padumanāmikāya gandhakuṭiyā pupphādhāratthāya heṭṭhā phalikamayaṃ silāsanaṃ kāretvā. 
461300,107,2419,112,121,1,93,9,Suvaṇṇenābhilepayin ti taṃ silāsanaṃ jambonadasuvaṇṇena abhivisesena lepayiṃ chādesinti attho. 
461301,107,2420,2,19,1,134,13,32. Ratanāmayaṃ sattahi ratanehi kataṃ chattaṃ paggayha muddhani dhāretvā vāḷabījaniñca setapavaracāmariñca paggayha buddhassa abhiropayiṃ. 
