461324,107,2426,55,100,1,271,33,"So pana gacchanto‘‘ sacāhaṃ, deva, pabbajituṃ labhissāmi, evāhaṃ bhagavantaṃ idhānessāmī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ yaṃ kiñci katvā mama puttaṃ dassehī’’ ti vutto rājagahaṃ gantvā satthu dhammadesanavelāyaṃ parisapariyante ṭhito dhammaṃ sutvā saparivāro arahattaṃ patvā ehibhikkhubhāve patiṭṭhāsi. "
