461420,107,2467,60,87,1,260,25,Evaṃ so yāvajīvaṃ puññāni katvā teneva puññabalena devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiṃ anubhavitvā kamena imasmiṃ buddhuppāde uppanno paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ patto pubbakammavasena {lasuṇadāyakatthero}ti pākaṭo. 
