461434,107,2473,43,65,1,221,22,So yāvatāyukaṃ puññāni katvā devamanussesuyeva saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā ghaṭento vāyamanto vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā na cirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
