461445,107,2479,2,8,1,72,5,Siddhatthassa {bhagavato}tiādikaṃ āyasmato dhammacakkikattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461446,107,2479,9,42,1,318,31,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto puttadārehi vaḍḍhito vibhavasampanno mahābhogo, so ratanattaye pasanno saddhājāto dhammasabhāyaṃ dhammāsanassa piṭṭhito ratanamayaṃ dhammacakkaṃ kāretvā pūjesi. "
461447,107,2479,43,72,1,315,28,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu nibbattaṭṭhānesu sakkasampattiṃ cakkavattisampattiñca anubhavitvā kamena imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe uppanno vibhavasampanno sañjātasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ patvā pubbe katakusalanāmasadisanāmena {dhammacakkikatthero}ti pākaṭo jāto ahosi. 
461448,107,2480,2,17,1,146,11,102. So puññasambhārānurūpena pattaarahattaphalo attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā jātasomanasso pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento siddhatthassa {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
461449,107,2480,18,45,1,239,25,"Sīhāsanassa {sammukhā}ti sīhassa bhagavato nisinnassa sammukhā buddhāsanassa abhimukhaṭṭhāneti attho, dhammacakkaṃ me ṭhapitan ti mayā dhammacakkākārena ubhato sīharūpaṃ dassetvā majjhe ādāsasadisaṃ kāretvā kataṃ dhammacakkaṃ ṭhapitaṃ pūjitaṃ. "
461450,107,2480,46,48,1,10,2,Kiṃ bhūtaṃ? 
