461471,107,2490,10,40,1,267,29,Eso hi thero purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tasmiṃ tasmiṃ bhave puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kule nibbatto vuddhimanvāya gharāvāse ādīnavaṃ disvā gehaṃ pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā pañcābhiññāaṭṭhasamāpattilābhī hutvā himavante vāsaṃ kappesi. 
461472,107,2490,41,48,1,62,7,Tasmiṃ samaye padumuttaro bhagavā vivekakāmo himavantaṃ pāvisi. 
461473,107,2490,49,72,1,237,23,Tāpaso bhagavantaṃ puṇṇacandamiva virocamānaṃ dūratova disvā pasannamānaso ajinacammaṃ aṃse katvā añjaliṃ paggayha vanditvā ṭhitakova dasanakhasamodhānañjaliṃ sirasi patiṭṭhapetvā anekāhi upamāhi anekehi thutivacanehi bhagavantaṃ thomesi. 
461474,107,2490,73,76,1,17,3,Taṃ sutvā bhagavā–
