461555,107,2516,36,68,1,304,31,So teneva cittappasādena yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto dibbasampattiṃ manussasampattiñcāti dve sampattiyo anekakkhattuṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ amhākaṃ sammāsambuddhakāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto satthari pasīditvā sāsane pabbajito ghaṭento vāyamanto nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
461556,107,2516,69,83,1,130,12,"Tassa rattiṭṭhānadivāṭṭhānādīsu tattha tattha viharantassa vihāro padumapupphehi chādīyati, tena so {padumacchadaniyatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
461557,107,2517,2,14,1,101,8,83. Attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassavasena pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādimāha. 
461558,107,2517,15,36,1,194,19,"Tattha {nibbute}ti khandhaparinibbānena parinibbute satthari, vipassissa sammāsambuddhassa sarīre citamāniyamāne citake āropite suphullaṃ padumakalāpaṃ ahaṃ gahetvā citakaṃ āropayiṃ pūjesinti attho. "
