461593,107,2531,37,51,1,132,13,Dhammajomhi {sunimmito}ti dhammato kammaṭṭhānadhammato jāto ariyāya jātiyā sunimmito suṭṭhu nippphāditasabbakicco amhi bhavāmīti attho. 
461594,107,2532,2,17,1,111,11,116. Dhammarājaṃ {upagammā}ti dhammena sabbasattānaṃ rājānaṃ issarabhūtaṃ bhagavantaṃ upagantvā samīpaṃ gantvāti attho. 
461595,107,2532,18,26,1,105,8,Apucchiṃ pañhamuttaman ti uttamaṃ khandhāyatanadhātusaccasamuppādādipaṭisaṃyuttaṃ pañhaṃ apucchinti attho. 
461596,107,2532,27,41,1,85,13,Kathayanto ca me pañhan ti eso amhākaṃ bhagavā me mayhaṃ pañhaṃ kathayanto byākaronto. 
461597,107,2532,42,51,1,103,8,Dhammasotaṃ {upānayī}ti anupādisesanibbānadhātusaṅkhātaṃ dhammasotaṃ dhammapavāhaṃ upānayi pāvisīti attho. 
461598,107,2533,2,13,1,72,6,118. {Jalajuttamanāyako}ti padumuttaranāmako ma-kārassa ya-kāraṃ katvā katavohāro. 
461599,107,2533,14,31,1,135,14,"Nibbāyi {anupādāno}ti upādāne pañcakkhandhe aggahetvā nibbāyi na paññāyi adassanaṃ agamāsi, manussalokādīsu katthacipi apatiṭṭhitoti attho. "
461600,107,2533,32,42,1,81,9,Dīpova {telasaṅkhayā}ti vaṭṭitelānaṃ saṅkhayā abhāvā padīpo iva nibbāyīti sambandho. 
461601,107,2534,2,18,1,122,12,119. Sattayojanikaṃ {āsī}ti tassa parinibbutassa padumuttarassa bhagavato ratanamayaṃ thūpaṃ sattayojanubbedhaṃ āsi ahosīti attho. 
461602,107,2534,19,34,1,116,15,Dhajaṃ tattha apūjesin ti tattha tasmiṃ cetiye sabbabhaddaṃ sabbato bhaddaṃ sabbaso manoramaṃ dhajaṃ pūjesinti attho. 
461603,107,2535,2,31,1,225,25,120. Kassapassa ca {buddhassā}ti padumuttarassa bhagavato kālato paṭṭhāya āgatassa devamanussesu saṃsarato me mayhaṃ oraso putto tisso nāma kassapassa sammāsambuddhassa aggasāvako jinasāsane buddhasāsane dāyādo āsi ahosīti sambandho. 
461604,107,2536,2,33,1,184,23,121. Tassa hīnena {manasā}ti tassa mama puttassa tissassa aggasāvakassa hīnena lāmakena manasā cittena abhaddakaṃ asundaraṃ ayuttakaṃ‘‘ antako pacchimo’’ ti vācaṃ vacanaṃ abhāsiṃ kathesinti attho. 
461605,107,2536,34,41,1,79,6,Tena {kammavipākenā}ti tena arahantabhakkhānasaṅkhātassa akusalakammassa vipākena. 
