461609,107,2537,2,23,1,169,17,122. Pabbājesi {mahāvīro}ti mahāvīriyo sabbasattahito karuṇāyutto jitamāro muni mallānaṃ upavattane sālavane pacchime sayane parinibbānamañce sayitova maṃ pabbājesīti sambandho. 
