461625,107,2543,16,30,1,129,12,Tiṇṇoghehi {purakkhato}ti kāmoghādīnaṃ catunnaṃ oghānaṃ tiṇṇattā atikkantattā oghatiṇṇehi khīṇāsavehi purakkhato parivāritoti attho. 
