461630,107,2546,2,29,1,184,23,141. Ubho hatthehi {paggayhā}ti taṃ mahā dinnaṃ dhātuṃ so bhagavā attano ubhohi hatthehi pakārena gahetvā taṃ dhātuṃ saṃsuṭṭhu dassayanto aggasāvakaṃ sāriputtattheraṃ kittayi pakāsesīti attho. 
