461739,107,2593,51,85,1,359,33,So yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā jīvitapariyosāne sagge nibbatto dhajamiva chakāmāvacare pākaṭo pūjito ca dibbasampattimanubhavitvā manussesu ca cakkavattisampattimanubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampanne saddhāsampanne ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya saddhājāto pañcavassikova pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā hutvā katapuññanāmena {padumatthero}ti pākaṭo. 
