461749,107,2598,2,8,1,70,6,Jātiyā sattavassohan tiādikaṃ āyasmato asanabodhiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461750,107,2598,9,45,1,325,34,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto tissassa bhagavato kāle aññatarasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto sukhappatto sāsane pasanno asanabodhito phalaṃ gahetvā tato vuṭṭhitabodhitaruṇe gahetvā bodhiṃ ropesi, yathā na vinassati tathā udakāsiñcanādikammena rakkhitvā pūjesi. "
461751,107,2598,46,69,1,222,20,"So tena puññena devamanussesu sampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto paripakkasambhārattā sattavassikova samāno pabbajitvā khuraggeyeva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi, purākatapuññanāmena {asanabodhiyatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
461752,107,2599,2,14,1,103,8,78. So pubbasambhāramanussaritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento jātiyā sattavassohan tiādimāha. 
461753,107,2599,15,22,1,61,6,Tattha {jātiyā}ti mātugabbhato nikkhantakālato paṭṭhāyāti attho. 
461754,107,2599,23,31,1,82,8,Sattavasso paripuṇṇasarado ahaṃ lokanāyakaṃ tissaṃ bhagavantaṃ addasanti sambandho. 
461755,107,2599,32,42,1,112,8,"Pasannacitto {sumano}ti pakārena pasannaanāluḷitaavikampitacitto, sumano sundaramano somanassasahagatacittoti attho. "
461756,107,2600,2,26,1,142,17,"79. Tissassāhaṃ {bhagavato}ti tikkhattuṃ jātoti tisso, so mātugabbhato, manussajātito, pañcakkhandhato ca mutto hutvā jāto nibbatto buddho jātoti attho. "
461757,107,2600,27,37,1,85,9,"Tassa tissassa bhagavato tādino, lokajeṭṭhassa asanabodhiṃ uttamaṃ ropayinti sambandho. "
461758,107,2601,2,16,1,90,10,80. Asano {nāmadheyyenā}ti nāmapaññattiyā nāmasaññāya asano nāma asanarukkho bodhi ahosīti attho. 
461759,107,2601,17,25,1,77,6,"{Dharaṇīruhapādapo}ti vallirukkhapabbatagaṅgāsāgarādayo dhāretīti dharaṇī, kā sā? "
461760,107,2601,26,45,1,146,16,"Pathavī, tassaṃ ruhati patiṭṭhahatīti dharaṇīruho, pādena pivatīti pādapo, pādasaṅkhātena mūlena siñcitodakaṃ pivati āporasaṃ sinehaṃ dhāretīti attho. "
461761,107,2601,46,62,1,113,15,"Dharaṇīruho ca so pādapo cāti dharaṇīruhapādapo, taṃ uttamaṃ asanaṃ bodhiṃ pañca vassāni paricariṃ posesinti attho. "
461762,107,2602,2,30,1,229,23,81. Pupphitaṃ pādapaṃ {disvā}ti taṃ mayā positaṃ asanabodhirukkhaṃ pupphitaṃ accharayoggabhūtapupphattā abbhutaṃ lomahaṃsakaraṇaṃ disvā sakaṃ kammaṃ attano kammaṃ pakittento pakārena kathayanto buddhaseṭṭhassa santikaṃ agamāsinti attho. 
461763,107,2602,31,34,1,32,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānatthamevāti. 
461764,107,2603,2,4,1,40,2,Asanabodhiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā. 
461765,107,2604,2,4,1,27,2,Chaṭṭhavaggavaṇṇanā samattā.
461766,107,2605,2,4,1,18,2,7 . Sakacintaniyavaggo
461767,107,2606,2,4,1,33,2,1 . Sakacintaniyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461768,107,2607,2,10,1,70,6,Pavanaṃ kānanaṃ {disvā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato sakacintaniyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461769,107,2607,11,58,1,454,46,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya tassa bhagavato āyupariyosāne uppanno dharamānaṃ bhagavantaṃ apāpuṇitvā parinibbutakāle isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavante vasanto vivekaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ ekaṃ vanaṃ patvā tatthevekāya kandarāya pulinacetiyaṃ katvā bhagavati saññaṃ katvā sadhātukasaññañca katvā vanapupphehi pūjetvā namassamāno paricari. 
461770,107,2607,59,83,1,242,24,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto dvīsu aggaṃ aggasampattiṃ aggañca cakkavattisampattiṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vibhavasampanno saddhāsampanno satthari pasīditvā pabbajitvā arahā chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
461771,107,2608,2,16,1,103,10,1. So attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento pavanaṃ kānanaṃ {disvā}tiādimāha. 
461772,107,2608,17,26,1,76,9,Tattha pavanan ti pakārena vanaṃ patthaṭaṃ vitthiṇṇaṃ gahanabhūtanti pavanaṃ. 
461773,107,2608,27,45,1,233,17,"Kānanaṃ avakucchitaṃ ānanaṃ avahanaṃ satataṃ sīhabyagghayakkharakkhasamaddahatthiassasupaṇṇauragehi vihaṅgagaṇasaddakukkuṭakokilehi vā bahalanti kānanaṃ, taṃ kānanasaṅkhātaṃ pavanaṃ manussasaddavirahitattā appasaddaṃ nissaddanti attho. "
461774,107,2608,46,52,1,45,6,Anāvilan ti na āvilaṃ upaddavarahitanti attho. 
461775,107,2608,53,61,1,102,8,Isīnaṃ anuciṇṇan ti buddhapaccekabuddhaarahantakhīṇāsavasaṅkhātānaṃ isīnaṃ anuciṇṇaṃ nisevitanti attho. 
461776,107,2608,62,72,1,81,9,Āhutīnaṃ paṭiggahan ti āhunaṃ vuccati pūjāsakkāraṃ paṭiggahaṃ gehasadisanti attho. 
461777,107,2609,2,13,1,58,7,2. Thūpaṃ katvāna {veḷunā}ti veḷupesikāhi cetiyaṃ katvāti attho. 
461778,107,2609,14,23,1,79,9,Nānāpupphaṃ samokirin ti campakādīhi anekehi pupphehi samokiriṃ pūjesinti attho. 
461779,107,2609,24,42,1,142,17,Sammukhā viya sambuddhan ti sajīvamānassa sambuddhassa sammukhā iva nimmitaṃ uppāditaṃ cetiyaṃ ahaṃ abhi visesena vandiṃ paṇāmamakāsinti attho. 
461780,107,2609,43,45,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
461781,107,2610,2,4,1,41,2,Sakacintaniyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461782,107,2611,2,4,1,31,2,2 . Avopupphiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461783,107,2612,2,8,1,67,5,Vihārā {abhinikkhammā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato avopupphiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461784,107,2612,9,36,1,257,27,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sikhissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto saddhāsampanno dhammaṃ sutvā somanassappatto nānāpupphāni ubhohi hatthehi gahetvā buddhassa upari abbhukkiri. 
461785,107,2612,37,60,1,218,22,So tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto saggasampattiñca cakkavattisampattiñca anubhavitvā sabbattha pūjito imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbato vuddhippatto sāsane pasīditvā pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
461786,107,2612,61,74,1,97,11,"Ā samantato kāsati dippatīti ākāso, tasmiṃ ākāse pupphānaṃ avakiritattā {avopupphiyatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
461787,107,2613,2,16,1,119,10,7. Evaṃ pattasantipado attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento vihārā {abhinikkhammā}tiādimāha. 
461788,107,2613,17,37,1,154,18,"Tattha {vihārā}ti visesena harati catūhi iriyāpathehi apatantaṃ attabhāvaṃ āharati pavatteti etthāti vihāro, tasmā vihārā abhi visesena nikkhamma nikkhamitvā. "
461789,107,2613,38,50,1,99,10,"Abbhuṭṭhāsi ca {caṅkame}ti caṅkamanatthāya saṭṭhiratane caṅkame abhivisesena uṭṭhāsi, abhiruhīti attho. "
461790,107,2613,51,72,1,208,19,Catusaccaṃ {pakāsento}ti tasmiṃ caṅkame caṅkamanto dukkhasamudayanirodhamaggasaccasaṅkhātaṃ catusaccaṃ pakāsento pākaṭaṃ karonto amataṃ padaṃ nibbānaṃ desento vibhajanto uttānīkaronto tasmiṃ caṅkameti sambandho. 
461791,107,2614,2,20,1,128,13,"8. Sikhissa giramaññāya, buddhaseṭṭhassa {tādino}ti seṭṭhassa tādiguṇasamaṅgissa sikhissa buddhassa giraṃ saddaṃ ghosaṃ aññāya jānitvā. "
461792,107,2614,21,28,1,70,6,Nānāpupphaṃ {gahetvānā}ti nāgapunnāgādianekāni pupphāni gahetvā āharitvā. 
461793,107,2614,29,38,1,75,9,Ākāsamhi samokirin ti caṅkamantassa bhagavato muddhani ākāse okiriṃ pūjesiṃ. 
461794,107,2615,2,13,1,75,7,9. Tena kammena {dvipadindā}ti dvipadānaṃ devabrahmamanussānaṃ inda padhānabhūta. 
461795,107,2615,14,18,1,29,3,Narāsabha narānaṃ āsabhabhūta. 
461796,107,2615,19,32,1,95,13,Pattomhi acalaṃ ṭhānan ti tumhākaṃ santike pabbajitvā acalaṃ ṭhānaṃ nibbānaṃ patto amhi bhavāmi. 
461797,107,2615,33,45,1,140,12,Hitvā jayaparājayan ti dibbamanussasampattisaṅkhātaṃ jayañca caturāpāyadukkhasaṅkhātaṃ parājayañca hitvā chaḍḍetvā nibbānaṃ pattosmīti attho. 
461798,107,2615,46,48,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
461799,107,2616,2,4,1,39,2,Avopupphiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samatto.
461800,107,2617,2,4,1,33,2,3 . Paccāgamaniyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461801,107,2618,2,9,1,69,6,Sindhuyā nadiyā {tīre}tiādikaṃ āyasmato paccāgamaniyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461802,107,2618,10,33,1,237,23,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle sindhuyā gaṅgāya samīpe cakkavākayoniyaṃ nibbatto pubbasambhārayuttattā pāṇino akhādanto sevālameva bhakkhayanto carati. 
461803,107,2618,34,41,1,65,7,Tasmiṃ samaye vipassibhagavā sattānuggahaṃ karonto tattha agamāsi. 
461804,107,2618,42,57,1,127,14,Tasmiṃ khaṇe so cakkavāko vijjotamānaṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso tuṇḍena sālarukkhato sālapupphaṃ chinditvā āgamma pūjesi. 
461805,107,2618,58,102,1,419,41,"So teneva cittappasādena tato cuto devaloke uppanno aparāparaṃ chakāmāvacarasampattiṃ anubhavitvā tato cuto manussaloke uppajjitvā cakkavattisampattiādayo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto pubbacaritavasena satthari pasanno pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi, cakkavāko hutvā bhagavantaṃ disvā katthaci gantvā pupphamāharitvā pūjitattā pubbapuññanāmena {paccāgamaniyatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
461806,107,2619,2,15,1,99,9,13. Attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento sindhuyā nadiyā {tīre}tiādimāha. 
461807,107,2619,16,28,1,83,11,"Sīti saddaṃ kurumānā dhunāti kampatīti sindhu, nadati saddaṃ karonto gacchatīti nadi. "
461808,107,2619,29,47,1,110,17,Cakkavāko ahaṃ {tadā}ti cakkaṃ sīghaṃ gacchantaṃ iva udake vā thale vā ākāse vā sīghaṃ vāti gacchatīti cakkavāko. 
461809,107,2619,48,56,1,67,8,Tadā vipassiṃ bhagavantaṃ dassanakāle ahaṃ cakkavāko ahosinti attho. 
461810,107,2619,57,64,1,83,7,Suddhasevālabhakkhohan ti aññagocaraamissattā suddhasevālameva khādanto ahaṃ vasāmi. 
461811,107,2619,65,77,1,97,11,Pāpesu ca {susaññato}ti pubbavāsanāvasena pāpakaraṇe suṭṭhu saññato tīhi dvārehi saññato susikkhito. 
461812,107,2620,2,16,1,95,10,14. Addasaṃ virajaṃ buddhan ti rāgadosamohavirahitattā virajaṃ nikkilesaṃ buddhaṃ addasaṃ addakkhiṃ. 
461813,107,2620,17,24,1,64,6,Gacchantaṃ {anilañjase}ti anilañjase ākāsapathe gacchantaṃ buddhaṃ. 
461814,107,2620,25,37,1,123,12,Tuṇḍena mayhaṃ mukhatuṇḍena tālaṃ sālapupphaṃ paggayha paggahetvā vipassissābhiropayiṃ vipassissa bhagavato pūjesinti attho. 
461815,107,2620,38,40,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
461816,107,2621,2,4,1,41,2,Paccāgamaniyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461817,107,2622,2,4,1,33,2,4 . Parappasādakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461818,107,2623,2,9,1,72,7,Usabhaṃ pavaraṃ vīran tiādikaṃ āyasmato parappasādakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461819,107,2623,10,56,1,480,43,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbatto tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū itihāsapañcamānaṃ padako veyyākaraṇo sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo nāmena {selabrāhmaṇo}ti pākaṭo siddhatthaṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā dvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇehi asītianubyañjanehi cāti sayaṃ sobhamānaṃ disvā pasannamānaso anekehi kāraṇehi anekāhi upamāhi thomanaṃ pakāsesi. 
461820,107,2623,57,92,1,380,33,"So tena puññakammena devaloke sakkamārādayo cha kāmāvacarasampattiyo anubhavitvā manussesu cakkavattisampattiṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto satthari pasīdisvā pabbajito nacirasseva catupaṭisambhidāchaḷabhiññappatto mahākhīṇāsavo ahosi, buddhassa thutiyā sattānaṃ sabbesaṃ cittappasādakaraṇato {parappasādakatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
461821,107,2624,2,16,1,113,11,20. Ekadivasaṃ attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento usabhaṃ pavaraṃ vīran tiādimāha. 
461822,107,2624,17,26,1,72,9,Tattha usabhan ti vasabho nisabho visabho āsabhoti cattāro jeṭṭhapuṅgavā. 
461823,107,2624,27,60,1,289,29,"Tattha gavasatajeṭṭhako vasabho, gavasahassajeṭṭhako nisabho, gavasatasahassajeṭṭhako visabho, gavakoṭisatasahassajeṭṭhako āsabhoti ca yassa kassaci thutiṃ karontā brāhmaṇapaṇḍitā bahussutā attano attano paññāvasena thutiṃ karonti, buddhānaṃ pana sabbākārena thutiṃ kātuṃ samattho ekopi natthi. "
461824,107,2624,61,64,1,19,3,Appameyyo hi buddho. 
461825,107,2624,65,66,1,11,1,Vuttañhetaṃ–
461826,107,2625,2,13,1,62,8,"‘ ‘ Buddhopi buddhassa bhaṇeyya vaṇṇaṃ, kappampi ce aññamabhāsamāno; "
461827,107,2626,2,45,1,65,8,"Khīyetha kappo ciradīghamantare, vaṇṇo na khīyetha tathāgatassā’’ ti.( dī. ni. aṭṭha.1.304;3.141; ma. ni. aṭṭha.2.425; udā. aṭṭha.53)– "
461828,107,2627,2,3,1,6,1,Ādikaṃ . 
461829,107,2627,4,21,1,89,9,Ayampi brāhmaṇo mukhārūḷhavasena ekapasīdanavasena‘‘ āsabhan’’ ti vattabbe‘‘ usabhan’’ tiādimāha. 
461830,107,2627,22,25,1,28,3,Varitabbo patthetabboti varo. 
461831,107,2627,26,30,1,45,4,Anekesu kappasatasahassesu katavīriyattā vīro. 
461832,107,2627,31,40,1,70,8,"Mahantaṃ sīlakkhandhādikaṃ esati gavesatīti mahesī, taṃ mahesiṃ buddhaṃ. "
461833,107,2627,41,50,1,80,8,"Visesena kilesakhandhamārādayo māre jitavāti vijitāvī, taṃ vijitāvinaṃ sambuddhaṃ. "
461834,107,2627,51,68,1,124,16,"Suvaṇṇassa vaṇṇo iva vaṇṇo yassa sambuddhassa so suvaṇṇavaṇṇo, taṃ suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ sambuddhaṃ disvā ko nāma satto nappasīdatīti. "
461835,107,2628,2,4,1,41,2,Parappasādakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461836,107,2629,2,4,1,31,2,5 . Bhisadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461837,107,2630,2,10,1,67,6,Vessabhū nāma {nāmenā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato bhisadāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461838,107,2630,11,28,1,173,17,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vessabhussa bhagavato kāle himavantasmiṃ hatthiyoniyaṃ nibbatto tasmiṃ paṭivasati. 
461839,107,2630,29,35,1,59,6,Tasmiṃ samaye vessabhū bhagavā vivekakāmo himavantamagamāsi. 
461840,107,2630,36,46,1,78,9,Taṃ disvā so hatthināgo pasannamānaso bhisamuḷālaṃ gahetvā bhagavantaṃ bhojesi. 
461841,107,2630,47,82,1,345,33,"So tena puññakammena hatthiyonito cuto devaloke uppajjitvā tattha cha kāmāvacarasampattiyo anubhavitvā manussattamāgato manussesu cakkavattisampattiādayo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde mahābhoge aññatarasmiṃ kule nibbatto pubbavāsanābalena satthari pasanno pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi, so pubbe katakusalanāmena {bhisadāyakatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
461842,107,2631,2,15,1,87,9,29. So attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā pubbacaritāpadānaṃ dassento vessabhū nāma {nāmenā}tiādimāha. 
461843,107,2631,16,23,1,54,6,Tattha {vessabhū}ti vessaṃ bhunāti atikkamatīti vessabhū. 
461844,107,2631,24,45,1,148,19,"Atha vā vesse vāṇijakamme vā kāmarāgādike vā kusalādikamme vā vatthukāmakilesakāme vā bhunāti abhibhavatīti vessabhū, so nāmena vessabhū nāma bhagavā. "
461845,107,2631,46,73,1,132,19,"Isīnaṃ tatiyo {ahū}ti kusaladhamme esati gavesatīti isi,‘‘ vipassī, sikhī, vessabhū’’ ti vuttattā tatiyo isi tatiyo bhagavā ahu ahosīti attho. "
461846,107,2631,74,83,1,75,8,Kānanaṃ {vanamoggayhā}ti kānanasaṅkhātaṃ vanaṃ ogayha ogahetvā pāvisīti attho. 
461847,107,2632,2,17,1,92,10,"30. Bhisamuḷālaṃ {gaṇhitvā}ti dvipadacatuppadānaṃ chātakaṃ bhisati hiṃsati vināsetīti bhisaṃ, ko so? "
461848,107,2632,18,28,1,76,8,"Padumakando, bhisañca muḷālañca bhisamuḷālaṃ, taṃ bhisamuḷālaṃ gahetvāti attho. "
461849,107,2633,2,21,1,140,14,"31. Karena ca {parāmaṭṭho}ti taṃ mayā dinnadānaṃ, vessabhūvarabuddhinā uttamabuddhinā vessabhunā karena hatthatalena parāmaṭṭho katasamphasso ahosi. "
461850,107,2633,22,45,1,140,20,"Sukhāhaṃ nābhijānāmi, samaṃ tena kutottarin ti tena sukhena samaṃ sukhaṃ nābhijānāmi, tato uttariṃ tato paraṃ tato adhikaṃ sukhaṃ kutoti attho. "
461851,107,2633,46,49,1,32,3,Sesaṃ nayānusārena suviññeyyanti. 
461852,107,2634,2,4,1,39,2,Bhisadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461853,107,2635,2,4,1,29,2,6 . Sucintitattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461854,107,2636,2,8,1,65,6,Giriduggacaro āsin tiādikaṃ āyasmato sucintitattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461855,107,2636,9,28,1,198,19,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto atthadassissa bhagavato kāle himavantappadese nesādakule uppanno migasūkarādayo vadhitvā khādanto viharati. 
461856,107,2636,29,35,1,71,6,Tadā lokanātho lokānuggahaṃ sattānuddayatañca paṭicca himavantamagamāsi. 
461857,107,2636,36,47,1,98,11,Tadā so nesādo bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso attano khādanatthāya ānītaṃ varamadhuramaṃsaṃ adāsi. 
461858,107,2636,48,57,1,73,8,"Paṭiggahesi bhagavā tassānukampāya, taṃ bhuñjitvā anumodanaṃ vatvā pakkāmi. "
461859,107,2636,58,84,1,240,25,So teneva puññena teneva somanassena tato cuto sugatīsu saṃsaranto cha kāmāvacarasampattiyo anubhavitvā manussesu cakkavattisampattiādayo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
461860,107,2637,2,17,1,141,11,36. Catupaṭisambhidāpañcābhiññādibhedaṃ patvā attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento giriduggacaro āsin tiādimāha. 
461861,107,2637,18,25,1,33,6,"Girati saddaṃ karotīti giri, ko so? "
461862,107,2637,26,39,1,94,10,"Silāpaṃsumayapabbato, duṭṭhu dukkhena gamanīyaṃ duggaṃ, girīhi duggaṃ giriduggaṃ, duggamoti attho. "
461863,107,2637,40,47,1,57,7,Tasmiṃ giridugge pabbatantare caro caraṇasīlo āsiṃ ahosiṃ. 
461864,107,2637,48,61,1,100,12,Abhijātova {kesarī}ti abhi visesena jāto nibbatto kesarīva kesarasīho iva giriduggasmiṃ carāmīti attho. 
461865,107,2638,2,16,1,93,11,40. Giriduggaṃ pavisiṃ ahan ti ahaṃ tadā tena maṃsadānena pītisomanassajāto pabbatantaraṃ pāvisiṃ. 
