461868,107,2640,2,4,1,32,2,7 . Vatthadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461869,107,2641,2,10,1,70,7,Pakkhijāto tadā āsin tiādikaṃ āyasmato vatthadāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461870,107,2641,11,40,1,318,29,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto atthadassissa bhagavato kāle supaṇṇayoniyaṃ nibbatto gandhamādanapabbataṃ gacchantaṃ atthadassiṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso supaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ vijahitvā māṇavakavaṇṇaṃ nimminitvā mahagghaṃ dibbavatthaṃ ādāya bhagavantaṃ pūjesi. 
461871,107,2641,41,47,1,50,6,Sopi bhagavā paṭiggahetvā anumodanaṃ vatvā pakkāmi. 
461872,107,2641,48,95,1,453,44,"So teneva somanassena vītināmetvā yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cuto devaloke nibbatto tattha aparāparaṃ saṃsaranto puññāni anubhavitvā tato manussesu manussasampattinti sabbattha mahagghaṃ vatthābharaṇaṃ laddhaṃ, tato uppannuppannabhave vatthacchāyāya gatagataṭṭhāne vasanto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva chaḷabhiññappattakhīṇāsavo ahosi, pubbe katapuññanāmena {vatthadāyakatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
461873,107,2642,2,16,1,104,11,45. So attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento pakkhijāto tadā āsin tiādimāha. 
461874,107,2642,17,34,1,127,14,"Tattha {pakkhijāto}ti pakkhandati upalavati sakuṇo etenāti pakkhaṃ, pakkhamassa atthīti pakkhī, pakkhiyoniyaṃ jāto nibbattoti attho. "
461875,107,2642,35,48,1,101,9,"{Supaṇṇo}ti sundaraṃ paṇṇaṃ pattaṃ yassa so supaṇṇo, vātaggāhasuvaṇṇavaṇṇajalamānapattamahābhāroti attho. "
461876,107,2642,49,68,1,144,16,"{Garuḷādhipo}ti nāge gaṇhanatthāya garuṃ bhāraṃ pāsāṇaṃ giḷantīti garuḷā, garuḷānaṃ adhipo rājāti garuḷādhipo, virajaṃ buddhaṃ addasāhanti sambandho. "
461877,107,2643,2,4,1,40,2,Vatthadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461878,107,2644,2,4,1,30,2,8 . Ambadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461879,107,2645,2,8,1,64,5,Anomadassī {bhagavā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato ambadāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461880,107,2645,9,28,1,179,18,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto anomadassissa bhagavato kāle vānarayoniyaṃ nibbatto himavante kapirājā hutvā paṭivasati. 
461881,107,2645,29,35,1,65,6,Tasmiṃ samaye anomadassī bhagavā tassānukampāya himavantamagamāsi. 
461882,107,2645,36,46,1,90,10,Atha so kapirājā bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso sumadhuraṃ ambaphalaṃ khuddamadhunā adāsi. 
461883,107,2645,47,57,1,82,10,Atha bhagavā tassa passantasseva taṃ sabbaṃ paribhuñjitvā anumodanaṃ vatvā pakkāmi. 
461884,107,2645,58,88,1,312,30,Atha so somanassasampannahadayo teneva pītisomanassena yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cuto devaloke nibbatto aparāparaṃ tattha dibbasukhamanubhavitvā manussesu ca manussasampattiṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto satthari pasīditvā pabbajitvā nacirasseva chaḷabhiññappatto ahosi. 
461885,107,2645,89,93,1,42,3,Pubbapuññanāmena {ambadāyakatthero}ti pākaṭo. 
461886,107,2646,2,17,1,120,11,53. So aparabhāge attanā katakusalabījaṃ disvā somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento anomadassī {bhagavā}tiādimāha. 
461887,107,2646,18,46,1,183,22,"Mettāya aphari loke, appamāṇe {nirūpadhī}ti so bhagavā sabbaloke appamāṇe satte‘‘ sukhī hontū’’ tiādinā nirupadhi upadhivirahitaṃ katvā mettāya mettacittena aphari patthari vaḍḍhesīti attho. "
461888,107,2647,2,15,1,67,10,54. Kapi ahaṃ tadā āsin ti tadā tassāgamanakāle kapirājā ahosinti attho. 
461889,107,2648,2,4,1,38,2,Ambadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461890,107,2649,2,4,1,26,2,9 . Sumanattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461891,107,2650,2,10,1,60,6,Sumano nāma {nāmenā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato sumanattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461892,107,2650,11,36,1,244,24,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sikhissa bhagavato kāle mālākārassa kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya saddhājāto bhagavati pasannamānaso sumanamālāmuṭṭhiyo gahetvā ubhohi hatthehi pūjesi. 
461893,107,2650,37,61,1,211,23,So tena puññena devamanussesu dve sampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya puttadārehi vaḍḍhitvā sumananāmena pākaṭo satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
461894,107,2651,2,19,1,119,13,62. So arahā hutvā attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento sumano nāma {nāmenā}tiādimāha. 
461895,107,2651,20,26,1,37,6,Sundaraṃ manaṃ cittaṃ yassa so sumano. 
461896,107,2651,27,36,1,73,9,Saddhāpasādabahumānena yutto nāmena sumano nāma mālākāro tadā ahaṃ ahosiṃ. 
461897,107,2652,2,12,1,50,6,63. Sikhino {lokabandhuno}ti sikhā muddhā kāsatīti sikhī. 
461898,107,2652,13,22,1,61,8,"Atha vā sampayuttasampayoge khādati viddhaṃsetīti sikhī, kā sā? "
461899,107,2652,23,30,1,48,6,"Aggisikhā, aggisikhā viya sikhāya dippanato sikhī. "
461900,107,2652,31,48,1,149,15,"Yathā aggisikhā jotati pākaṭā hoti, sikhī pattatiṇakaṭṭhapalāsādike dahati, evamayampi bhagavā nīlapītādiraṃsīhi jotati sakalalokasannivāse pākaṭo hoti. "
461901,107,2652,49,59,1,104,9,"Sakasantānagatasabbakilese soseti viddhaṃseti jhāpetīti vohāranāmaṃ nāmakammaṃ nāmadheyyaṃ, tassa sikhino. "
461902,107,2652,60,72,1,118,11,"Sakalalokassa bandhuñātakoti lokabandhu, tassa sikhino lokabandhuno bhagavato sumanapupphaṃ abhiropayiṃ pūjesinti attho. "
