461920,107,2660,2,4,1,15,2,8 . Nāgasamālavaggo
461921,107,2661,2,4,1,30,2,1 . Nāgasamālattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461922,107,2662,2,10,1,69,7,Āpāṭaliṃ ahaṃ pupphan tiādikaṃ āyasmato nāgasamālattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461923,107,2662,11,80,1,736,67,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sikhissa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā tathārūpasajjanasaṃsaggassa alābhena satthari dharamānakāle dassanasavanapūjākammamakaritvā parinibbutakāle tassa bhagavato sārīrikadhātuṃ nidahitvā katacetiyamhi cittaṃ pasādetvā pāṭalipupphaṃ pūjetvā somanassaṃ uppādetvā yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā teneva somanassena tato kālaṃ kato tusitādīsu chasu devalokesu sukhamanubhavitvā aparabhāge manussesu manussasampattiṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto nāgarukkhapallavakomaḷasadisasarīrattā {nāgasamālo}ti mātāpitūhi katanāmadheyyo bhagavati pasanno pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
461924,107,2663,2,18,1,112,12,1. So pacchā attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento āpāṭaliṃ ahaṃ pupphan tiādimāha. 
461925,107,2663,19,34,1,105,14,"Tattha āpāṭalin ti ā samantato, ādarena vā pāṭalipupphaṃ gahetvā ahaṃ thūpamhi abhiropesiṃ pūjesinti attho. "
461926,107,2663,35,49,1,160,12,"Ujjhitaṃ {sumahāpathe}ti sabbanagaravāsīnaṃ vandanapūjanatthāya mahāpathe nagaramajjhe vīthiyaṃ ujjhitaṃ uṭṭhāpitaṃ, iṭṭhakakammasudhākammādīhi nipphāditanti attho. "
461927,107,2663,50,56,1,59,6,Sesaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayattā uttānatthattā ca suviññeyyamevāti. 
461928,107,2664,2,4,1,38,2,Nāgasamālattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461929,107,2665,2,4,1,31,2,2 . Padasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461930,107,2666,2,9,1,69,6,Akkantañca padaṃ {disvā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato padasaññakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461931,107,2666,10,38,1,300,27,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro uppannuppannabhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto tissassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ saddhāsampanne upāsakagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto ratanattaye pasanno bhagavatā tassa anukampāya dassitaṃ padacetiyaṃ disvā pasanno lomahaṭṭhajāto vandanapūjanādibahumānamakāsi. 
461932,107,2666,39,71,1,307,29,"So teneva sukhette sukatena puññena tato cuto sagge nibbatto tattha dibbasukhamanubhavitvā aparabhāge manussesu jāto manussasampattiṃ sabbamanubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampannakule nibbatto vuddhimanvāya saddhājāto pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi, purākatapuññanāmena {padasaññakatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
461933,107,2667,2,16,1,101,10,5. So ekadivasaṃ attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento akkantañca padaṃ {disvā}tiādimāha. 
461934,107,2667,17,22,1,37,5,Tattha akkantan ti akkamitaṃ dassitaṃ. 
461935,107,2667,23,50,1,193,21,"Sabbabuddhānaṃ sabbadā caturaṅgulopariyeva gamanaṃ, ayaṃ pana tassa saddhāsampannataṃ ñatvā‘‘ eso imaṃ passatū’’ ti padacetiyaṃ dassesi, tasmā so tasmiṃ pasīditvā vandanapūjanādisakkāramakāsīti attho. "
461936,107,2667,51,54,1,32,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānatthamevāti. 
461937,107,2668,2,4,1,39,2,Padasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461938,107,2669,2,4,1,33,2,3 . Buddhasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461939,107,2670,2,8,1,71,6,Dumagge paṃsukūlikan tiādikaṃ āyasmato buddhasaññakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461940,107,2670,9,41,1,283,27,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto tissassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto saddhājāto dumagge laggitaṃ bhagavato paṃsukūlacīvaraṃ disvā pasannamānaso‘‘ arahaddhajan’’ ti cintetvā vandanapūjanādisakkāramakāsi. 
461941,107,2670,42,57,1,160,15,So tena puññakammena devamanussasampattimanubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto saddhājāto pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
461942,107,2671,2,16,1,125,11,9. So pattaarahattādhigamo attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento dumagge paṃsukūlikan tiādimāha. 
461943,107,2671,17,21,1,29,4,Tattha dhunāti kampatīti dumo. 
461944,107,2671,22,35,1,77,11,"Duhati pūreti ākāsatalanti vā dumo, dumassa aggo koṭīti dumaggo, tasmiṃ dumagge. "
461945,107,2671,36,60,1,207,21,"Paṃsumiva paṭikkūlabhāvaṃ amanuññabhāvaṃ ulati gacchatīti paṃsukūlaṃ, paṃsukūlameva paṃsukūlikaṃ, satthuno paṃsukūlaṃ dumagge laggitaṃ disvā ahaṃ añjaliṃ paggahetvā taṃ paṃsukūlaṃ avandiṃ paṇāmamakāsinti attho. "
461946,107,2671,61,64,1,19,3,Tan ti nipātamattaṃ. 
461947,107,2671,65,68,1,32,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānatthamevāti. 
461948,107,2672,2,4,1,41,2,Buddhasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461949,107,2673,2,4,1,35,2,4 . Bhisāluvadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461950,107,2674,2,9,1,71,5,Kānanaṃ {vanamoggayhā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato bhisāluvadāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461951,107,2674,10,34,1,254,24,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle himavantassa samīpe araññāvāse vasanto vanamūlaphalāhāro vivekavasenāgataṃ vipassiṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso pañcabhisāluve adāsi. 
461952,107,2674,35,41,1,55,6,Bhagavā tassa cittaṃ pasādetuṃ passantasseva paribhuñji. 
461953,107,2674,42,66,1,230,24,So tena cittappasādena kālaṃ katvā tusitādīsu sampattimanubhavitvā pacchā manussasampattiñca anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vibhavasampattiṃ patto taṃ pahāya sāsane pabbajito nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
461954,107,2675,2,16,1,107,10,13. So tato attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento kānanaṃ {vanamoggayhā}tiādimāha. 
461955,107,2675,17,20,1,24,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttatthameva. 
461956,107,2675,21,29,1,56,8,Vasāmi vipine ahan ti vivekavāso ahaṃ vasāmīti sambandho. 
461957,107,2675,30,32,1,22,2,Sesaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
461958,107,2676,2,4,1,43,2,Bhisāluvadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā. 
461959,107,2677,2,4,1,32,2,Chaṭṭhabhāṇavāravaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
461960,107,2678,2,4,1,30,2,5 . Ekasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461961,107,2679,2,10,1,66,6,Khaṇḍo nāmāsi {nāmenā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato ekasaññakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461962,107,2679,11,39,1,269,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto ratanattaye pasannamānaso tassa satthuno khaṇḍaṃ nāma aggasāvakaṃ bhikkhāya caramānaṃ disvā saddahitvā piṇḍapātamadāsi. 
461963,107,2679,40,62,1,206,21,So tena puññakammena devamanussasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
461964,107,2679,63,72,1,93,8,So ekadivasaṃ piṇḍapātassa saññaṃ manasikaritvā paṭiladdhavisesattā {ekasaññakatthero}ti pākaṭo. 
461965,107,2680,2,18,1,113,11,18. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento khaṇḍo nāmāsi {nāmenā}tiādimāha. 
461966,107,2680,19,27,1,69,7,Tattha tassa aggasāvakattherassa kilesānaṃ khaṇḍitattā {khaṇḍo}ti nāmaṃ. 
461967,107,2680,28,31,1,28,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānamevāti. 
461968,107,2681,2,4,1,38,2,Ekasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
461969,107,2682,2,4,1,38,2,6 . Tiṇasantharadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
461970,107,2683,2,7,1,72,4,{Himavantassāvidūre}tiādikaṃ āyasmato tiṇasantharadāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
461971,107,2683,8,36,1,269,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto tissassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto buddhuppādato pageva uppannattā gharāvāsaṃ pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavantassa avidūre ekaṃ saraṃ nissāya paṭivasati. 
461972,107,2683,37,44,1,58,7,Tasmiṃ samaye tisso bhagavā tassānukampāya ākāsena agamāsi. 
461973,107,2683,45,67,1,189,22,Atha kho so tāpaso ākāsato oruyha ṭhitaṃ taṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso tiṇaṃ lāyitvā tiṇasantharaṃ katvā nisīdāpetvā bahumānādarena pañcapatiṭṭhitena vanditvā paṭikuṭiko hutvā pakkāmi. 
461974,107,2683,68,89,1,203,21,So yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cavitvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto anekavidhasampattiṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
461975,107,2684,2,15,1,111,9,22. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento {himavantassāvidūre}tiādimāha. 
461976,107,2684,16,19,1,24,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttatthameva. 
461977,107,2684,20,47,1,189,23,"{Mahājātassaro}ti ettha pana saranti ettha pānīyatthikā dvipadacatuppadādayo sattāti saraṃ, atha vā saranti ettha nadīkandarādayoti saraṃ, mahanto ca so sayameva jātattā saro ceti mahājātassaro. "
461978,107,2684,48,59,1,80,7,Anotattachaddantadahādayo viya apākaṭanāmattā‘‘ mahājātassaro’’ ti vuttoti daṭṭhabbo. 
461979,107,2684,60,75,1,126,11,"Satapattehi {sañchanno}ti ekekasmiṃ pupphe satasatapattānaṃ vasena satapatto, satapattasetapadumehi sañchanno gahanībhūtoti attho. "
461980,107,2684,76,90,1,146,13,{Nānāsakuṇamālayo}ti aneke haṃsakukkuṭakukkuhadeṇḍibhādayo ekato kuṇanti saddaṃ karontīti sakuṇāti laddhanāmānaṃ pakkhīnaṃ ālayo ādhārabhūtoti attho. 
461981,107,2684,91,94,1,32,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānatthamevāti. 
