462001,107,2695,2,4,1,32,2,9 . Ṭhitañjaliyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462002,107,2696,2,9,1,69,7,Migaluddo pure āsin tiādikaṃ āyasmato ṭhitañjaliyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462003,107,2696,10,34,1,251,24,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tatthuppannabhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto tissassa bhagavato kāle purākatena ekena kammacchiddena nesādayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto migasūkarādayo māretvā nesādakammena araññe vāsaṃ kappesi. 
462004,107,2696,35,42,1,61,7,Tasmiṃ samaye tisso bhagavā tassānukampāya himavantaṃ agamāsi. 
462005,107,2696,43,57,1,146,14,So taṃ dvattiṃsavaralakkhaṇehi asītānubyañjanabyāmappabhāhi ca jalamānaṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā somanassajāto paṇāmaṃ katvā gantvā paṇṇasanthare nisīdi. 
462006,107,2696,58,69,1,90,10,"Tasmiṃ khaṇe devo gajjanto asani pati, tato maraṇasamaye buddhamanussaritvā punañjalimakāsi. "
462007,107,2696,70,99,1,297,29,So tena puññena sukhette katakusalattā akusalavipākaṃ paṭibāhitvā sagge nibbatto kāmāvacarasampattiyo anubhavitvā manussesu manussasampattiyo ca anubhavitvā aparabhāge imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya purākatavāsanāya satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462008,107,2697,2,19,1,114,13,42. So tato paraṃ attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento migaluddo pure āsin tiādimāha. 
462009,107,2697,20,27,1,58,6,Tattha {migaluddo}ti migānaṃ māraṇaṃ upagacchatīti migaluddo. 
462010,107,2697,28,42,1,103,13,"Miganti sīghaṃ vātavegena gacchanti dhāvantīti migā, tesaṃ migānaṃ māraṇe luddo dāruṇo lobhīti migaluddo. "
462011,107,2697,43,53,1,66,9,So ahaṃ pure bhagavato dassanasamaye migaluddo āsiṃ ahosinti attho . 
462012,107,2697,54,75,1,166,18,"Araññe {kānane}ti arati gacchati migasamūho etthāti araññaṃ, atha vā ā samantato rajjanti tattha vivekābhiratā buddhapaccekabuddhādayo mahāsārappattā sappurisāti araññaṃ. "
462013,107,2697,76,97,1,144,19,"Kā kucchitākārena vā bhayānakākārena vā nadanti saddaṃ karonti, ānanti vindantīti vā kānanaṃ, tasmiṃ araññe kānane migaluddo pure āsinti sambandho. "
462014,107,2697,98,110,1,95,12,Tattha addasaṃ sambuddhan ti tattha tasmiṃ araññe upagataṃ sambuddhaṃ addasaṃ addakkhinti attho. 
462015,107,2697,111,124,1,120,12,"Dassanaṃ pure ahosi avidūre, tasmā manodvārānusārena cakkhuviññāṇaṃ purecārikaṃ kāyaviññāṇasamaṅgiṃ pāpeti appetīti attho. "
462016,107,2698,2,23,1,112,15,"44. Tato me {asanīpāto}ti ā samantato sananto gajjanto patatīti asani, asaniyā pāto patanaṃ asanīpāto, devadaṇḍoti attho. "
462017,107,2698,24,27,1,32,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānatthamevāti. 
462018,107,2699,2,4,1,40,2,Ṭhitañjaliyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462019,107,2700,2,4,1,30,2,10 . Tipadumiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462020,107,2701,2,9,1,67,6,Padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādikaṃ āyasmato tipadumiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462021,107,2701,10,38,1,294,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle haṃsavatiyaṃ mālākārakulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto mālākārakammaṃ katvā vasanto ekadivasaṃ anekavidhāni jalajathalajapupphāni gahetvā rañño santikaṃ gantukāmo evaṃ cintesi–
462022,107,2701,39,85,1,283,35,"‘‘ rājā imāni tāva pupphāni disvā pasanno sahassaṃ vā dhanaṃ gāmādikaṃ vā dadeyya, lokanāthaṃ pana pūjetvā nibbānāmatadhanaṃ labhāmi, kiṃ me etesu sundaran’’ ti tena‘‘ bhagavantaṃ pūjetvā saggamokkhasampattiyo nipphādetuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti cintetvā vaṇṇavantaṃ atīva rattapupphattayaṃ gahetvā pūjesi. "
462023,107,2701,86,92,1,48,6,Tāni gantvā ākāsaṃ chādetvā pattharitvā aṭṭhaṃsu. 
462024,107,2701,93,97,1,70,4,Nagaravāsino acchariyabbhutacittajātā celukkhepasahassāni pavattayiṃsu. 
462025,107,2701,98,103,1,34,5,Taṃ disvā bhagavā anumodanaṃ akāsi. 
462026,107,2701,104,124,1,193,20,So tena puññena devamanussesu sampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde gahapatikule nibbatto vuddhimanvāya satthari pasīditvā dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462027,107,2702,2,17,1,103,10,48. So attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādimāha. 
462028,107,2702,18,21,1,24,3,Tassattho heṭṭhā vuttova. 
462029,107,2702,22,33,1,98,10,Sabbadhammāna {pāragū}ti sabbesaṃ navalokuttaradhammānaṃ pāraṃ nibbānaṃ gato paccakkhaṃ katoti attho. 
462030,107,2702,34,46,1,91,10,Danto {dantaparivuto}ti sayaṃ kāyavācādīhi danto etadagge ṭhapitehi sāvakehi parivutoti attho. 
462031,107,2702,47,51,1,48,4,Sesaṃ sabbattha sambandhavasena uttānatthamevāti. 
462032,107,2703,2,4,1,38,2,Tipadumiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā. 
462033,107,2704,2,4,1,27,2,Aṭṭhamavaggavaṇṇanā samattā.
462034,107,2705,2,4,1,11,2,9 . Timiravaggo
462035,107,2706,2,4,1,34,2,1 . Timirapupphiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462036,107,2707,2,8,1,68,4,{Candabhāgānadītīre}tiādikaṃ āyasmato timirapupphiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462037,107,2707,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
462038,107,2707,12,57,1,423,44,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā vasanto kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā gharāvāsaṃ pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā candabhāgāya nadiyā samīpe vasati, vivekakāmatāya himavantaṃ gantvā nisinnaṃ siddhatthaṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā vanditvā tassa guṇaṃ pasīditvā timirapupphaṃ gahetvā pūjesi. "
462039,107,2707,58,80,1,183,21,So tena puññena devesu ca manussesu ca sampattimanubhavanto saṃsaritvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462040,107,2708,2,14,1,104,8,1. So aparabhāge pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento {candabhāgānadītīre}tiādimāha. 
462041,107,2708,15,18,1,24,3,Tassattho heṭṭhā vuttova. 
462042,107,2708,19,37,1,152,18,Anubhotaṃ vajāmahan ti gaṅgāya āsanne vasanabhāvena sabbattha rammabhāvena gaṅgāto heṭṭhā sotānusārena ahaṃ vajāmi gacchāmi tattha tattha vasāmīti attho. 
462043,107,2708,38,48,1,98,9,Nisinnaṃ samaṇaṃ {disvā}ti samitapāpattā sositapāpattā samaṇasaṅkhātaṃ sammāsambuddhaṃ disvāti attho. 
462044,107,2709,2,24,1,141,18,2. Evaṃ cintesahaṃ {tadā}ti ayaṃ bhagavā sayaṃ tiṇṇo sabbasatte tārayissati saṃsārato uttāreti sayaṃ kāyadvārādīhi damito ayaṃ bhagavā pare dameti. 
462045,107,2710,2,16,1,90,9,"3. Sayaṃ assattho assāsampatto, kilesapariḷāhato mutto sabbasatte assāseti, santabhāvaṃ āpāpeti. "
462046,107,2710,17,23,1,57,6,Sayaṃ santo santakāyacitto paresaṃ santakāyacittaṃ pāpeti. 
462047,107,2710,24,31,1,56,7,Sayaṃ mutto saṃsārato muccito pare saṃsārato mocayissati. 
462048,107,2710,32,47,1,118,15,So ayaṃ bhagavā sayaṃ nibbuto kilesaggīhi nibbuto paresampi kilesaggīhi nibbāpessatīti ahaṃ tadā evaṃ cintesinti attho. 
462049,107,2711,2,29,1,195,23,4. Gahetvā timirapupphan ti sakalaṃ vanantaṃ nīlakāḷaraṃsīhi andhakāraṃ viya kurumānaṃ khāyatīti timiraṃ pupphaṃ taṃ gahetvā kaṇṇikāvaṇṭaṃ gahetvā matthake sīsassa upari ākāse okiriṃ pūjesinti attho. 
462050,107,2711,30,32,1,22,2,Sesaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
462051,107,2712,2,4,1,42,2,Timirapupphiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462052,107,2713,2,4,1,31,2,2 . Gatasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462053,107,2714,2,9,1,69,6,Jātiyā sattavassohan tiādikaṃ āyasmato gatasaññakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462054,107,2714,10,34,1,244,23,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto tissassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto purākatavāsanāvasena saddhājāto sattavassikakāleyeva pabbajito bhagavato paṇāmakaraṇeneva pākaṭo ahosi. 
462055,107,2714,35,44,1,98,9,So ekadivasaṃ atīva nīlamaṇippabhāni naṅgalakasitaṭṭhāne uṭṭhitasattapupphāni gahetvā ākāse pūjesi. 
462056,107,2714,45,66,1,186,21,So yāvatāyukaṃ samaṇadhammaṃ katvā tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462057,107,2715,2,16,1,115,11,10. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento jātiyā sattavassohan tiādimāha. 
462058,107,2715,17,26,1,94,8,Tattha jātiyā {sattavasso}ti mātugabbhato nikkhantakālato paṭṭhāya paripuṇṇasattavassikoti attho. 
462059,107,2715,27,42,1,130,14,"Pabbajiṃ anagāriyan ti agārassa hitaṃ āgāriyaṃ kasivāṇijjādikammaṃ natthi āgāriyanti anagāriyaṃ, buddhasāsane pabbajiṃ ahanti attho. "
462060,107,2716,2,11,1,45,6,12. Sugatānugataṃ maggan ti buddhena gataṃ maggaṃ. 
462061,107,2716,12,21,1,105,9,Atha vā sugatena desitaṃ dhammānudhammapaṭipattipūraṇavasena haṭṭhamānaso tuṭṭhacitto pūjetvāti sambandho. 
462062,107,2716,22,25,1,32,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānatthamevāti. 
462063,107,2717,2,4,1,39,2,Gatasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462064,107,2718,2,4,1,34,2,3 . Nipannañjalikattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462065,107,2719,2,9,1,73,6,Rukkhamūle nisinnohan tiādikaṃ āyasmato nipannañjalikattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462066,107,2719,10,29,1,197,19,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro anekesu bhavesu vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto tissassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto pabbajitvā rukkhamūlikaṅgaṃ pūrayamāno araññe viharati. 
462067,107,2719,30,40,1,72,9,"Tasmiṃ samaye kharo ābādho uppajji, tena pīḷito paramakāruññappatto ahosi. "
462068,107,2719,41,47,1,43,6,Tadā bhagavā tassa kāruññena tattha agamāsi. 
462069,107,2719,48,59,1,83,11,Atha so nipannakova uṭṭhituṃ asakkonto sirasi añjaliṃ katvā bhagavato paṇāmaṃ akāsi. 
462070,107,2719,60,89,1,266,26,"So tato cuto tusitabhavane uppanno tattha sampattimanubhavitvā evaṃ cha kāmāvacarasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi, purākatapuññavasena {nipannañjalikatthero}ti pākaṭo. "
462071,107,2720,2,17,1,121,11,16. So aparabhāge attano puññasampattiyo oloketvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento rukkhamūle nisinnohan tiādimāha. 
462072,107,2720,18,30,1,90,11,"Tattha ruhati paṭiruhati uddhamuddhaṃ ārohatīti rukkho, tassa rukkhassa mūle samīpeti attho. "
462073,107,2720,31,47,1,118,14,"Byādhito paramena {cā}ti paramena adhikena kharena kakkhaḷena byādhinā rogena byādhito, byādhinā ahaṃ samannāgatoti attho. "
462074,107,2720,48,59,1,110,10,{Paramakāruññappattomhī}ti paramaṃ adhikaṃ kāruññaṃ dīnabhāvaṃ dukkhitabhāvaṃ pattomhi araññe kānaneti sambandho. 
462075,107,2721,2,13,1,65,7,20. Pañcevāsuṃ {mahāsikhā}ti sirasi piḷandhanatthena sikhā vuccati cūḷā. 
462076,107,2721,14,28,1,108,13,"Maṇīti jotamānaṃ makuṭaṃ tassa atthīti sikho, cakkavattino ekanāmakā pañceva cakkavattino āsuṃ ahesunti attho. "
462077,107,2721,29,32,1,32,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānatthamevāti. 
462078,107,2722,2,4,1,42,2,Nipannañjalikattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462079,107,2723,2,4,1,32,2,4 . Adhopupphiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462080,107,2724,2,10,1,71,7,Abhibhū nāma so {bhikkhū}tiādikaṃ āyasmato adhopupphiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462081,107,2724,11,43,1,317,31,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro anekesu bhavesu vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sikhissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā aparabhāge kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā taṃ pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā pañcābhiññāaṭṭhasamāpattilābhī iddhīsu ca vasībhāvaṃ patvā himavantasmiṃ paṭivasati. 
462082,107,2724,44,52,1,80,8,Tassa sikhissa bhagavato abhibhū nāma aggasāvako vivekābhirato himavantamagamāsi. 
462083,107,2724,53,70,1,155,17,Atha so tāpaso taṃ aggasāvakattheraṃ disvā therassa ṭhitapabbataṃ āruhanto pabbatassa heṭṭhātalato sugandhāni vaṇṇasampannāni satta pupphāni gahetvā pūjesi. 
462084,107,2724,71,75,1,33,4,Atha so thero tassānumodanamakāsi. 
462085,107,2724,76,80,1,30,4,Sopi tāpaso sakassamaṃ agamāsi. 
462086,107,2724,81,116,1,345,34,Tattha ekena ajagarena pīḷito aparabhāge aparihīnajjhāno teneva upaddavena upadduto kālaṃ katvā brahmalokaparāyano hutvā brahmasampattiṃ chakāmāvacarasampattiñca anubhavitvā manussesu manussasampattiyo ca khepetvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā pasannamānaso pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462087,107,2724,117,124,1,64,6,So aparabhāge attano katapuññanāmena {adhopupphiyatthero}ti pākaṭo. 
462088,107,2725,2,18,1,116,12,22. So ekadivasaṃ attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento abhibhū nāma so {bhikkhū}tiādimāha. 
462089,107,2725,19,38,1,181,16,"Tattha sīlasamādhīhi pare abhibhavatīti abhibhū, khandhamārādimāre abhibhavati ajjhottharatīti vā abhibhū, sasantānaparasantānagatakilese abhibhavati viheseti viddhaṃsetīti vā abhibhū. "
462090,107,2725,39,46,1,69,6,"Bhikkhanasīlo yācanasīloti bhikkhu, chinnabhinnapaṭadharoti vā bhikkhu. "
462091,107,2725,47,58,1,84,10,"Abhibhū nāma aggasāvako so bhikkhūti attho, sikhissa bhagavato aggasāvakoti sambandho. "
462092,107,2726,2,20,1,123,14,27. Ajagaro maṃ {pīḷesī}ti tathārūpaṃ sīlasampannaṃ jhānasampannaṃ tāpasaṃ pubbe katapāpena verena ca mahanto ajagarasappo pīḷesi. 
462093,107,2726,21,30,1,80,9,So teneva upaddavena upadduto aparihīnajjhāno kālaṃ katvā brahmalokaparāyaṇo āsi. 
462094,107,2726,31,34,1,28,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānamevāti. 
462095,107,2727,2,4,1,40,2,Adhopupphiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462096,107,2728,2,4,1,32,2,5 . Raṃsisaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462097,107,2729,2,8,1,68,5,Pabbate {himavantamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato raṃsisaññakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462098,107,2729,9,38,1,280,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tesu tesu bhavesu vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā gharāvāsaṃ pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā ajinacammadharo himavantamhi vāsaṃ kappesi. 
462099,107,2729,39,44,1,47,5,Tasmiṃ samaye vipassī bhagavā himavantamagamāsi. 
462100,107,2729,45,61,1,155,15,Atha so tāpaso tamupagataṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā tassa bhagavato sarīrato nikkhantachabbaṇṇabuddharaṃsīsu pasīditvā añjaliṃ paggayha pañcaṅgena namakkāramakāsi. 
462101,107,2729,62,89,1,252,27,So teneva puññena ito cuto tusitādīsu dibbasampattiyo anubhavitvā aparabhāge manussasampattiyo ca anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā tatthādīnavaṃ disvā gehaṃ pahāya pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462102,107,2730,2,16,1,113,10,30. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento pabbate {himavantamhī}tiādimāha. 
462103,107,2730,17,36,1,126,16,"Tattha {pabbate}ti pakārena brūhati vaḍḍhetīti pabbato, himo assa atthīti himavanto, himavanto ca so pabbato cāti himavantapabbato. "
462104,107,2730,37,48,1,80,7,Himavantapabbateti vattabbe gāthāvacanasukhatthaṃ‘‘ pabbate himavantamhī’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
462105,107,2730,49,57,1,64,8,Tasmiṃ himavantamhi pabbate vāsaṃ kappesiṃ pure ahanti sambandho. 
462106,107,2730,58,62,1,41,4,Sesaṃ sabbattha nayānusārena uttānamevāti. 
462107,107,2731,2,4,1,40,2,Raṃsisaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462108,107,2732,2,4,1,38,2,6 . Dutiyaraṃsisaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462109,107,2733,2,9,1,74,5,Pabbate {himavantamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato dutiyaraṃsisaññakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462110,107,2733,10,37,1,290,27,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katakusalo uppannuppannabhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto phussassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā tattha dosaṃ disvā taṃ pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavantapabbate vasanto vākacīranivasano vivekasukhena viharati. 
462111,107,2733,38,89,1,485,49,Tasmiṃ samaye so phussaṃ bhagavantaṃ taṃ padesaṃ sampattaṃ disvā tassa sarīrato nikkhantachabbaṇṇabuddharaṃsiyo ito cito vidhāvantiyo daṇḍadīpikānikkhantavipphurantamiva disvā tasmiṃ pasanno añjaliṃ paggahetvā vanditvā cittaṃ pasādetvā teneva pītisomanassena kālaṃ katvā tusitādīsu nibbatto tattha cha kāmāvacarasampattiyo ca anubhavitvā aparabhāge manussasampattiyo ca anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto pubbavāsanāvasena pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462112,107,2734,2,15,1,106,9,35. So aparabhāge pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento pabbate {himavantamhī}tiādimāha. 
462113,107,2734,16,19,1,27,3,Taṃ sabbaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
462114,107,2735,2,4,1,46,2,Dutiyaraṃsisaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462115,107,2736,2,4,1,31,2,7 . Phaladāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462116,107,2737,2,8,1,67,5,Pabbate {himavantamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato phaladāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462117,107,2737,9,33,1,241,24,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katakusalasambhāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto phussassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto sukhappatto taṃ sabbaṃ pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā kharājinacammadhārī hutvā viharati. 
462118,107,2737,34,46,1,106,12,Tasmiñca samaye phussaṃ bhagavantaṃ tattha sampattaṃ disvā pasannamānaso madhurāni phalāni gahetvā bhojesi. 
462119,107,2737,47,65,1,173,18,So teneva kusalena devalokādīsu puññasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya satthari pasīditvā pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462120,107,2738,2,15,1,103,9,39. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ anussaritvā pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento pabbate {himavantamhī}tiādimāha. 
462121,107,2738,16,21,1,47,5,Taṃ sabbaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayattā uttānatthamevāti. 
462122,107,2739,2,4,1,39,2,Phaladāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462123,107,2740,2,4,1,32,2,8 . Saddasaññakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462124,107,2741,2,8,1,68,5,Pabbate {himavantamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato saddasaññakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462125,107,2741,9,68,1,550,56,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto phussassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto saddhājāto tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavantamhi araññāvāse vasanto attano anukampāya upagatassa bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā dhammesu cittaṃ pasādetvā yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā aparabhāge kālaṃ katvā tusitādīsu chasu kāmāvacarasampattiyo ca manussesu manussasampattiyo ca anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya saddhājāto pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
462126,107,2742,2,16,1,113,10,43. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento pabbate {himavantamhī}tiādimāha. 
462127,107,2742,17,20,1,27,3,Taṃ sabbaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
