462163,107,2760,2,4,1,29,2,2 . Sucintikattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462164,107,2761,2,8,1,66,5,Tissassa {lokanāthassā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato sucintikattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462165,107,2761,9,31,1,240,22,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro anekāsu jātīsu nibbānādhigamāya puññaṃ upacinitvā tissassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya satthari pasīditvā satthu nisīdanatthāya parisuddhaṃ siliṭṭhaṃ kaṭṭhamayamanagghapīṭhamadāsi. 
462166,107,2761,32,51,1,182,19,So tena puññakammena sugatisukhamanubhavitvā tattha tattha saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
