462188,107,2773,11,23,1,107,11,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto mahaddhano mahābhogo ahosi. 
462189,107,2773,24,34,1,109,10,So satthari pasīditvā candanāgarukappūrakassaturādīni anekāni sugandhāni vaḍḍhetvā satthu gandhathūpaṃ kāresi. 
462190,107,2773,35,42,1,67,6,"Tassupari sumanapupphehi chādesi, buddhañca aṭṭhaṅganamakkāraṃ akāsi. "
462191,107,2773,43,62,1,186,19,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu sampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462192,107,2774,2,16,1,116,10,24. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento siddhatthassa {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
