462205,107,2780,2,4,1,32,2,7 . Madhupiṇḍikattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462206,107,2781,2,9,1,67,6,Vivane kānane {disvā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato madhupiṇḍikattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462207,107,2781,10,26,1,165,16,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle nesādayoniyaṃ nibbatto mahāaraññe paṭivasati. 
462208,107,2781,27,38,1,111,11,Tadā vivekābhiratiyā sampattaṃ siddhatthaṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā samādhito vuṭṭhitassa tassa sumadhuraṃ madhumadāsi. 
462209,107,2781,39,44,1,40,5,Tattha ca pasannamānaso vanditvā pakkāmi. 
462210,107,2781,45,63,1,168,18,So teneva puññena sampattiṃ anubhavanto devamanussesu saṃsaritvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462211,107,2782,2,17,1,112,11,37. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento vivane kānane {disvā}tiādimāha. 
462212,107,2782,18,39,1,185,18,"Tattha {vivane}ti visesena vanaṃ patthaṭaṃ vivanaṃ, hatthiassarathasaddehi bherisaddehi ca vatthukāmakilesakāmehi ca vigataṃ byāpagatanti attho, kānanasaṅkhāte mahāaraññe vivaneti sambandho. "
462213,107,2782,40,47,1,80,7,Osadhiṃva virocantan ti bhavavaḍḍhakijanānaṃ icchiticchitaṃ nipphādetīti osadhaṃ. 
462214,107,2782,48,57,1,81,9,Ojānibbattikāraṇaṃ paṭicca yāya tārakāya uggatāya uddharanti gaṇhantīti sā osadhi. 
462215,107,2782,58,73,1,93,10,Osadhitārakā iva virocantīti vattabbe gāthābandhasukhatthaṃ‘‘ osadhiṃva virocantan’’ ti ca vuttaṃ. 
