462230,107,2791,2,4,1,34,2,10 . Buddhupaṭṭhākattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462231,107,2792,2,9,1,70,5,Vipassissa {bhagavato}tiādikaṃ āyasmato buddhupaṭṭhākattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462232,107,2792,10,37,1,258,26,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle saṅkhadhamakakule nibbatto vuddhimanvāya attano sippe saṅkhadhamane cheko ahosi, niccakālaṃ bhagavato saṅkhaṃ dhametvā saṅkhasaddeneva pūjesi. "
462233,107,2792,38,70,1,270,28,"So tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto sabbattha pākaṭo mahāghoso mahānādī madhurassaro ahosi, imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ pākaṭakule nibbatto vuddhippatto {madhurassaro}ti pākaṭo, satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi, aparabhāge madhurassarattheroti pākaṭo. "
462234,107,2793,2,17,1,113,10,51. So ekadivasaṃ attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento vipassissa {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
462235,107,2793,18,21,1,20,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttameva. 
462236,107,2793,22,36,1,116,12,"Ahosiṃ {saṅkhadhamako}ti saṃ suṭṭhu khananto gacchatīti saṅkho, samuddajalapariyante caramāno gacchati vicaratīti attho. "
462237,107,2793,37,48,1,86,10,"Taṃ saṅkhaṃ dhamati ghosaṃ karotīti saṅkhadhamako, sohaṃ saṅkhadhamakova ahosinti attho. "
462238,107,2793,49,52,1,28,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānamevāti. 
