462254,107,2802,2,4,1,31,2,2 . Ñāṇasaññikattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462255,107,2803,2,9,1,73,6,Suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ sambuddhan tiādikaṃ āyasmato ñāṇasaññikattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462256,107,2803,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
462257,107,2803,13,44,1,331,31,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya saddhājāto saddhammassavane sādaro sālayo bhagavato dhammadesanānusārena ñāṇaṃ pesetvā ghosapamāṇattā bhagavato ñāṇe pasanno pañcaṅgaaṭṭhaṅganamakkāravasena paṇāmaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
462258,107,2803,45,76,1,287,29,So tato cuto devalokesu uppanno tattha cha kāmāvacare dibbasampattimanubhavanto tato cavitvā manussaloke jāto tatthaggabhūtā cakkavattisampadādayo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462259,107,2804,2,16,1,119,11,7. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ sambuddhan tiādimāha. 
