462406,107,2863,2,11,1,71,6,Vipassī nāma {bhagavā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato suvaṇṇapupphiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462407,107,2863,12,37,1,243,25,Ayampi purimajinavaresu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ ṭhāne bhūmaṭṭhakadevaputto hutvā nibbatto tassa bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā pasannamānaso catūhi suvaṇṇapupphehi pūjesi. 
462408,107,2863,38,54,1,119,15,"Tāni pupphāni ākāse suvaṇṇavitānaṃ hutvā chādesuṃ, suvaṇṇapabhā ca buddhassa sarīrapabhā ca ekato hutvā mahāobhāso ahosi. "
462409,107,2863,55,61,1,54,6,So atirekataraṃ pasanno sakabhavanaṃ gatopi saratiyeva. 
462410,107,2863,62,85,1,218,23,So tena puññakammena tusitabhavanādisugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto dibbasampattiṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā sāsane uraṃ datvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462411,107,2864,2,17,1,113,11,40. So aparabhāge pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento vipassī nāma {bhagavā}tiādimāha. 
462412,107,2864,18,21,1,24,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttatthameva. 
