462422,107,2869,17,28,1,75,8,"{Rājāyatane}ti devarājūnaṃ āyatanaṃ rājāyatanaṃ, tassa rukkhassa nāmadheyyo vā. "
462423,107,2869,29,41,1,151,11,Parinibbute {bhagavatī}ti parisamantato kiñci anavasesetvā khandhaparinibbānakāle parinibbānasamaye parinibbānappattassa sikhino lokabandhunoti sambandho. 
