462431,107,2873,29,34,1,42,5,Tadā vipassī bhagavā āyusaṅkhāraṃ vossajji. 
462432,107,2873,35,39,1,59,4,Atha sakaladasasahassilokadhātu sasāgarapabbatā pakampittha. 
462433,107,2873,40,45,1,44,5,Tadā tassa devaputtassa bhavanampi kampittha. 
462434,107,2873,46,52,1,37,5,Tasmiṃ khaṇe so devaputto saṃsayajāto–
462435,107,2873,53,70,1,118,13,‘‘ kiṃ nu kho pathavīkampāya nibbattī’’ ti cintetvā buddhassa āyusaṅkhāravossajjabhāvaṃ ñatvā mahāsokaṃ domanassaṃ uppādesi. 
462436,107,2873,71,83,1,58,8,Tadā vessavaṇo mahārājā āgantvā‘‘ mā cintayitthā’’ ti assāsesi. 
