462447,107,2878,8,37,1,255,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tato oraṃ tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle himavante devaputto hutvā nibbatto araññaṃ gantvā maggamūḷhānaṃ maggaṃ gavesantānaṃ tassa sāvakānaṃ bhojetvā maggaṃ ācikkhi. 
462448,107,2878,38,47,1,97,9,So tena puññena devamanussasampattimanubhavitvā uppannuppannabhave sabbattha amūḷho saññavā ahosi. 
462449,107,2878,48,61,1,111,13,Atha imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto gharāvāse anallīno pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
