462462,107,2884,2,23,1,124,15,"73. Dulladdhaṃ vata me {āsī}ti me mayā laddhayasaṃ dulladdhaṃ, buddhabhūtassa satthuno sakkāraṃ akatattā virādhetvā laddhanti attho. "
