462478,107,2893,2,4,1,29,2,1 . Sereyyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462479,107,2894,2,10,1,65,5,Ajjhāyako {mantadharo}tiādikaṃ āyasmato sereyyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462480,107,2894,11,46,1,357,35,Ayampi purimajinavaresu katādhikāro tato paresu attabhāvasahassesu vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāraṃ gantvā itihāsādisakalabrāhmaṇadhammesu koṭippatto ekasmiṃ divase abbhokāse saparivāro ṭhito bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso sereyyapupphaṃ gahetvā ākāse khipanto pūjesi. 
462481,107,2894,47,56,1,71,9,Tāni pupphāni ākāse vitānaṃ hutvā sattāhaṃ ṭhatvā pacchā antaradhāyiṃsu. 
462482,107,2894,57,87,1,293,30,So taṃ acchariyaṃ disvā atīva pasannamānaso teneva pītisomanassena kālaṃ katvā tusitādīsu nibbatto tattha dibbasukhamanubhavitvā tato manussasukhamanubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ pāpuṇitvā pubbavāsanābalena satthari pasanno pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462483,107,2895,2,15,1,110,9,1. So aparabhāge purākatakusalaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento ajjhāyako {mantadharo}tiādimāha. 
462484,107,2895,16,19,1,24,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttatthameva. 
462485,107,2896,2,20,1,117,12,"3. Sereyyakaṃ {gahetvānā}ti sirise bhavaṃ jātipupphaṃ sereyyaṃ, sereyyameva sereyyakaṃ, taṃ sereyyakaṃ gahetvānāti sambandho. "
462486,107,2896,21,37,1,157,16,Bhagavati pasanno jātisumanamakuḷacampakādīni pupphāni patiṭṭhapetvā pūjetuṃ kālaṃ natthitāya tattha sampattaṃ taṃ sereyyakaṃ pupphaṃ gahetvā pūjesinti attho. 
