462489,107,2898,2,4,1,33,2,2 . Pupphathūpiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462490,107,2899,2,8,1,67,4,{Himavantassāvidūre}tiādikaṃ āyasmato pupphathūpiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462491,107,2899,9,49,1,387,38,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassibuddhassa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā sakasippe nipphattiṃ patto tattha sāraṃ apassanto gehaṃ pahāya himavantaṃ pavisitvā attanā sahagatehi pañcasissasahassehi saddhiṃ pañcābhiññā aṭṭha samāpattiyo nibbattetvā kukkuranāmapabbatasamīpe paṇṇasālaṃ kāretvā paṭivasati. 
462492,107,2899,50,81,1,305,31,Tadā buddhuppādabhāvaṃ sutvā sissehi saha buddhassa santikaṃ gantukāmo kenaci byādhinā pīḷito paṇṇasālaṃ pavisitvā sissasantikā buddhassānubhāvaṃ lakkhaṇañca sutvā pasannamānaso himavantato campakāsokatilakakeṭakādyaneke pupphe āharāpetvā thūpaṃ katvā buddhaṃ viya pūjetvā kālaṃ katvā brahmalokūpago ahosi. 
462493,107,2899,82,93,1,78,11,Atha te sissā tassa āḷahanaṃ katvā buddhasantikaṃ gantvā taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesuṃ. 
462494,107,2899,94,100,1,72,6,Atha bhagavā buddhacakkhunā oloketvā anāgataṃsañāṇena pākaṭīkaraṇamakāsi. 
462495,107,2899,101,117,1,148,16,So aparabhāge imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto pubbavāsanābalena satthari pasanno pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462496,107,2900,2,15,1,106,9,10. Atha so attano pubbakusalaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento {himavantassāvidūre}tiādimāha. 
462497,107,2900,16,19,1,24,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttatthameva. 
462498,107,2900,20,46,1,187,20,"Kukkuro nāma {pabbato}ti pabbatassa sikharaṃ kukkurākārena sunakhākārena saṇṭhitattā‘‘ kukkurapabbato’’ ti saṅkhyaṃ gato, tassa samīpe paṇṇasālaṃ katvā pañcatāpasasahassehi saha vasamānoti attho. "
462499,107,2900,47,51,1,42,4,Nayānusārena sesaṃ sabbaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
