462502,107,2903,2,8,1,70,5,Suvaṇṇavaṇṇo {sambuddho}tiādikaṃ āyasmato pāyasadāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462503,107,2903,9,45,1,393,35,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ vibhavasampanne kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā gharāvāsaṃ vasanto hatthiassadhanadhaññasattaratanādivibhavasampanno saddhāsampanno kammaphalaṃ saddahitvā sahassamattā suvaṇṇapātiyo kāretvā tasmiṃ khīrapāyasasahassassa pūretvā tā sabbā gāhāpetvā simbalivanaṃ agamāsi. 
462504,107,2903,46,56,1,91,10,Tasmiṃ samaye vipassī bhagavā chabbaṇṇaraṃsiyo vissajjetvā ākāse caṅkamaṃ māpetvā caṅkamati. 
462505,107,2903,57,70,1,96,13,So pana seṭṭhi taṃ acchariyaṃ disvā atīva pasanno pātiyo ṭhapetvā vanditvā ārocesi paṭiggahaṇāya. 
462506,107,2903,71,91,1,187,17,"Atha bhagavā anukampaṃ upādāya paṭiggahesi, paṭiggahetvā ca pana tassa somanussuppādanatthaṃ sahassamattehi bhikkhusaṅghehi saddhiṃ paribhuñji, tadavasesaṃ anekasahassabhikkhū paribhuñjiṃsu. "
462507,107,2903,92,109,1,138,16,So tena puññena sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto saddhājāto pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462508,107,2904,2,18,1,131,12,26. So aparabhāge attano kusalaṃ paccavekkhamāno taṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento suvaṇṇavaṇṇo {sambuddho}tiādimāha. 
462509,107,2904,19,22,1,20,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttameva. 
462510,107,2905,2,27,1,199,19,"28. Caṅkamaṃ {susamārūḷho}ti cadinanto padavikkhepaṃ karonto kamati gacchatīti caṅkamaṃ, caṅkamassa padavikkhepassa ādhārabhūtapathavipadeso caṅkamaṃ nāmāti attho, etaṃ caṅkamaṃsu visesena ārūḷhoti sambandho. "
462511,107,2905,28,43,1,103,12,"Ambare {anilāyane}ti varīyati chādiyati anenāti varaṃ, na baranti ambaraṃ, setavatthasadisaṃ ākāsanti attho. "
