462528,107,2912,53,74,1,203,21,So tena kusalakammena cha kāmāvacarasampattiyo anubhavitvā manussesu ca cakkavattisampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto saddhājāto pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
