462534,107,2915,2,4,1,32,2,6 . Kusumāsaniyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462535,107,2916,2,8,1,67,5,Nagare {dhaññavatiyā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato kusumāsaniyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462536,107,2916,9,74,1,646,63,Ayampi purimajinavaresu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbatto viññutaṃ patto mahaddhano mahābhogo tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāraṃ gato brāhmaṇasippesu koṭippatto sakaparasamayakusalo mātāpitaro pūjetukāmo pañca uppalakalāpe attano samīpe ṭhapetvā nisinno bhikkhusaṅghaparivutaṃ vipassiṃ bhagavantaṃ āgacchantaṃ disvā nīlapītādighanabuddharasmiyo ca disvā pasannamānaso āsanaṃ paññāpetvā tattha tāni pupphāni santharitvā bhagavantaṃ tattha nisīdāpetvā sakaghare mātu atthāya paṭiyattāni sabbāni khādanīyabhojanīyāni gahetvā saparivāraṃ bhagavantaṃ sahatthena santappento bhojesi. 
462537,107,2916,75,79,1,38,4,Bhojanāvasāne ekaṃ uppalahatthaṃ adāsi. 
462538,107,2916,80,84,1,34,4,Tena somanassajāto patthanaṃ akāsi. 
462539,107,2916,85,89,1,33,4,Bhagavāpi anumodanaṃ katvā pakāmi. 
462540,107,2916,90,117,1,236,27,So tena puññena devamanussesu dve sampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kule nibbatto viññutaṃ patto bhogayasehi vaḍḍhito kāmesu ādīnavaṃ disvā gharāvāsaṃ pahāya pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462541,107,2917,2,17,1,131,11,65. So aparabhāge pubbe katakusalaṃ pubbenivāsañāṇena saritvā somanassappatto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nagare {dhaññavatiyā}tiādimāha. 
462542,107,2917,18,46,1,312,24,"Dhaññānaṃ puññavantānaṃ khattiyabrāhmaṇagahapatimahāsālānaṃ anekesaṃ kulānaṃ ākarattā dhaññavatī, atha vā muttāmaṇiādisattaratanānaṃ sattavidhadhaññānaṃ upabhogaparibhogānaṃ ākarattā dhaññavatī, atha vā dhaññānaṃ buddhapaccekabuddhakhīṇāsavānaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ ārāmavihārādīnaṃ ākarattā dhaññavatī, tassā dhaññavatiyā. "
462543,107,2917,47,61,1,128,12,"Nagaranti patthenti ettha upabhogaparibhogatthikā janāti nagaraṃ, na gacchatīti vā nagaṃ, rājayuvarājamahāmattādīnaṃ vasanaṭṭhānaṃ. "
462544,107,2917,62,76,1,142,13,"Nagaṃ rāti ādadāti gaṇhātīti nagaraṃ, rājādīnaṃ vasanaṭṭhānasamūhabhūtaṃ pākāraparikhādīhi parikkhittaṃ paricchinnaṭṭhānaṃ nagaraṃ nāmāti attho. "
462545,107,2917,77,93,1,124,15,"Nagare yadā ahaṃ vipassissa bhagavato santike byākaraṇaṃ alabhiṃ, tadā tasmiṃ dhaññavatiyā nagare brāhmaṇo ahosinti sambandho. "
