462570,107,2928,9,32,1,233,23,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro anekāsu jātīsu katapuññasañcayo vipassissa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto upabhogaparibhogehi anūno ekadivasaṃ vipassiṃ bhagavantaṃ sagaṇaṃ disvā pasannamānaso lājāpañcamehi pupphehi pūjesi. 
462571,107,2928,33,57,1,240,24,So teneva cittappasādena yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato devaloke nibbatto dibbasampattiṃ anubhavitvā aparabhāge manussesu manussasampattiṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto saddhājāto pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
