462576,107,2932,2,8,1,66,4,{Himavantassāvidūre}tiādikaṃ āyasmato padumapūjakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462577,107,2932,9,56,1,444,45,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā sakasippe nipphattiṃ patvā tattha sāraṃ apassanto buddhuppattito puretaraṃ uppannattā ovādānusāsanaṃ alabhitvā gharāvāsaṃ pahāya isipabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavantassa avidūre gotamakaṃ nāma pabbataṃ nissāya assamaṃ kāretvā pañcābhiññā aṭṭha samāpattiyo nibbattetvā jhānasukheneva vihāsi. 
462578,107,2932,57,68,1,98,11,Tadā padumuttaro bhagavā buddho hutvā satte saṃsārato uddharanto tassānukampāya himavantaṃ agamāsi. 
462579,107,2932,69,79,1,96,10,Tāpaso bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso sakasisse samānetvā tehi padumapupphāni āharāpetvā pūjesi. 
462580,107,2932,80,98,1,169,18,So tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ kulagehe nibbatto saddho pasanno pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462581,107,2933,2,14,1,100,8,97. So attano puññakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento {himavantassāvidūre}tiādimāha. 
462582,107,2933,15,28,1,119,12,Gotamo nāma {pabbato}ti anekesaṃ yakkhadevatānaṃ āvāsabhāvena adhiṭṭhānavasena gotamassa bhavanattā gotamoti pākaṭo ahosi. 
462583,107,2933,29,32,1,28,3,Pavattati tiṭṭhatīti pabbato. 
462584,107,2933,33,39,1,49,5,Nāgarukkhehi {sañchanno}ti ruhati tiṭṭhatīti rukkho. 
462585,107,2933,40,61,1,186,19,"Atha vā pathaviṃ khananto uddhaṃ ruhatīti rukkho, nānā anekappakārā campakakappūranāgaagarucandanādayo rukkhāti nānārukkhā, tehi nānārukkhehi sañchanno parikiṇṇo gotamo pabbatoti sambandho. "
462586,107,2933,62,87,1,196,21,"{Mahābhūtagaṇālayo}ti bhavanti jāyanti uppajjanti vaḍḍhanti cāti bhūtā, mahantā ca te bhūtā cāti mahābhūtā, mahābhūtānaṃ gaṇo samūhoti mahābhūtagaṇo, mahābhūtagaṇassa ālayo patiṭṭhāti mahābhūtagaṇālayo. "
462587,107,2934,2,19,1,114,13,98. Vemajjhamhi ca {tassāsī}ti tassa gotamassa pabbatassa vemajjhe abbhantare assamo abhinimmito nipphādito katoti attho. 
