462595,107,2939,41,66,1,231,25,So teneva somanassena kālaṃ katvā devesu nibbatto tattha dibbasukhaṃ anubhavitvā manussesu ca manussasukhaṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ kulagehe nibbatto sattavassikova pabbajitvā nacirasseva chaḷabhiñño arahā ahosi. 
