462650,107,2964,2,4,1,35,2,7 . Atthasandassakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462651,107,2965,2,8,1,67,5,Visālamāḷe {āsīno}tiādikaṃ āyasmato atthasandassakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462652,107,2965,9,47,1,392,37,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro anekesu attabhāvesu katapuññūpacayo padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbatto vuddhimanvāya sakasippesu nipphattiṃ patto tattha sāraṃ apassanto gehaṃ pahāya himavantaṃ gantvā ramaṇīye ṭhāne paṇṇasālaṃ katvā paṭivasati, tadā sattānukampāya himavantamāgataṃ padumuttarabhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso pañcaṅgasamannāgato vanditvā thutivacanehi thomesi. "
462653,107,2965,48,56,1,65,8,So tena puññena yāvatāyukaṃ katvā kālaṅkatvā brahmalokūpago ahosi. 
462654,107,2965,57,72,1,138,15,So aparabhāge imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
462655,107,2966,2,16,1,98,9,47. So attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento visālamāḷe {āsīno}tiādimāha. 
462656,107,2966,17,36,1,144,16,"Tattha {visālamāḷe}ti visālaṃ patthaṭaṃ vitthiṇṇaṃ mahantaṃ māḷaṃ visālamāḷaṃ, tasmiṃ visālamāḷe āsīno nisinno ahaṃ lokanāyakaṃ addasanti sambandho. "
462657,107,2966,37,39,1,22,2,Tesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
462658,107,2967,2,4,1,43,2,Atthasandassakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462659,107,2968,2,4,1,33,2,8 . Ekapasādaniyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462660,107,2969,2,10,1,70,8,Nārado iti me nāman tiādikaṃ āyasmato ekapasādaniyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462661,107,2969,11,41,1,287,30,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro anekāsu jātīsu katakusalo atthadassissa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbatto kesavoti pākaṭo hutvā viññutaṃ patvā gharāvāsaṃ pahāya pabbajitvā vasanto ekadivasaṃ satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā pasannamānaso añjaliṃ paggayha ativiya pītisomanassajāto pakkāmi. 
462662,107,2969,42,71,1,267,29,So yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā teneva somanassena kālaṃ katvā devesu nibbatto tattha dibbasampattiṃ anubhavitvā manussesu uppanno tattha sampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde aññatarasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto satthari pasīditvā pabbajito nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462663,107,2970,2,19,1,119,13,55. So aparabhāge attano katakusalakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nārado iti me nāman tiādimāha. 
462664,107,2970,20,38,1,134,16,"Tattha {nārado}ti jātivasena suddhasarīrattā natthi rajo dhūli malaṃ etassāti nārado, ja-kārassa da-kāraṃ katvā nāradoti kuladattikaṃ nāmaṃ. "
462665,107,2970,39,51,1,86,11,{Kesavo}ti kisavacchagotte jātattā kesavo nāradakesavo iti maṃ janā vidū jānantīti attho. 
462666,107,2970,52,54,1,18,2,Sesaṃ pākaṭamevāti. 
462667,107,2971,2,4,1,41,2,Ekapasādaniyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462668,107,2972,2,4,1,36,2,9 . Sālapupphadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462669,107,2973,2,10,1,72,7,Migarājā tadā āsin tiādikaṃ āyasmato sālapupphadāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462670,107,2973,11,25,1,149,14,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave katakusalasañcayo kenaci kammacchiddena himavante sīhayoniyaṃ nibbatto anekasīhaparivāro vihāsi. 
462671,107,2973,26,32,1,52,6,Tadā sikhī bhagavā tassānukampāya himavantaṃ agamāsi. 
462672,107,2973,33,42,1,87,9,Sīho taṃ upagataṃ disvā pasannamānaso sākhābhaṅgena sakaṇṇikasālapupphaṃ gahetvā pūjesi. 
462673,107,2973,43,47,1,30,4,Bhagavā tassa anumodanaṃ akāsi. 
462674,107,2974,2,35,1,274,29,60. So tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā satthari pasanno pabbajitvā arahattaṃ patto attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento migarājā tadā āsin tiādimāha. 
462675,107,2974,36,51,1,94,13,"Tattha maraṇaṃ gacchantīti migā, atha vā ghāsaṃ magganti gavesantīti migā, migānaṃ rājā migarājā. "
462676,107,2974,52,61,1,91,9,Sakalacatuppadānaṃ rājabhāve satipi gāthābandhasukhatthaṃ mige ādiṃ katvā migarājāti vuttaṃ. 
462677,107,2974,62,75,1,95,12,"Yadā bhagavantaṃ disvā sapupphaṃ sālasākhaṃ bhañjitvā pūjesiṃ, tadā ahaṃ migarājā ahosinti attho. "
462678,107,2975,2,13,1,70,8,62. Sakosaṃ pupphamāharin ti sakaṇṇikaṃ sālapupphaṃ āhariṃ pūjesinti attho. 
462679,107,2975,14,16,1,22,2,Sesaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
462680,107,2976,2,4,1,44,2,Sālapupphadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462681,107,2977,2,4,1,37,2,10 . Piyālaphaladāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462682,107,2978,2,10,1,74,7,Parodhako tadā āsin tiādikaṃ āyasmato piyālaphaladāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462683,107,2978,11,33,1,200,22,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sikhissa bhagavato kāle nesādakule nibbatto himavante ekasmiṃ pabbhāre mige vadhitvā jīvikaṃ kappetvā vasati. 
462684,107,2978,34,53,1,156,18,Tasmiṃ kāle tattha gataṃ sikhiṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso sāyaṃ pātaṃ namassamāno kañci deyyadhammaṃ apassanto madhurāni piyālaphalāni uccinitvā adāsi. 
462685,107,2978,54,57,1,23,3,Bhagavā tāni paribhuñji. 
462686,107,2978,58,72,1,136,14,So nesādo buddhārammaṇāya pītiyā nirantaraṃ phuṭṭhasarīro pāpakamme virattacitto mūlaphalāhāro nacirasseva kālaṃ katvā devaloke nibbatti. 
462687,107,2979,2,43,1,378,38,66. So tattha dibbasampattiyo anubhavitvā manussesu ca anekavidhasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde gahapatikule nibbatto viññutaṃ patto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā tattha anabhirato gehaṃ pahāya satthu santike pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ patto attano kataphaladānakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento parodhako tadā āsin tiādimāha. 
462688,107,2979,44,57,1,89,12,"Tattha yadā ahaṃ piyālaphalaṃ datvā cittaṃ pasādesiṃ, tadā ahaṃ parodhako āsinti sambandho. "
462689,107,2979,58,62,1,37,3,{Parodhako}ti parasattarodhako vihesako.
462690,107,2979,63,81,1,74,10,‘‘ Pararodhako’’ ti vattabbe pubbassa ra-kārassa lopaṃ katvā‘‘ parodhako’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
462691,107,2980,2,27,1,124,15,"69. Paricāriṃ vināyakan ti taṃ nibbānapāpakaṃ satthāraṃ,‘‘ bhante , imaṃ phalaṃ paribhuñjathā’’ ti pavāriṃ nimantesiṃ ārādhesinti attho. "
462692,107,2980,28,30,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
462693,107,2981,2,4,1,45,2,Piyālaphaladāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā. 
462694,107,2982,2,4,1,29,2,Cuddasamavaggavaṇṇanā samattā.
462695,107,2983,2,4,1,11,2,15 . Chattavaggo
462696,107,2984,2,4,1,31,2,1 . Atichattiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462697,107,2985,2,9,1,68,5,Parinibbute {bhagavatī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato atichattiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462698,107,2985,10,55,1,355,37,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto atthadassissa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto dharamānassa bhagavato adiṭṭhattā parinibbutakāle‘‘ aho mama parihānī’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ mama jātiṃ saphalaṃ karissāmī’’ ti katasanniṭṭhāno chattādhichattaṃ kāretvā tassa bhagavato sarīradhātuṃ nihitadhātugabbhaṃ pūjesi. 
462699,107,2985,56,63,1,60,6,Aparabhāge pupphacchattaṃ kāretvā tameva dhātugabbhaṃ pūjesi. 
462700,107,2985,64,86,1,216,22,So teneva puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde gahapatikule nibbatto viññutaṃ patto satthari pasanno pabbajitvā kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā vāyamanto nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
462701,107,2986,2,15,1,103,9,1. So attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento parinibbute {bhagavatī}tiādimāha. 
462702,107,2986,16,35,1,167,17,"Tattha chattātichattan ti chādiyati saṃvariyati ātapādinti chattaṃ, chattassa atichattaṃ chattassa upari katachattaṃ chattātichattaṃ, chattassa uparūpari chattanti attho. "
462703,107,2986,36,66,1,239,28,"Thūpamhi abhiropayin ti thūpiyati rāsikarīyatīti thūpo, atha vā thūpati thirabhāvena vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjamāno patiṭṭhātīti thūpo, tasmiṃ thūpamhi mayā kāritaṃ chattaṃ uparūpari ṭhapanavasena abhi visesena āropayiṃ pūjesinti attho. "
462704,107,2987,2,18,1,115,12,2. Pupphacchadanaṃ {katvānā}ti vikasitehi sugandhehi anekehi phupphehi chadanaṃ chattupari vitānaṃ katvā pūjesinti attho. 
462705,107,2987,19,22,1,32,3,Sesaṃ sabbattha uttānatthamevāti. 
462706,107,2988,2,4,1,39,2,Atichattiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462707,107,2989,2,4,1,33,2,2 . Thambhāropakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462708,107,2990,2,9,1,69,5,Nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato thambhāropakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462709,107,2990,10,36,1,245,25,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto dhammadassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto saddho pasanno parinibbute bhagavati tassa bhagavato dhātugabbhamāḷake thambhaṃ nikhanitvā dhajaṃ āropesi. 
462710,107,2990,37,43,1,61,6,Bahūni jātisumanapupphāni ganthitvā nisseṇiyā ārohitvā pūjesi. 
462711,107,2991,2,41,1,347,34,5. So yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā kālaṃ katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā sabbattha pūjito imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto daharakālato pabhuti pūjanīyo sāsane baddhasaddho pabbajitvā saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ patto attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādimāha. 
462712,107,2991,42,59,1,159,16,Tattha nibbute {lokanāthamhī}ti sakalalokassa nāthe padhānabhūte paṭisaraṇe ca satthari khandhaparinibbānena nibbute nibbutadīpasikhā viya adassanaṃ gateti attho. 
462713,107,2991,60,89,1,277,24,"{Dhammadassīnarāsabhe}ti catusaccadhammaṃ passatīti dhammadassī, atha vā satipaṭṭhānādike sattatiṃsabodhipakkhiyadhamme dassanasīlo passanasīloti dhammadassī, narānaṃ āsabho pavaro uttamoti narāsabho, dhammadassī ca so narāsabho ceti dhammadassīnarāsabho, tasmiṃ dhammadassīnarāsabhe. "
462714,107,2991,90,103,1,110,13,Āropesiṃ dhajaṃ thambhan ti cetiyamāḷake thambhaṃ nikhanitvā tattha dhajaṃ āropesiṃ bandhitvā ṭhapesinti attho. 
462715,107,2992,2,24,1,152,17,"6. Nisseṇiṃ {māpayitvānā}ti nissāya taṃ iṇanti gacchanti ārohanti uparīti nisseṇi, taṃ nisseṇiṃ māpayitvā kāretvā bandhitvā thūpaseṭṭhaṃ samāruhinti sambandho. "
462716,107,2992,25,66,1,287,29,"Jātipupphaṃ {gahetvānā}ti jāyamānameva janānaṃ sundaraṃ manaṃ karotīti jātisumanaṃ, jātisumanameva pupphaṃ‘‘ jātisumanapupphan’’ ti vattabbe gāthābandhasukhatthaṃ sumanasaddassa lopaṃ katvā‘‘ jātipupphan’’ ti vuttaṃ, taṃ jātisumanapupphaṃ gahetvā ganthitvā thūpamhi āropayiṃ, āropetvā pūjesinti attho. "
462717,107,2992,67,69,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
462718,107,2993,2,4,1,41,2,Thambhāropakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462719,107,2994,2,4,1,30,2,3 . Vedikārakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462720,107,2995,2,9,1,66,5,Nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato vedikārakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462721,107,2995,10,43,1,296,32,"Ayampi purimajinavaresu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto piyadassissa bhagavato kāle vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kule nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā nibbute satthari pasanno tassa cetiye valayaṃ kāresi, sattahi ratanehi paripūretvā mahāpūjaṃ kāresi. "
462722,107,2995,44,67,1,220,22,So tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto anekesu jātisatasahassesu pūjanīyo mahaddhano mahābhogo ubhayasukhaṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kulagehe nibbatto vibhavasampanno pabbajitvā vāyamanto nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462723,107,2996,2,18,1,119,11,10. So ekadivasaṃ attano pubbe katakusalaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādimāha. 
462724,107,2996,19,22,1,24,3,Taṃ heṭṭhā vuttatthameva. 
462725,107,2996,23,37,1,196,12,"{Piyadassīnaruttame}ti piyaṃ somanassākāraṃ dassanaṃ yassa so piyadassī, ārohapariṇāhadvattiṃsamahāpurisalakkhaṇaasītānubyañjanabyāmappabhāmaṇḍalehi sādhu mahājanappasādaṃ janayanākāradassanoti attho. "
462726,107,2996,38,57,1,160,17,"Narānaṃ uttamoti naruttamo, piyadassī ca so naruttamo ceti piyadassīnaruttamo, tasmiṃ piyadassīnaruttame nibbute dhātugabbhamhi muttavediṃ ahaṃ akāsinti sambandho. "
462727,107,2996,58,63,1,57,5,Pupphādhāratthāya pariyosāne vedikāvalayaṃ akāsinti attho. 
462728,107,2997,2,34,1,233,26,"11. Maṇīhi {parivāretvā}ti maṇati jotati pabhāsatīti maṇi, atha vā janānaṃ manaṃ pūrento somanassaṃ karonto ito gato pavattoti maṇi, jātiraṅgamaṇiveḷuriyamaṇiādīhi anekehi maṇīhi katavedikāvalayaṃ parivāretvā uttamaṃ mahāpūjaṃ akāsinti attho. "
462729,107,2997,35,37,1,22,2,Sesaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
462730,107,2998,2,4,1,38,2,Vedikārakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462731,107,2999,2,4,1,32,2,4 . Saparivāriyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462732,107,3000,2,9,1,69,6,Padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādikaṃ āyasmato saparivāriyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462733,107,3000,10,29,1,176,18,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro anekāsu jātīsu vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto mahaddhano mahābhogo ahosi. 
462734,107,3000,30,42,1,102,12,Atha padumuttare bhagavati parinibbute mahājano tassa dhātuṃ nidahitvā mahantaṃ cetiyaṃ kāretvā pūjesi. 
462735,107,3000,43,53,1,85,10,Tasmiṃ kāle ayaṃ upāsako tassupari candanasārena cetiyagharaṃ karitvā mahāpūjaṃ akāsi. 
462736,107,3000,54,75,1,196,21,So teneva puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya kusalaṃ katvā saddhāya sāsane pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
462737,107,3001,2,4,1,0,0,15-8. 
462738,107,3001,5,18,1,114,11,So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādimāha. 
462739,107,3001,19,37,1,118,16,"Tattha omattan ti lāmakabhāvaṃ nīcabhāvaṃ dukkhitabhāvaṃ vā na passāmi na jānāmi, na diṭṭhapubbo mayā nīcabhāvoti attho. "
462740,107,3001,38,40,1,18,2,Sesaṃ pākaṭamevāti. 
462741,107,3002,2,4,1,40,2,Saparivāriyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
462742,107,3003,2,4,1,31,2,5 . Umāpupphiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462743,107,3004,2,8,1,65,5,Nibbute {lokamahite}tiādikaṃ āyasmato umāpupphiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462744,107,3004,9,35,1,269,26,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto vuddhippatto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā vasanto nibbutassa bhagavato cetiyamahe vattamāne indanīlamaṇivaṇṇaṃ umāpupphaṃ gahetvā pūjesi. 
462745,107,3004,36,49,1,145,13,So tena puññena sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto dibbamānusasampattiyo anubhavitvā uppannuppannabhave bahulaṃ nīlavaṇṇo jātisampanno vibhavasampanno ahosi. 
462746,107,3004,50,64,1,129,14,So imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā saddhājāto pabbajito nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
462747,107,3005,2,15,1,96,9,21. So pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nibbute {lokamahite}tiādi vuttaṃ. 
462748,107,3005,16,30,1,119,12,"Tattha {lokamahite}ti lokehi mahito pūjitoti lokamahito, tasmiṃ lokamahite siddhatthamhi bhagavati parinibbuteti sambandho. "
462749,107,3005,31,50,1,179,15,"{Āhutīnaṃpaṭiggahe}ti āhutino vuccanti pūjāsakkārā, tesaṃ āhutīnaṃ paṭiggahetuṃ arahatīti āhutīnaṃpaṭiggaho, aluttakitantasamāso, tasmiṃ āhutīnaṃpaṭiggahe bhagavati parinibbuteti attho. "
462750,107,3006,2,22,1,130,15,"22. Umāpupphan ti uddhamuddhaṃ nīlapabhaṃ muñcamānaṃ pupphati vikasatīti umāpupphaṃ, taṃ umāpupphaṃ gahetvā cetiye pūjaṃ akāsinti attho. "
