462810,107,3031,2,11,1,74,7,Candaṃva vimalaṃ suddhan tiādikaṃ āyasmato bandhujīvakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462811,107,3031,12,42,1,296,29,Ayampāyasmā purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sikhissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā vasanto sikhissa bhagavato rūpakāyasampattiṃ disvā pasannamānaso bandhujīvakapupphāni gahetvā bhagavato pādamūle pūjesi. 
