462865,107,3054,2,34,1,303,27,30. So tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā hutvā pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento {himavantassāvidūre}tiādimāha. 
462866,107,3054,35,37,1,17,2,Taṃ vuttatthameva. 
