462938,107,3086,34,39,1,59,5,Bhagavā tassa pasādavaḍḍhanatthāya passantasseva paribhuñji. 
462939,107,3086,40,65,1,266,25,So tena puññena sugatisampattiyoyeva anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā sañjātasaddho pasādabahumāno pabbajitvā vattapaṭipattiyā sāsanaṃ sobhento sīlālaṅkārapaṭimaṇḍito nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
462940,107,3087,2,26,1,143,16,13. So pubbakammaṃ saranto‘‘ pubbe mayā sukhette kusalaṃ kataṃ sundaran’’ ti somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento tissassa kho {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
