462945,107,3087,77,97,1,181,19,Khajjakaṃ abhisammatan ti khāditabbaṃ khajjakaṃ abhi visesena madhusakkarādīhi sammissaṃ katvā nipphāditaṃ sundaraṃ madhuranti sammataṃ ñātaṃ abhisammataṃ khajjakañca adāsinti attho. 
