462995,107,3105,2,4,1,31,2,8 . Dussadāyakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
462996,107,3106,2,10,1,67,6,Tivarāyaṃ pure {ramme}tiādikaṃ āyasmato dussadāyakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
462997,107,3106,11,38,1,335,27,Ayampāyasmā purimajinavaresu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle rājakule nibbatto vuddhippattakāle yuvarājabhāvaṃ patvā pākaṭo ekaṃ janapadaṃ labhitvā tatrādhipatibhūto sakalajanapadavāsino dānapiyavacanaatthacariyāsamānatthatāsaṅkhātehi catūhi saṅgahavatthūhi saṅgaṇhāti. 
462998,107,3106,39,46,1,56,7,Tasmiṃ samaye siddhattho bhagavā taṃ janapadaṃ sampāpuṇi. 
462999,107,3106,47,57,1,78,9,Atha so yuvarājā paṇṇākāraṃ labhitvā tattha sukhumavatthena bhagavantaṃ pūjesi. 
463000,107,3106,58,65,1,57,7,Bhagavā taṃ vatthaṃ hatthena parāmasitvā ākāsaṃ pakkhandi. 
463001,107,3106,66,70,1,38,4,Tampi vatthaṃ bhagavantameva anubandhi. 
463002,107,3106,71,82,1,76,11,Atha so yuvarājā taṃ acchariyaṃ disvā atīva pasanno añjaliṃ paggayha aṭṭhāsi. 
463003,107,3106,83,94,1,111,11,Bhagavato sampattasampattaṭṭhāne sabbe janā taṃ acchariyaṃ disvā acchariyabbhutacittā añjaliṃ paggayha aṭṭhaṃsu. 
463004,107,3106,95,98,1,26,3,Bhagavā vihārameva agamāsi. 
463005,107,3106,99,133,1,344,34,Yuvarājā teneva kusalakammena tato cuto devaloke uppanno tattha dibbasampattiṃ anubhavitvā manussesu cakkavattiādisampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kule nibbatto viññutaṃ patto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā ratanattaye pasanno bhagavato dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vāyamanto nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
463006,107,3107,2,18,1,113,11,38. So ekadivasaṃ attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento tivarāyaṃ pure {ramme}tiādimāha. 
463007,107,3107,19,31,1,105,12,Tattha tivaranāmake nagare ramaṇīye ahaṃ rājaputto hutvā siddhatthaṃ bhagavantaṃ vatthena pūjesinti attho. 
