463075,107,3141,2,4,1,32,2,6 . Maggadattikattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
463076,107,3142,2,8,1,66,5,Anomadassī {bhagavā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato maggadattikattherassa apadānaṃ. 
463077,107,3142,9,47,1,371,36,"Ayampāyasmā purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto anomadassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto vuddhimanvāya gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā vasanto anomadassiṃ bhagavantaṃ ākāse caṅkamantaṃ pāduddhāre pāduddhāracaṅkamanaṭṭhāne pupphānaṃ vikiraṇaṃ acchariyañca disvā pasannamānaso pupphāni ākāse ukkhipi, tāni vitānaṃ hutvā aṭṭhaṃsu. "
463078,107,3143,2,34,1,259,27,26. So tena puññena sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto sabbattha pūjito sukhaṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde ekasmiṃ kule nibbatto kamena yobbaññaṃ pāpuṇitvā saddhājāto pabbajitvā vattasampanno nacirasseva arahattaṃ patto caṅkamanassa pūjitattā {maggadattikatthero}ti pākaṭo. 
463079,107,3143,35,44,1,93,8,So pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento anomadassī {bhagavā}tiādimāha. 
463080,107,3143,45,53,1,95,7,{Diṭṭhadhammasukhatthāyā}ti imasmiṃ attabhāve caṅkamanena sarīrasallahukādisukhaṃ paṭiccāti attho. 
463081,107,3143,54,65,1,94,9,"Abbhokāsamhi {caṅkamī}ti abbhokāse aṅgaṇaṭṭhāne caṅkami, padavikkhepaṃ padasañcāraṃ akāsīti attho. "
463082,107,3144,2,16,1,119,13,Uddhate pāde {pupphānī}ti caṅkamantena pāde uddhate padumuppalādīni pupphāni pathavito uggantvā caṅkame vikiriṃsūti attho. 
463083,107,3144,17,29,1,85,10,Sobhaṃ muddhani {tiṭṭhare}ti buddhassa muddhani sīse sobhayamānā tāni tiṭṭhantīti attho. 
463084,107,3144,30,32,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
463085,107,3145,2,4,1,40,2,Maggadattikattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
463086,107,3146,2,4,1,29,2,7 . Ekadīpiyattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
463087,107,3147,2,8,1,66,5,Padumuttarassa {munino}tiādikaṃ āyasmato ekadīpiyattherassa apadānaṃ. 
463088,107,3147,9,36,1,299,26,"Ayampāyasmā purimajinaseṭṭhesu katakusalasambhāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle gahapatikule nibbatto vuddhippatto saddho pasanno bhagavato salalamahābodhimhi ekapadīpaṃ pūjesi, thāvaraṃ katvā niccamekapadīpapūjanatthāya telavaṭṭaṃ paṭṭhapesi. "
463089,107,3147,37,66,1,302,28,So tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto sabbattha jalamāno pasannacakkhuko ubhayasukhamanubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ vibhavasampanne ekasmiṃ kule nibbatto viññutaṃ patto ratanattaye pasanno pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ patto dīpapūjāya laddhavisesādhigamattā {ekadīpiyatthero}ti pākaṭo. 
463090,107,3148,2,16,1,114,10,30. So aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttarassa {munino}tiādimāha. 
463091,107,3148,17,20,1,27,3,Taṃ sabbaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
