463093,107,3150,2,4,1,30,2,8 . Maṇipūjakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
463094,107,3151,2,10,1,64,5,Orena {himavantassā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato maṇipūjakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
463095,107,3151,11,55,1,428,43,Ayampi thero purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle ekasmiṃ kule nibbatto gharāvāsaṃ saṇṭhapetvā tatthādīnavaṃ disvā gharāvāsaṃ pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā himavantaorabhāge ekissā nadiyā samīpe paṇṇasālaṃ kāretvā vasanto vivekakāmatāya tassānukampāya ca tattha upagataṃ padumuttaraṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso maṇipallaṅkaṃ bhagavato pūjesi. 
463096,107,3151,56,61,1,48,5,Bhagavā tassa pasādavaḍḍhanatthāya tattha nisīdi. 
463097,107,3151,62,68,1,63,6,So bhiyyosomattāya pasanno nibbānādhigamatthāya patthanaṃ akāsi. 
463098,107,3151,69,73,1,32,4,Bhagavā anumodanaṃ vatvā pakkāmi. 
463099,107,3151,74,100,1,247,26,So tena puññena devamanussesu saṃsaranto sabbattha pūjito sukhaṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ vibhavasampanne kule nibbatto gharāvāsaṃ vasanto ekadivasaṃ satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā nacirasseva arahā ahosi. 
463100,107,3152,2,16,1,114,10,34. So ekadivasaṃ attanā katakusalaṃ saritvā sañjātasomanasso pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento orena {himavantassā}tiādimāha. 
463101,107,3152,17,32,1,105,12,"Tattha {orenā}ti himavantassa aparaṃ bhāgaṃ vihāya orena, bhummatthe karaṇavacanaṃ, orasmiṃ disābhāgeti attho. "
463102,107,3152,33,45,1,100,11,Nadikā {sampavattathā}ti apākaṭanāmadheyyā ekā nadī saṃsuṭṭhu pavattānī vahānī sandamānā ahosīti attho. 
463103,107,3152,46,54,1,70,7,Tassā {cānupakhettamhī}ti tassā nadiyā anupakhettamhi tīrasamīpeti attho. 
463104,107,3152,55,73,1,130,16,"Sayambhū vasate {tadā}ti yadā ahaṃ maṇipallaṅkaṃ pūjesiṃ, tadā anācariyako hutvā sayameva buddhabhūto bhagavā vasate viharatīti attho. "
463105,107,3153,2,52,1,342,44,"35. Maṇiṃ paggayha pallaṅkan ti maṇin ti cittaṃ ārādheti somanassaṃ karotīti maṇi, atha vā māti pamāṇaṃ karoti ābharaṇanti maṇi, atha vā marantāpi rājayuvarājādayo taṃ na pariccajanti tadatthāya saṅgāmaṃ karontīti maṇi, taṃ maṇiṃ maṇimayaṃ pallaṅkaṃ manoramaṃ sādhu cittaṃ suṭṭhu vicittaṃ paggayha gahetvā buddhaseṭṭhassa abhiropayiṃ pūjesinti attho. "
463106,107,3153,53,56,1,29,3,Sesaṃ sabbaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
