463990,107,3459,68,89,1,171,19,"Tesu arahattappattatthero parinibbāyi, dutiyo anāgāmī brahmaloke nibbatti, itare pañca visesaṃ nibbattetuṃ asakkontā sussitvā sattame divase kālaṃ katvā devaloke nibbattiṃsu. "
