463993,107,3459,123,162,1,354,37,"Tesu ayaṃ bāhiyo dārucīriyo suppārakapaṭṭane vāṇijakule nibbatto vāṇijakamme nipphattiṃ gato mahaddhano mahābhogo, so suvaṇṇabhūmiṃ gacchantehi vāṇijehi saddhiṃ nāvamāruyha videsaṃ gacchanto katipāhaṃ gantvā bhinnāya nāvāya sesesu macchakacchapabhakkhesu jātesu ekoyeva avasiṭṭho ekaṃ phalakaṃ gahetvā vāyamanto sattame divase suppārakapaṭṭanatīraṃ okkami. "
463994,107,3459,163,183,1,171,18,"Tassa nivāsanapārupanaṃ natthi, so aññaṃ kiñci apassanto sukkhakaṭṭhadaṇḍake vākehi paliveṭhetvā nivāsetvā pārupitvā ca devakulato kapālaṃ gahetvā suppārakapaṭṭanaṃ agamāsi. "
463995,107,3459,184,198,1,68,10,Manussā taṃ disvā yāgubhattādīni datvā‘‘ ayaṃ eko arahā’’ ti sambhāvesuṃ. 
463996,107,3459,199,220,1,124,15,"So vatthesu upanītesu‘‘ sacāhaṃ nivāsemi, pārupāmi vā, lābhasakkāro me parihāyissatī’’ ti tāni paṭikkhipitvā dārucīrāneva parihari. "
463997,107,3460,2,40,1,202,28,"Athassa ‘‘ arahā, arahā’’ ti bahūhi sambhāviyamānassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi‘‘ ye keci loke arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannā, ahaṃ tesaṃ aññataro’’ ti so tena niyāmena kuhanakammena jīvikaṃ kappeti. "
463998,107,3461,2,102,1,887,89,"Kassapadasabalassa sāsane sattasu janesu pabbataṃ āruyha samaṇadhammaṃ karontesu eko anāgāmī hutvā suddhāvāsabrahmaloke nibbattitvā attano brahmasampattiṃ olokento āgataṭṭhānaṃ āvajjento pabbatamāruyha samaṇadhammaṃ karaṇaṭṭhānaṃ disvā sesānaṃ nibbattanaṭṭhānaṃ āvajjento ekassa parinibbutabhāvaṃ itaresañca pañcannaṃ kāmāvacaradevaloke nibbattabhāvaṃ ñatvā te kālānukālaṃ āvajjesi‘‘ imasmiṃ pana kāle kahaṃ nu kho te’’ ti āvajjento dārucīriyaṃ suppārakapaṭṭanaṃ nissāya kuhanakammena jīvitaṃ kappentaṃ disvā‘‘ naṭṭho vatāyaṃ bālo, pubbe samaṇadhammaṃ karonto atiukkaṭṭhabhāvena arahatāpi ābhataṃ piṇḍapātaṃ aparibhuñjitvā idāni udarahetu anārahāva samāno arahattaṃ paṭijānitvā lokaṃ vañcento vicarati, dasabalassa uppannabhāvaṃ na jānāti, gacchāmi naṃ saṃvejetvā buddhuppādaṃ jānāpessāmī’’ ti khaṇeneva brahmalokato otaritvā suppārakapaṭṭane rattibhāgasamanantare dārucīriyassa sammukhe pāturahosi. "
463999,107,3461,103,123,1,109,15,So attano vasanaṭṭhāne obhāsaṃ disvā bahi nikkhamitvā mahābrahmānaṃ disvā añjaliṃ paggayha‘‘ ke tumhe’’ ti pucchi.
464000,107,3461,124,146,1,153,17,"‘‘ Ahaṃ tumhākaṃ porāṇakasahāyo anāgāmiphalaṃ patvā brahmaloke nibbatto, amhākaṃ sabbajeṭṭhako arahā hutvā parinibbuto, tumhe pana pañcajanā devaloke nibbattā. "
464001,107,3461,147,165,1,107,16,Svāhaṃ dāni taṃ imasmiṃ ṭhāne kuhanakammena jīvikaṃ kappentaṃ disvā damituṃ āgato’’ ti vatvā idaṃ kāraṇaṃ āha–
464002,107,3461,166,196,1,138,22,"‘‘ neva kho tvaṃ, bāhiya, arahā nāpi arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpanno, sāpi te paṭipadā natthi, yāya tvaṃ arahā vā assa arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpanno’’ ti. "
464003,107,3461,197,216,1,129,14,Athassa satthu uppannabhāvaṃ sāvatthiyaṃ vasanabhāvañca ācikkhitvā‘‘ satthu santikaṃ gacchā’’ ti taṃ uyyojetvā brahmalokameva agamāsi. 
464004,107,3462,2,10,1,65,8,Bāhiyo pana ākāse ṭhatvā kathentaṃ mahābrahmānaṃ oloketvā cintesi–
464005,107,3462,11,48,1,163,27,"‘‘ aho bhāriyaṃ kammaṃ mayā kataṃ, anarahaṃ arahā ahanti cintesiṃ, ayañca maṃ‘ na tvaṃ arahā, nāpi arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannāsī’ ti vadati, atthi nu kho loke añño arahā’’ ti. "
464006,107,3462,49,52,1,15,3,Atha naṃ pucchi–
464007,107,3462,53,68,1,71,11,‘‘ atha ke carahi sadevake loke arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannā’’ ti. 
464008,107,3462,69,72,1,22,3,Athassa devatā ācikkhi–
464009,107,3462,73,92,1,111,14,"‘‘ atthi, bāhiya, uttaresu janapadesu sāvatthi nāma nagaraṃ, tattha so bhagavā etarahi viharati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho. "
464010,107,3462,93,108,1,63,11,"So hi, bāhiya, bhagavā arahā ceva arahattāya ca dhammaṃ desesī’’ ti. "
464011,107,3462,109,141,1,287,30,"Bāhiyo rattibhāge devatāya kathaṃ sutvā saṃviggamānaso taṃkhaṇaṃyeva suppārakā nikkhamitvā ekarattivāsena sāvatthiṃ agamāsi, gacchanto ca pana devatānubhāvena buddhānubhāvena ca vīsayojanasatikaṃ maggaṃ atikkamitvā sāvatthiṃ anuppatto, tasmiṃ khaṇe satthā sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya paviṭṭho hoti. "
464012,107,3462,142,150,1,68,8,So jetavanaṃ pavisitvā abbhokāse caṅkamante sambahule bhikkhū pucchi–
464013,107,3462,151,159,1,23,4,‘‘ kuhiṃ etarahi satthā’’ ti? 
464014,107,3462,160,180,1,81,12,Bhikkhū‘‘ sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya paviṭṭho’’ ti vatvā‘‘ tvaṃ pana kuto āgatosī’’ ti pucchiṃsu.
