464036,107,3467,2,15,1,106,10,183. Pītisamphullitānanan ti pītiyā suṭṭhu phullitaṃ vikasitaṃ ānanaṃ mukhaṃ ādāsatalasadisamukhavantanti attho. 
464037,107,3468,2,16,1,116,10,184. Khippābhiññassa {bhikkhuno}ti khippaṃ desanāya samugghāṭitakkhaṇeyeva abhivisesena ñātuṃ samatthassa bhikkhunoti attho. 
464038,107,3469,2,19,1,78,11,186. Saggaṃ agaṃ sabhavanaṃ {yathā}ti attano gehaṃ viya saggaṃ lokaṃ agamāsinti attho. 
464039,107,3470,2,15,1,77,8,196. Na tvaṃ {upāyamaggaññū}ti tvaṃ nibbānādhigamūpāyabhūtamaggaññū na ahosīti attho. 
464040,107,3471,2,22,1,166,17,200. Satthuno sadā jinan ti sadā sabbakālaṃ jinaṃ jinanto parājitakopo satthuno sammāsambuddhassa vimalānanaṃ ādāsatalasadisamukhaṃ passissāmi passituṃ nikkhamāmīti yojanā. 
464041,107,3471,23,38,1,113,14,Dije apucchiṃ kuhiṃ {lokanandano}ti kuhiṃ ṭhāne lokapasādakaro satthāti dije brāhmaṇe ahaṃ bhikkhū apucchinti attho. 
464042,107,3472,2,18,1,114,12,201. Sasova khippaṃ {munidassanussuko}ti munidassane tathāgatadassane ussuko ussāhajāto saso iva khippaṃ pāpuṇātīti attho. 
464043,107,3473,2,10,1,30,4,202. Tuvaṭaṃ {gantvā}ti sīghaṃ gantvā. 
464044,107,3473,11,20,1,82,9,Piṇḍatthaṃ apihāgidhan ti piṇḍapātaṃ paṭicca apihaṃ apagatapihaṃ agidhaṃ nittaṇhaṃ. 
464045,107,3474,2,17,1,102,12,203. Alolakkhan ti ito cito ca anolokayamānaṃ uttame sāvatthinagare piṇḍāya vicarantaṃ adakkhinti sambandho. 
