464194,107,3514,318,335,1,166,16,"Satthā tassānukampaṃ paṭicca catumahārājehi dattiyena selamayapattena taṃ paṭiggahetvā yathā aṭṭhasaṭṭhiyā bhikkhusatasahassassa diyyamānaṃ na khīyati, evaṃ adhiṭṭhāsi. "
