464340,107,3546,2,4,1,27,2,4 . Vaṅgīsattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
464341,107,3547,2,10,1,79,7,Catutthāpadāne padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādikaṃ āyasmato vaṅgīsattherassa apadānaṃ. 
464342,107,3547,11,46,1,346,34,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle haṃsavatīnagare mahābhogakule nibbatto vuddhippatto dhammaṃ sotuṃ gacchantehi nagaravāsīhi saddhiṃ vihāraṃ gantvā dhammaṃ suṇanto satthāraṃ ekabhikkhuṃ paṭibhānavantānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā satthu adhikārakammaṃ katvā–
464343,107,3547,47,93,1,397,41,‘‘ ahampi anāgate paṭibhānavantānaṃ aggo bhaveyyan’’ ti patthanaṃ katvā satthārā byākato yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā devamanussesu ubhayasampattiyo anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā mātu paribbājikābhāvena aparabhāge paribbājakoti pākaṭo {vaṅgīso}ti ca laddhanāmo tayo vede uggaṇhitvā tato ācariyaṃ ārādhetvā chavasīsajānanamantaṃ nāma sikkhitvā chavasīsaṃ nakhena ākoṭetvā–
464344,107,3547,94,104,1,42,6,‘‘ ayaṃ satto asukayoniyaṃ nibbatto’’ ti jānāti. 
464345,107,3548,2,16,1,88,10,Brāhmaṇā ‘‘ ayaṃ amhākaṃ jivikāya maggo’’ ti vaṅgīsaṃ gahetvā gāmanigamarājadhāniyo vicariṃsu. 
464346,107,3548,17,24,1,67,7,Vaṅgīso tivassamatthake matānampi sīsaṃ āharāpetvā nakhena ākoṭetvā–
464347,107,3548,25,46,1,123,16,‘‘ ayaṃ satto asukayoniyaṃ nibbatto’’ ti vatvā mahājanassa kaṅkhācchedanatthaṃ te te jane āvāhetvā attano attano gatiṃ kathāpeti. 
464348,107,3548,47,52,1,34,4,Tena tasmiṃ mahājano abhippasīdati. 
464349,107,3548,53,61,1,62,8,So taṃ nissāya mahājanassa hatthato satampi sahassampi labhati. 
464350,107,3548,62,67,1,43,5,Brāhmaṇā vaṅgīsaṃ ādāya yathāruci vicariṃsu. 
464351,107,3548,68,75,1,58,7,Vaṅgīso satthu guṇe sutvā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitukāmo ahosi. 
464352,107,3548,76,88,1,62,8,Brāhmaṇā‘‘ samaṇo gotamo māyāya taṃ āvaṭṭessatī’’ ti paṭikkhipiṃsu. 
464353,107,3549,2,16,1,92,11,"Vaṅgīso tesaṃ vacanaṃ anādiyitvā, satthu santikaṃ gantvā, paṭisanthāraṃ katvā, ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
