464357,107,3549,55,74,1,119,16,"Atha satthā tassa ekaṃ niraye nibbattassa sīsaṃ, ekaṃ manussesu, ekaṃ devesu, ekaṃ parinibbutassa sīsaṃ āharāpetvā dassesi. "
464358,107,3549,75,92,1,69,11,"So paṭhamasīsaṃ ākoṭetvā,‘‘ bho gotama, ayaṃ satto niraye nibbatto’’ ti āha. "
