464681,107,3736,2,13,1,94,8,Chappaññāsame vagge paṭhamāpadāne mahāsamuddaṃ {oggayhā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato yasattherassa apadānaṃ. 
464682,107,3736,14,49,1,341,33,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sumedhassa bhagavato kāle mahānubhāvo nāgarājā hutvā buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ attano bhavanaṃ netvā mahādānaṃ pavattesi, bhagavantaṃ mahagghena ticīvarena acchādesi, ekekañca bhikkhuṃ mahaggheneva paccekadussayugena sabbena ca samaṇaparikkhārena. "
464683,107,3736,50,64,1,134,14,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle seṭṭhiputto hutvā mahābodhimaṇḍalaṃ sattahi ratanehi pūjesi. 
464684,107,3736,65,72,1,63,7,Kassapassa bhagavato kāle sāsane pabbajitvā samaṇadhammaṃ akāsi. 
464685,107,3736,73,98,1,208,23,"Evaṃ so sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto amhākaṃ bhagavato kāle bārāṇasiyaṃ mahāvibhavassa seṭṭhino putto hutvā sujātāya bhagavato khīrapāyāsaṃ dinnāya seṭṭhidhītāya kucchimhi nibbatti, yaso nāma nāmena paramasukhumālo. "
464686,107,3736,99,112,1,63,10,"Tassa tayo pāsādā honti– eko hemantiko, eko gimhiko, eko vassikoti. "
464687,107,3736,113,127,1,106,13,"So vassike pāsāde vassike cattāro māse nippurisehi tūriyehi paricārayamāno vasati, heṭṭhāpāsādaṃ na otarati. "
464688,107,3736,128,135,1,73,7,Hemantike pāsāde cattāro māse suphusitavātapānakavāṭe tattheva paṭivasati. 
464689,107,3736,136,142,1,64,6,Gimhike pāsāde bahukavāṭavātapānajālāhi sampanne tattheva vasati. 
464690,107,3736,143,148,1,59,5,Hatthapādānaṃ sukhumālatāya bhūmiyaṃ nisajjādikiccaṃ natthi. 
464691,107,3736,149,155,1,69,6,Simbalitulādipuṇṇasabhāve attharitvā tattha upadhānāni kiccāni karoti. 
464692,107,3736,156,177,1,182,19,"Evaṃ devaloke devakumāro viya pañcahi kāmaguṇehi samappitassa samaṅgībhūtassa paricārayamānassa paṭikacceva niddā okkami, parijanassāpi niddā okkami, sabbarattiyo ca telapadīpo jhāyati. "
464693,107,3736,178,218,1,280,33,"Atha kho yaso kulaputto paṭikacceva pabujjhitvā addasa sakaṃ parijanaṃ supantaṃ aññissā kacche vīṇaṃ, aññissā kaṇṭhe mudiṅgaṃ, aññissā kacche āḷambaraṃ, aññaṃ vikesikaṃ, vikkheḷikaṃ, aññā vippalapantiyo hatthapattaṃ susānaṃ maññe, disvānassa ādīnavo pāturahosi, nibbidāya cittaṃ saṇṭhāsi. "
464694,107,3736,219,225,1,38,6,Atha kho yaso kulaputto udānaṃ udānesi–
