465017,107,3794,2,22,1,173,15,29. Evaṃ ādittapariyāyadesanaṃ sutvā saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ sampatto nadīkassapo thero somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttarassa {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
