465021,107,3796,2,4,1,31,2,3 . Gayākassapattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
465022,107,3797,2,9,1,81,6,Tatiyāpadāne ajinacammavatthohan tiādikaṃ āyasmato gayākassapattherassa apadānaṃ. 
465023,107,3797,10,38,1,286,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ kusalaṃ upacinanto ito ekatiṃsakappe sikhissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbatto viññutaṃ patto nissaraṇajjhāsayatāya gharāvāsaṃ pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā araññāyatane assamaṃ māpetvā vanamūlaphalāhāro vasati. 
465024,107,3797,39,62,1,190,22,"Tena ca samayena bhagavā eko adutiyo tassa assamasamīpenāgacchi, so bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ ṭhito velaṃ olokento manoharāni kolaphalāni satthu upanesi. "
465025,107,3797,63,83,1,211,20,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā vayappatto nissaraṇajjhāsayatāya gharāvāsaṃ pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā dvīhi tāpasasatehi saddhiṃ gayāya viharati. 
465026,107,3797,84,93,1,69,8,Gayāya vasanato hissa kassapagottatāya ca {gayākassapo}ti samaññā ahosi. 
465027,107,3797,94,107,1,139,13,So bhagavato saddhiṃ parisāya ehibhikkhūpasampadaṃ datvā nadīkassapassa vuttanayena ādittapariyāya desanāya ovadiyamāno arahatte patiṭṭhāsi. 
465028,107,3798,2,15,1,99,9,35. So arahattaṃ patvā somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento ajinacammavatthohan tiādimāha . 
465029,107,3798,16,22,1,79,5,Tattha {ajinacammavattho}ti tāpasapabbajitattā ajinacammanivāsanapāvuraṇoti attho. 
465030,107,3798,23,28,1,71,4,{Khāribhāradharo}ti tāpasakāle tāpasaparikkhāraparipuṇṇakājadharoti attho. 
465031,107,3798,29,31,1,31,2,Khārikatāpasaparikkhāre pūretvā. 
465032,107,3798,32,42,1,71,10,Kolaṃ ahāsi assaman ti kolaphalaṃ assame pūretvā assame nisinnoti attho. 
465033,107,3798,43,53,1,72,9,Agopayin ti pāṭhe kolaphalaṃ pariyesitvā assamaṃ gopesiṃ rakkhinti attho. 
465034,107,3798,54,57,1,29,3,Sesaṃ sabbaṃ uttānatthamevāti. 
465035,107,3799,2,4,1,39,2,Gayākassapattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
465036,107,3800,2,4,1,26,2,4 . Kimilattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
465037,107,3801,2,9,1,78,6,Catutthāpadāne nibbute {kakusandhamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato kimilattherassa apadānaṃ. 
465038,107,3801,10,37,1,241,26,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto kakusandhassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto parinibbute satthari tassa dhātuyo uddissa salalamālāhi maṇḍapaṃ kāretvā pūjaṃ akāsi. 
465039,107,3801,38,56,1,171,17,So tena puññakammena tāvatiṃsesu uppajjitvā aparāparaṃ devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kapilavatthunagare sakyarājakule nibbattitvā {kimilo}ti tassa nāmaṃ akāsi. 
465040,107,3801,57,62,1,46,5,So vayappatto bhogasampattiyā pamatto viharati. 
465041,107,3801,63,86,1,216,22,"Tassa ñāṇaparipākaṃ ñatvā saṃvegajananatthaṃ anupiyāyaṃ viharanto satthā paṭhamayobbane ṭhitaṃ ramaṇīyaṃ itthirūpaṃ abhinimminitvā purato dassetvā puna anukkamena yathā jarārogavipattīhi abhibhūtā dissati, tathā akāsi. "
465042,107,3801,87,101,1,124,14,Taṃ disvā kimilakumāro ativiya saṃvegajāto attano saṃvegaṃ pakāsento bhagavato pākaṭaṃ katvā laddhānusāsano arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
465043,107,3802,2,15,1,99,9,42. So arahattaṃ patvā somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nibbute {kakusandhamhī}tiādimāha. 
465044,107,3802,16,23,1,63,6,Brāhmaṇamhi {vusīmatī}ti pañcahi vasitāhi vasippattamhi bhagavati. 
465045,107,3802,24,33,1,106,9,Brāhmaṇassa sabbaguṇagaṇehi maṇḍitattā abhivūḷhītattā brāhmaṇamhi kakusandhe bhagavati parinibbuteti attho. 
465046,107,3802,34,37,1,25,3,Sesaṃ sabbaṃ uttānamevāti. 
465047,107,3803,2,4,1,34,2,Kimilattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
465048,107,3804,2,4,1,30,2,5 . Vajjiputtattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
465049,107,3805,2,10,1,66,5,Sahassaraṃsī {bhagavā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato vajjiputtattherassa apadānaṃ. 
465050,107,3805,11,30,1,190,19,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ puññaṃ upacinanto ito catunavutikappe ekaṃ paccekabuddhaṃ bhikkhāya gacchantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso kadaliphalāni adāsi. 
465051,107,3805,31,47,1,155,15,"So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde vesāliyaṃ licchavirājakumāro hutvā nibbatti, vajjirājaputtattā vajjiputto tvevassa samaññā. "
465052,107,3805,48,69,1,221,21,So daharo hutvā hatthisippādisikkhanakālepi hetusampannatāya nissaraṇajjhāsayova hutvā vicaranto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho satthu santike pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ katvā nacirasseva chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
465053,107,3805,70,99,1,273,29,Chaḷabhiñño pana hutvā aparabhāge aciraparinibbute satthari dhammaṃ saṅgāyituṃ saṅketaṃ katvā mahātheresu tattha tattha viharantesu ekadivasaṃ āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ sekhaṃyeva samānaṃ mahatiyā parisāya parivutaṃ dhammaṃ desentaṃ disvā tassa uparimaggādhigamāya ussāhaṃ janento–
465054,107,3806,2,11,1,53,6,"‘ ‘ Rukkhamūlagahanaṃ pasakkiya, nibbānaṃ hadayasmiṃ opiya; "
465055,107,3807,2,24,1,70,12,"Jhāya gotama mā ca pamādo, kiṃ te biḷibiḷikā karissatī’’ ti.( theragā.119)– gāthaṃ abhāsi; "
465056,107,3808,2,37,1,310,28,"Tattha rukkhamūlagahanan ti rukkhamūlabhūtaṃ gahanaṃ, gahanañhi atthi, na rukkhamūlaṃ, rukkhamūlañca atthi, na gahanaṃ, tesu rukkhamūlaggahaṇena ṭhānassa chāyāya sampannatāya vātātapaparissayābhāvaṃ dīpeti, gahanaggahaṇena nivātabhāvena vātaparissayābhāvaṃ janasambādhābhāvañca dasseti, tadubhayena ca bhāvanāyogyataṃ. "
465057,107,3808,38,41,1,21,2,{Pasakkiyā}ti upagantvā. 
465058,107,3808,42,61,1,113,14,Nibbānaṃ hadayasmiṃ {opiyā}ti‘‘ evaṃ mayā paṭipajjitvā nibbānaṃ adhigantabban’’ ti nibbutiṃ hadaye ṭhapetvā citte katvā. 
465059,107,3808,62,70,1,82,6,"{Jhāyā}ti tilakkhaṇūpanijjhānena jhāya, vipassanābhāvanāsahitaṃ maggabhāvanaṃ bhāvehi. "
465060,107,3808,71,75,1,42,3,{Gotamā}ti dhammabhaṇḍāgārikaṃ gottenālapati. 
465061,107,3808,76,85,1,54,8,Mā ca {pamādo}ti adhikusalesu dhammesu mā pamādaṃ āpajji. 
465062,107,3808,86,105,1,93,13,"Idāni yādiso therassa pamādo, taṃ paṭikkhepavasena dassento‘‘ kiṃ te biḷibiḷikā karissatī’’ ti āha. "
465063,107,3808,106,118,1,109,9,"Tattha {biḷibiḷikā}ti biḷibiḷikiriyā, biḷibiḷitisaddapavatti yathā niratthakā, evaṃ biḷibiḷikāsadisā janapaññatti. "
465064,107,3808,119,135,1,113,14,"Kiṃ te {karissatī}ti kīdisaṃ atthaṃ tuyhaṃ sādhessati, tasmā janapaññattiṃ pahāya sadatthapasuto hohīti ovādaṃ adāsi. "
465065,107,3809,2,35,1,279,28,Taṃ sutvā aññehi vuttena vissagandhavāyanavacanena saṃvegajāto bahudeva rattiṃ caṅkamena vītināmento vipassanaṃ ussukkāpetvā senāsanaṃ pavisitvā mañcake nisinnamattova‘‘ kiñci sayāmī’’ ti sīsaṃ bimbohanamasampattaṃ pādaṃ bhūmito uggataṃ sarīrassa ākāsagatakkhaṇeyeva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
465066,107,3810,2,14,1,107,8,49. Vajjiputtatthero aparabhāge somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento sahassaraṃsī {bhagavā}tiādimāha. 
465067,107,3810,15,35,1,119,11,Tattha {sahassaraṃsī}ti ettha‘‘ anekasatasahassaraṃsī’’ ti vattabbe gāthābandhasukhatthaṃ‘‘ sahassaraṃsī’’ ti vuttanti veditabbaṃ. 
465068,107,3810,36,38,1,22,2,Sesaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
465069,107,3811,2,4,1,38,2,Vajjiputtattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
465070,107,3812,2,4,1,26,2,6 . Uttarattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
465071,107,3813,2,10,1,80,7,Chaṭṭhāpadāne sumedho nāma {sambuddho}tiādikaṃ āyasmato uttarasāmaṇerassa apadānaṃ. 
465072,107,3813,11,28,1,151,16,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sumedhassa bhagavato kāle vijjādharo hutvā ākāsena vicarati. 
465073,107,3813,29,41,1,124,12,Tena ca samayena satthā tasseva anuggaṇhanatthaṃ vanantare aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle nisīdi chabbaṇṇabuddharaṃsiyo vissajjento. 
465074,107,3813,42,95,1,463,49,"So antalikkhena gacchanto bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso ākāsato oruyha suvisuddhehi vipulehi kaṇikārapupphehi bhagavantaṃ pūjesi, pupphāni buddhānubhāvena satthu upari chattākārena aṭṭhaṃsu, so tena bhiyyosomattāya pasannacitto hutvā aparabhāge kālaṃ katvā tāvatiṃsesu nibbattitvā dibbasampattiṃ anubhavanto yāvatāyukaṃ tattha ṭhatvā tato cuto devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde rājagahe brāhmaṇamahāsālassa putto hutvā nibbatti, uttaro tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
465075,107,3813,96,111,1,120,15,So viññutaṃ patto brāhmaṇavijjāsu nipphattiṃ gantvā jātiyā rūpena vijjāya vayena sīlācārena ca lokassa sambhāvanīyo jāto. 
465076,107,3814,2,15,1,110,13,Tassa taṃ sampattiṃ disvā vassakāro magadhamahāmatto attano dhītaraṃ dātukāmo hutvā attano adhippāyaṃ pavedesi. 
465077,107,3814,16,34,1,180,18,So nissaraṇajjhāsayatāya taṃ paṭikkhipitvā kālena kālaṃ dhammasenāpatiṃ payirupāsanto tassa santike dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vattasampanno hutvā theraṃ upaṭṭhahati. 
465078,107,3815,2,28,1,210,24,"Tena ca samayena therassa aññataro ābādho uppanno, tassa bhesajjatthāya uttaro sāmaṇero pātova pattacīvaramādāya vihārato nikkhanto antarāmagge taḷākassa samīpe pattaṃ ṭhapetvā udakasamīpaṃ gantvā mukhaṃ dhovati. "
465079,107,3815,29,46,1,171,17,Atha aññataro umaṅgacoro katakammo ārakkhapurisehi anubaddho aggamaggena nagarato nikkhamitvā palāyanto attanā gahitaṃ ratanabhaṇḍitaṃ sāmaṇerassa patte pakkhipitvā palāyi. 
465080,107,3815,47,50,1,31,3,Sāmaṇeropi pattasamīpaṃ upagato. 
465081,107,3815,51,75,1,162,19,"Coraṃ anubandhantā rājapurisā sāmaṇerassa patte bhaṇḍikaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ coro, iminā coriyaṃ katan’’ ti sāmaṇeraṃ pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā vassakārassa brāhmaṇassa dassesuṃ. "
465082,107,3815,76,115,1,192,24,"Vassakāro ca tadā rañño vinicchaye niyutto hutvā chejjabhejjaṃ anusāsati, so‘‘ pubbe mama vacanaṃ nādiyi, suddhapāsaṇḍiyesu pabbajī’’ ti( theragā. aṭṭha.1. uttarattheragāthāvaṇṇanā) kammaṃ asodhetvā ghātukāmattāva jīvantameva taṃ sūle uttāsesi. "
465083,107,3816,2,39,1,359,30,"Athassa bhagavā ñāṇaparipākaṃ oloketvā taṃ ṭhānaṃ gantvā vipphurantahatthanakhamaṇimayūkhasambhinnasitābhatāya paggharantajātihiṅgulakasuvaṇṇarasadhāraṃ viya jālāguṇṭhitamudutalunadīghaṅgulihatthaṃ uttarassa sīse ṭhapetvā‘‘ uttara, idaṃ te purimakammassa phalaṃ uppannaṃ, tattha tayā paccavekkhaṇabalena adhivāsanā kātabbā’’ ti vatvā ajjhāsayānurūpaṃ dhammaṃ desesi. "
465084,107,3816,40,64,1,268,23,Uttaro amatābhisekasadisena satthu hatthasamphassena sañjātappasādasomanassatāya uḷārapītipāmojjaṃ paṭilabhitvā yathāparicitaṃ vipassanāmaggaṃ samārūḷho ñāṇassa paripākaṃ gatattā satthu ca desanāvilāsena tāvadeva maggapaṭipāṭiyā sabbe kilese khepetvā chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
465085,107,3816,65,75,1,87,10,Chaḷabhiñño pana hutvā sūlato uṭṭhahitvā parānuddayāya ākāse ṭhatvā pāṭihāriyaṃ dassesi. 
465086,107,3816,76,79,1,39,3,Mahājano acchariyabbhutacittajāto ahosi. 
465087,107,3816,80,130,1,279,34,"Tāvadevassa vaṇo saṃrūḷhi, so bhikkhūhi,‘‘ āvuso, tādisadukkhaṃ anubhavanto kathaṃ tvaṃ vipassanaṃ anuyuñjituṃ asakkhī’’ ti puṭṭho,‘‘ pageva me, āvuso, saṃsāre ādīnavo, saṅkhārānañca sabhāvo sudiṭṭho, evāhaṃ tādisaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhavantopi asakkhiṃ vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā visesaṃ adhigantun’’ ti āha."
465088,107,3816,131,152,1,191,17,‘‘ Pubbajātiyā daharakāle makkhikaṃ gahetvā nimbasūlakaṃ gahetvā sūlāropanakīḷaṃ paṭicca evaṃ anekajātisatesu sūlāropanadukkhamanubhavitvā imāya pariyosānajātiyā evarūpaṃ dukkhamanubhūtan’’ ti āha. 
465089,107,3817,2,16,1,110,10,55. Atha aparabhāge pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento sumedho nāma {sambuddho}tiādimāha. 
465090,107,3817,17,20,1,40,3,Tattha anuttānapadavaṇṇanameva karissāma. 
465091,107,3818,2,23,1,173,17,57. Vijjādharo tadā āsin ti bāhirakamantādivijjāsiddhiyā ākāsagāmisamattho hutvā caraṇavasena taṃ vijjaṃ rakkhitvā avināsetvā pariharaṇavasena vijjādharayoni āsiṃ ahosinti attho. 
465092,107,3818,24,33,1,81,9,Antalikkhacaro ahan ti antaṃ pariyosānaṃ koṭiṃ likhate saṃkarissatīti antalikkhaṃ. 
465093,107,3818,34,50,1,112,14,"Atha vā antaṃ pariyosānaṃ likhyate olokiyate etenāti antalikkhaṃ, tasmiṃ antalikkhe, ākāse caraṇasīlo ahanti attho. "
465094,107,3818,51,60,1,52,7,"Tisūlaṃ sukataṃ {gayhā}ti tikhiṇaṃ sūlaṃ, aggaṃ āvudhaṃ. "
465095,107,3818,61,74,1,123,12,"Tisūlaṃ sundaraṃ kataṃ, koṭṭanaghaṃsanamaddanapaharaṇavasena suṭṭhu kataṃ sūlāvudhaṃ gayha gahetvā ambarato gacchāmīti attho. "
465096,107,3818,75,81,1,64,6,Sesaṃ sabbaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayattāva nayānuyogena suviññeyyamevāti. 
465097,107,3819,2,4,1,34,2,Uttarattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
465098,107,3820,2,4,1,31,2,7 . Aparauttarattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
465099,107,3821,2,11,1,85,7,Sattamāpadāne nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādikaṃ āyasmato aparassa uttarattherassa apadānaṃ. 
465100,107,3821,12,37,1,236,24,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto ito catunnavutikappe siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā vayappatto viññutaṃ patvā sāsane laddhappasādo hutvā upāsakattaṃ nivedesi. 
465101,107,3821,38,48,1,95,10,So satthari parinibbute attano ñātake sannipātetvā bahupūjāsakkāraṃ saṃharitvā dhātupūjaṃ akāsi. 
465102,107,3821,49,89,1,403,39,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sākete brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā {uttaro}ti laddhanāmo vayappatto kenacideva karaṇīyena sāvatthiṃ gato kaṇḍambamūle kataṃ yamakapāṭihāriyaṃ disvā pasīditvā puna kāḷakārāmasuttadesanāya abhivaḍḍhamānasaddho pabbajitvā satthārā saddhiṃ rājagahaṃ gantvā upasampadaṃ labhitvā tatheva caranto vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā nacirasseva chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
465103,107,3821,90,101,1,112,11,Chaḷabhiñño pana hutvā satthari sāvatthiyaṃ viharante buddhupaṭṭhānatthaṃ rājagahato sāvatthiṃ upagato bhikkhūhi–
465104,107,3821,102,118,1,71,10,"‘‘ kiṃ, āvuso, pabbajjākiccaṃ tayā matthakaṃ pāpitan’’ ti puṭṭho aññaṃ byākāsi. "
465105,107,3822,2,15,1,100,9,93. Arahattaṃ pana patvā somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento nibbute {lokanāthamhī}tiādimāha. 
465106,107,3822,16,21,1,47,5,Taṃ sabbaṃ heṭṭhā vuttanayattā uttānatthamevāti. 
465107,107,3823,2,4,1,39,2,Aparauttarattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
465108,107,3824,2,4,1,28,2,8 . Bhaddajittheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
465109,107,3825,2,10,1,81,7,Aṭṭhamāpadāne ogayhāhaṃ pokkharaṇin tiādikaṃ āyasmato bhaddajittherassa apadānaṃ. 
465110,107,3825,11,49,1,360,37,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto brāhmaṇānaṃ vijjāsippesu pāraṃ gantvā kāme pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā araññāyatane assamaṃ kāretvā vasanto ekadivasaṃ satthāraṃ ākāsena gacchantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso añjaliṃ paggayha aṭṭhāsi. 
465111,107,3825,50,56,1,43,6,Satthā tassa ajjhāsayaṃ disvā ākāsato otari. 
465112,107,3825,57,74,1,146,16,"Otiṇṇassa pana bhagavato madhuñca bhisamuḷālañca sappikhīrañca upanāmesi, tassa taṃ bhagavā anukammaṃ upādāya paṭiggahetvā anumodanaṃ katvā pakkāmi. "
465113,107,3825,75,98,1,220,23,So tena puññakammena tusitesu nibbatto tattha yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cuto aparāparaṃ sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto vipassissa bhagavato kāle mahaddhano seṭṭhi hutvā aṭṭhasaṭṭhibhikkhusatasahassaṃ bhojetvā ticīvarena acchādesi. 
465114,107,3826,2,9,1,42,6,Evaṃ bahuṃ kusalaṃ katvā devaloke nibbatti. 
465115,107,3826,10,43,1,299,33,Tattha yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cavitvā manussalokesu uppanno buddhasuññe loke pañca paccekabuddhasatāni catūhi paccayehi upaṭṭhahitvā tato cuto rājakule nibbattitvā rajjaṃ anusāsanto attano puttaṃ paccekabodhiṃ adhigantvā ṭhitaṃ upaṭṭhahitvā tassa parinibbutassa dhātuyo gahetvā cetiyaṃ katvā pūjesi. 
465116,107,3826,44,64,1,168,19,"Evaṃ tattha tattha tāni tāni puññāni katvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde bhaddiyanagare asītikoṭivibhavassa bhaddiyaseṭṭhissa ekaputtako hutvā nibbatti, bhaddajī tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
465117,107,3826,65,72,1,77,7,Tassa kira issariyabhogaparivārasampatti carimabhave bodhisattassa viya ahosi. 
465118,107,3827,2,18,1,166,16,Tadā satthā sāvatthiyaṃ vasitvā bhaddajikumāraṃ saṅgaṇhanatthāya mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ bhaddiyanagaraṃ gantvā jātiyāvane vasi tassa ñāṇaparipākaṃ āgamayamāno. 
465119,107,3827,19,58,1,303,34,"Sopi uparipāsāde nisinno sīhapañjaraṃ vivaritvā olokento bhagavato santike dhammaṃ sotuṃ gacchantaṃ mahājanaṃ disvā,‘‘ katthāyaṃ mahājano gacchatī’’ ti pucchitvā taṃ kāraṇaṃ sutvā sayampi mahatā parivārena satthu santikaṃ gantvā dhammaṃ suṇanto sabbābharaṇapaṭimaṇḍitova sabbakilese khepetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
465120,107,3827,59,66,1,59,7,Arahatte pana tena adhigate satthā bhaddiyaseṭṭhiṃ āmantesi–
465121,107,3827,67,90,1,137,16,"‘‘ tava putto alaṅkatapaṭiyatto dhammaṃ suṇanto arahatte patiṭṭhāsi, tenassa idāneva pabbajituṃ yuttaṃ, no ce pabbajissati, parinibbāyissatī’’ ti. "
