465145,107,3829,2,17,1,125,12,98. Thero pana arahattaṃ patto pubbasambhāraṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsetuṃ ogayhāhaṃ pokkharaṇin tiādimāha. 
465146,107,3829,18,45,1,241,22,Tattha ogayhāhaṃ pokkharaṇin ti puthunānāanekamahoghehi khaṇitattā‘‘ pokkharaṇī’’ ti laddhanāmaṃ jalāsayaṃ ogayha ogahetvā pavisitvā ajjhogāhetvā ghāsahetukhādanatthāya tattha pokkharaṇiyaṃ pavisitvā bhisaṃ padumapuṇḍarīkamūlaṃ uddharāmīti attho. 
