465149,107,3831,2,4,1,26,2,9 . Sivakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
465150,107,3832,2,10,1,73,6,Navamāpadāne esanāya {carantassā}tiādikaṃ āyasmato sivakattherassa apadānaṃ. 
465151,107,3832,11,38,1,251,27,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ bhagavantaṃ piṇḍāya carantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso pattaṃ ādāya kummāsassa pūretvā adāsi. 
465152,107,3832,39,53,1,128,14,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde rājagahe brāhmaṇakulagehe nibbattitvā sivako tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. 
465153,107,3832,54,78,1,235,23,So vayappatto vijjāsippesu nipphattiṃ gato nekkhammajjhāsayatāya kāme pahāya tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā vicaranto satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
465154,107,3833,2,14,1,93,8,117. Arahattaṃ patvā somanassajāto attano pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento esanāya {carantassā}tiādimāha. 
465155,107,3833,15,18,1,27,3,Taṃ sabbaṃ suviññeyyamevāti. 
465156,107,3834,2,4,1,34,2,Sivakattheraapadānavaṇṇanā samattā.
465157,107,3835,2,4,1,27,2,10 . Upavānattheraapadānavaṇṇanā 
465158,107,3836,2,10,1,77,7,Dasamāpadāne padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādikaṃ āyasmato upavānattherassa apadānaṃ. 
465159,107,3836,11,51,1,398,39,Ayaṃ kira purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto kenaci kammacchiddena padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle dalliddakule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto bhagavati parinibbute tassa dhātuṃ gahetvā manussadevanāgagaruḷayakkhakumbhaṇḍagandhabbehi sattaratanamaye sattayojanike thūpe kate tattha sudhotaṃ attano uttarāsaṅgaṃ veḷagge ābandhitvā dhajaṃ katvā pūjaṃ akāsi. 
465160,107,3836,52,67,1,151,15,Taṃ gahetvā abhisammatako nāma yakkhasenāpati devehi cetiyapūjārakkhaṇatthaṃ ṭhapito adissamānakāyo ākāse dhārento cetiyaṃ tikkhattuṃ padakkhiṇaṃ akāsi. 
465161,107,3836,68,73,1,45,5,Taṃ disvā bhiyyosomattāya pasannamānaso ahosi. 
465162,107,3836,74,98,1,248,23,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā {upavāno}ti laddhanāmo vayappatto jetavanapaṭiggahaṇe buddhānubhāvaṃ disvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
465163,107,3836,99,105,1,43,5,Athāyasmā upavāno bhagavato upaṭṭhāko ahosi . 
465164,107,3836,106,112,1,44,6,Tena ca samayena bhagavato vātābādho uppajji. 
465165,107,3836,113,120,1,65,7,Therassa gihisahāyo devahito nāma brāhmaṇo sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati. 
465166,107,3836,121,126,1,35,5,So theraṃ catūhi paccayehi pavāresi. 
465167,107,3836,127,136,1,86,9,Athāyasmā upavāno nivāsetvā pattacīvaraṃ gahetvā tassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṃ upagañchi. 
465168,107,3836,137,161,1,98,14,"Brāhmaṇo‘‘ kenaci maññe payojanena thero āgato bhavissatī’’ ti ñatvā‘‘ vadeyyātha, bhante, kenattho’’ ti āha. "
465169,107,3836,162,167,1,44,5,Thero tassa brāhmaṇassa payojanaṃ ācikkhanto–
465170,107,3837,2,10,1,37,6,"‘ ‘ Arahaṃ sugato loke, vātehābādhiko muni; "
465171,107,3838,2,9,1,41,6,"Sace uṇhodakaṃ atthi, munino dehi brāhmaṇa."
465172,107,3839,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Pūjito pūjaneyyānaṃ, sakkareyyāna sakkato; "
465173,107,3840,2,16,1,41,5,"Apacitopaceyyānaṃ , tassa icchāmi hātave’’ ti.( theragā.185-186)– "
465174,107,3841,2,4,1,18,2,Gāthādvayaṃ abhāsi. 
465175,107,3842,2,51,1,403,42,"Tassattho – yo imasmiṃ loke pūjaneyyānaṃ pūjetabbehi sakkādīhi devehi mahābrahmādīhi ca brahmehi pūjito, sakkareyyānaṃ sakkātabbehi bimbisārakosalarājādīhi sakkato, apaceyyānaṃ apacāyitabbehi mahesīhi khīṇāsavehi apacito, kilesehi ārakattādinā arahaṃ, sobhanagamanādinā sugato sabbaññū muni mayhaṃ satthā devadevo sakkānaṃ atisakko brahmānaṃ atibrahmā, so dāni vātehi vātahetu vātakkhobhanimittaṃ ābādhiko jāto. "
465176,107,3842,52,66,1,90,10,"Sace , brāhmaṇa, uṇhodakaṃ atthi, tassa vātābādhavūpasamanatthaṃ taṃ hātave upanetuṃ icchāmīti. "
465177,107,3843,2,11,1,82,9,Taṃ sutvā brāhmaṇo uṇhodakaṃ tadanurūpaṃ vātaharañca bhesajjaṃ bhagavato upanāmesi. 
465178,107,3843,12,17,1,28,5,Tena ca satthu rogo vūpasami. 
465179,107,3843,18,22,1,30,4,Tassa bhagavā anumodanaṃ akāsi. 
465180,107,3844,2,18,1,129,12,122. Athāyasmā upavāno aparabhāge attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassajāto pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttaro nāma {jino}tiādimāha. 
465181,107,3844,19,24,1,45,4,Tattha {padumuttaro}tiādīni pubbe vuttatthāneva. 
465182,107,3845,2,11,1,60,5,123. Mahājanā {samāgammā}ti sakalajambudīpavāsino rāsibhūtāti attho. 
465183,107,3845,12,23,1,105,10,Citakaṃ {katvā}ti yojanubbedhaṃ candanarāsicitakaṃ katvā bhagavato sarīraṃ tattha abhiropayiṃsūti sambandho. 
465184,107,3846,2,14,1,66,7,124. Sarīrakiccaṃ {katvānā}ti ādahanāti agginā dahanakiccaṃ katvāti attho. 
465185,107,3847,2,4,1,0,0,127-28. 
465186,107,3847,5,18,1,115,12,Jaṅghā maṇimayā {āsī}ti manussehi katathūpe jaṅghā pupphavāhatthaṃ caritaṭṭhānaṃ maṇimayā indanīlamaṇinā katāti attho. 
465187,107,3847,19,26,1,45,6,{Mayampī}ti sabbe devā thūpaṃ karissāmāti attho. 
465188,107,3848,2,25,1,129,18,"129. Dhātu āveṇikā {natthī}ti devamanussehi visuṃ visuṃ cetiyaṃ kātuṃ āveṇikā visuṃ dhātu natthi, taṃ dassento sarīraṃ ekapiṇḍitan ti āha. "
465189,107,3848,26,33,1,84,7,Adhiṭṭhānabalena sakalasarīradhātu ekaghanasilāmayapaṭimā viya ekameva ahosīti attho. 
465190,107,3848,34,47,1,131,12,Imamhi {buddhathūpamhī}ti sakalajambudīpavāsīhi katamhi imamhi suvaṇṇathūpamhi mayaṃ sabbe samāgantvā kañcukathūpaṃ karissāmāti attho. 
465191,107,3849,2,11,1,64,6,133. Indanīlaṃ mahānīlan ti indīvarapupphavaṇṇābhaṃ maṇi indanīlamaṇi. 
465192,107,3849,12,30,1,179,18,Tato adhikavaṇṇatā mahāmaṇi indanīlamaṇayo ca mahānīlamaṇayo ca jotirasamaṇijātiraṅgamaṇayo ca ekato sannipātetvā rāsī katvā suvaṇṇathūpe kañcukathūpaṃ katvā achādayunti sambandho. 
465193,107,3850,2,17,1,94,10,144. Paccekaṃ {buddhaseṭṭhassā}ti buddhuttamassa pati ekaṃ visuṃ uparichadanena thūpaṃ akaṃsūti attho. 
465194,107,3851,2,31,1,182,22,"147. Kumbhaṇḍā guyhakā {tathā}ti kumbhamattāni aṇḍāni yesaṃ devānaṃ te kumbhaṇḍā, paṭicchādetvā niguhitvā paṭicchādanato garuḷā guyhakā nāma jātā, te kumbhaṇḍā guyhakāpi thūpaṃ akaṃsūti attho. "
465195,107,3852,2,20,1,112,13,"151. Atibhonti na {tassābhā}ti tassa cetiyassa pabhaṃ candasūriyatārakānaṃ pabhā na atibhonti, na ajjhottharantīti attho. "
465196,107,3853,2,19,1,126,13,158. Ahampi kāraṃ {kassāmī}ti tādino lokanāthassa thūpasmiṃ ahampi kāraṃ puññakiriyaṃ kusalakammaṃ dhajapaṭākapūjaṃ karissāmīti attho. 
