465218,107,3858,51,57,1,46,4,"{Urūḷhavā}ti rājāvahanayoggasamattho, rājāraho vā. "
465219,107,3858,58,63,1,65,4,{Setacchatto}ti alaṅkāratthāya upaṭṭhahanasetacchattasahitoti attho. 
465220,107,3858,64,70,1,56,5,{Pasobhito}ti ārohapariṇāhavā rūpasobhāhi sampannoti attho. 
