465703,108,208,2,12,1,58,8,"‘ ‘ Tasmā mahārāja bhavesu bhoge, manorame paccanubhuyya bhiyyo; "
465704,108,209,2,13,1,63,8,"Vihāradānassa phalena santaṃ, sukhaṃ asokaṃ adhigaccha pacchā’’ ti. "
465705,108,210,2,23,1,279,21,Iccevaṃ munirājā nararājassa bimbisārassa vihāradānānumodanaṃ katvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhikkhusaṅghaparivuto paramadassanīyāya attano sarīrappabhāya suvaṇṇarasasekapiñcharāni viya nagaravanavimānādīni kurumāno anopamāya buddhalīḷāya anantāya buddhasiriyā veḷuvanamahāvihārameva pāvisīti.
465706,108,211,2,11,1,52,7,"‘ ‘ Akīḷane veḷuvane vihāre, tathāgato tattha manobhirāme; "
465707,108,212,2,10,1,53,5,"Nānāvihārena vihāsi dhīro, veneyyakānaṃ samudikkhamāno’’. "
465708,108,213,2,30,1,229,23,Athevaṃ bhagavati tasmiṃ viharante suddhodana mahārājā‘‘ putto me chabbassāni dukkarakārikaṃ katvā paramābhisambodhiṃ patvā pavattitavaradhammacakko rājagahaṃ patvā veḷuvanamahāvihāre viharatī’’ ti sutvā aññataraṃ mahāmaccaṃ āmantesi–
465709,108,213,31,58,1,139,19,"‘‘ ehi, bhaṇe, purisasahassaparivāro rājagahaṃ gantvā mama vacanena‘ pitā vo suddhodanamahārājā taṃ daṭṭhukāmo’ ti vatvā puttaṃ me gaṇhitvā ehī’’ ti. "
465710,108,213,59,76,1,117,12,"So‘‘ sādhu, devā’’ ti rañño paṭissuṇitvā purisasahassaparivāro saṭṭhiyojanamaggaṃ gantvā dhammadesanavelāya vihāraṃ pāvisi. "
465711,108,213,77,100,1,156,18,So‘‘ tiṭṭhatu tāva raññā pahitasāsanan’’ ti parisapariyante ṭhito satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā yathāṭhitova saddhiṃ purisasahassena arahattaṃ patvā pabbajjaṃ yāci. 
465712,108,213,101,102,1,7,1,Bhagavā–
465713,108,213,103,113,1,34,5,"‘‘ etha, bhikkhavo’’ ti hatthaṃ pasāresi. "
465714,108,213,114,124,1,118,10,Te sabbe taṅkhaṇaññeva iddhimayapattacīvaradharā vassasaṭṭhikattherā viya ākappasampannā hutvā bhagavantaṃ parivāresuṃ. 
465715,108,213,125,146,1,101,15,"Rājā‘‘ neva gato āgacchati, na ca sāsanaṃ suyyatī’’ ti cintetvā teneva nīhārena navakkhattuṃ amacce pesesi. "
465716,108,213,147,158,1,69,10,"Tesu navasu purisasahassesu ekopi rañño nārocesi, na sāsanaṃ vā pahiṇi. "
465717,108,213,159,163,1,34,4,Sabbe arahattaṃ patvāva pabbajiṃsu. 
465718,108,214,2,5,1,17,3,Atha rājā cintesi–
465719,108,214,6,21,1,73,11,‘‘ ko nu kho mama vacanaṃ karissatī’’ ti sabbarājabalaṃ olokento udāyiṃ addasa. 
465720,108,214,22,35,1,126,13,So kira rañño sabbatthasādhako amacco abbhantariko ativissāsiko bodhisattena saddhiṃ ekadivaseyeva jāto sahapaṃsukīḷito sahāyo. 
465721,108,214,36,40,1,22,4,Atha naṃ rājā āmantesi–
465722,108,214,41,69,1,188,22,"‘‘ tāta udāyi, ahaṃ mama puttaṃ daṭṭhukāmo navapurisasahassāni pesesiṃ, ekapurisopi āgantvā sāsanamattampi ārocetā natthi, dujjāno kho pana me jīvitantarāyo, ahaṃ jīvamānova puttaṃ daṭṭhumicchāmi. "
465723,108,214,70,77,1,33,5,Sakkhissasi me puttaṃ dassetun’’ ti? 
465724,108,214,78,92,1,53,8,"So‘‘ sakkhissāmi, deva, sace pabbajituṃ labhissāmī’’ ti āha."
465725,108,214,93,108,1,63,10,"‘‘ Tāta, tvaṃ pabbajitvā vā apabbajitvā vā mayhaṃ puttaṃ dassehī’’ ti. "
465726,108,214,109,134,1,176,20,"So‘‘ sādhu, devā’’ ti rañño sāsanaṃ ādāya rājagahaṃ gantvā satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā saddhiṃ purisasahassena arahattaṃ patvā ehibhikkhubhāve patiṭṭhāya phaggunīpuṇṇamāsiyaṃ cintesi–"
